\id LUK - Uare 
\h Luka 
\toc3 Luk 
\toc2 Luka 
\toc1 Iesu Keriso Hari Manoḡa Lukaꞌa Mirihiro 
\mt1 Luka  
\mt2 Iesu Keriso Hari Manoḡa Lukaꞌa Mirihiro  
\imt1 Ihore Ḡoeꞌa  
\ip Buka ꞌahiꞌe Lukaꞌa vaze boro ꞌahoga, niḡa Teofilo veize mirihiro. Lukaꞌe gohe vazeḡa zu Paulo teite tuburu gauiroteꞌe vazeḡa. Aniꞌe Iuda mene vazeḡa, rehano Giriki vazeḡa. Aniꞌe Iuda azaḡa ebu Iuda mene azaḡa veize Iesu hari manoḡa mirihadu Iesuꞌe zeḡe niduꞌa ḡabozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rae ihoziro. Aniꞌe Iesuꞌa nougenouge hugano radiunuteꞌe ihozeꞌenaꞌa, vaze niduꞌa iḡaiḡa ufeta vetuḡazinuteꞌe moneo rae fureniro. Mataio teige, Luka zuni Iesuꞌa fureraroteꞌe hariḡa mirihiro. Aniꞌe buka ꞌahoga, Apostolo Azaḡa Haḡai zuni mirihiro.  
\c 1  
\s1 Lukaꞌa Teofilo veize Mirihiro  
\p
\v 1 Vaze boro Teofilo, emeḡe boꞌaḡano naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe moneo vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa mirihozinihi radu inare huniro.  
\v 2 Vaze nuꞌe Iesu hariḡa ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo onamo ḡonagano ubumaze hina horonadu ane ḡoere rae fureniro zu emeḡe ihofiro. Ebu zeḡeꞌa ihofiroteꞌe idunaḡano vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa Iesu hari mirihiro.  
\v 3 Vaze boro Teofilo, eḡe zuni eꞌe hariḡa niduꞌaꞌe ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo onao izidi faifaine udahiro. Ebu eḡeꞌa ḡae veize hari ꞌadi ḡadaheḡanonoꞌo onamo ḡonaga mirihine, manoḡa rae zamariro.  
\v 4 Aꞌe ibite vazeꞌa ihoꞌirotaꞌaꞌe huga rae ḡaeꞌa ederifine raꞌohe.   
\s1 Ioane Babatisoꞌa Fureratiteꞌe moneo rae Fureniro  
\p
\v 5 Iudea habaꞌano Herodaꞌe kini reiroteꞌe madaḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ꞌahoga, niḡa Zekariaꞌa radiunu. Aniꞌe dibuꞌo azaḡa duḡuru ꞌahoga, Abia duḡuru mone dibuꞌo vazeḡa. Ebu inuga, niḡa Elizabetaꞌe Aroni mariga.  
\v 6 Zekaria zu Elizabetaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro goro ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa hegoteꞌenaꞌa, mene veꞌore radiunu ebu Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae reiro.  
\v 7 Rehano ze ubudeze oꞌoꞌa, mazaḡa Elizabetaꞌe gabani, zu anianineꞌe ufeta vouriro.   
\p
\v 8 Mada ꞌahogano Abia duḡuru dibuꞌo azaḡaniꞌa gaueꞌeteꞌe madaḡa meiro. Eꞌanoꞌo Zekaria zuni Badiꞌa kuru neḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa gauḡa haḡairo.  
\v 9 Eꞌe madaḡano dibuꞌo azaḡa haḡai idunaḡano ze kaḡusi arahoḡa arahiro, ebu Zuhiꞌa Boro kuru neḡano diuḡadu ꞌuvahu hohoḡa hufiteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga ohoniro. Kaḡusi arahirotene, Zekaria meiro.  
\v 10 Ebu Zekariaꞌa kuru neḡano ꞌuvahu hohoḡa hufiꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaꞌe kuru neḡa enogano kurau radiunu.   
\p
\v 11 Eꞌe madaḡano Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa Zekaria mazao fureraro. Aniꞌe ꞌuvahu hohoḡa hufiꞌeteꞌe fataḡa edaꞌe moneo edau radiro.  
\v 12 Zekariaꞌa tuḡure viga eꞌe horonirotene, ufeta zaguzagaro zu rihau rudaro.  
\v 13 Rehano tuḡure viga eꞌeꞌa ꞌahige rae niro, “Zekaria, ago rihanoꞌi. Badiꞌaꞌa ḡae kuru igiro ꞌahine, inugo Elizabetaꞌe ubugo ꞌahoga fureniꞌuma. Ebu niḡaꞌe Ioane rae turahoꞌi.  
\v 14 Ḡaꞌe ani uꞌano matuꞌe rudaꞌuma, ebu vaze ḡehaḡa zuni aneꞌa fureraroteꞌe moneo matuꞌiꞌuma.  
\v 15 Mazaḡa aniꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro zamao niḡa boro reꞌuma. Aniꞌe vaini vuḡa zu vu sauꞌa mene gagiꞌuma, ebu viꞌa isi zamaḡanonoꞌo Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ani ibitohaꞌuma.  
\v 16 Aniꞌe Isaraela azaḡa ḡehaḡa Zuhiꞌa Boro zeḡe Badiꞌa vaḡe tutuze ariꞌuma.  
\v 17 Ani viga zu gigiꞌaḡaꞌe peroveta vazeḡa Elia teigiꞌuma. Aniꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro ꞌizema arogano ariꞌuma, ebu moze zu ubudeze zamaze mae tibuzifine danaziꞌuma. Zu Badiꞌa mene egohauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe duduḡa azaḡa zamarone huhuzaḡa ibiḡano tutuziꞌuma, ebu vazeꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro veize ruhibifine ihoziꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 18 Zekariaꞌa tuḡure viga niro, “Ḡae ḡoere eꞌeꞌa fureratitaꞌaꞌe e nougenouge ederiꞌuma? E vaze vouḡa ebu inudehe zuni voureha.”  
\v 19 Ebu tuḡure viganiꞌa naenaeniro, “Eꞌe Gabiriela. Eꞌe Badiꞌa zamao edanadu ane gau haḡaeꞌohe. Badiꞌaꞌa hari manoḡa ꞌadi ḡae ihoꞌifine eḡe tuḡuheha.  
\v 20 Ḡianoꞌi. Madaḡaniꞌa arine, eḡeꞌa rateꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hugano fureraꞌuma. Ḡaꞌe eḡe ḡoere ꞌadi mene mae ḡihinateꞌe uꞌano, ḡaꞌe ḡoeroga mene idaraꞌuma, onamo eꞌeguḡaniꞌa fureratiteꞌe madaḡa meꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 21 U vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaꞌe enogano Zekaria guhine radiunu ebu ꞌahige zamarinu, “Aniꞌa kuru neḡa zamaḡano nougadu faḡa hune radiuꞌohe?”  
\v 22 Ebu Zekariaꞌa kuru neḡanonoꞌo buarotene, ani ḡorezoga mene idararo. Ani ꞌevoꞌa hina daꞌo ḡoreziro zu ḡoerogaꞌe mene idararo. Eꞌanoꞌo zeꞌe aniꞌa kuru neḡa zamaḡano ahiri raꞌaga iḡunaḡa horoniroteꞌe ederiro.  
\v 23 Ebu Zekariaꞌa kuru neḡano dibuꞌo gauḡa hauḡirotene, neḡa onamiro. \fig Zekariaꞌa ḡoeroga mene idararo|src="MH43001.tif" size="col" ref="1:21" \fig*   
\p
\v 24 Eꞌe enogano ani inuga Elizabetaꞌe ene tiro ebu bato fuꞌo ani neo radiunu.  
\v 25 Aniꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa eḡe veize ꞌahiguḡa haḡairo. Izidi Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa vaze boꞌaḡano eḡe mazagaro mae vaḡiniro.”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Fureratiteꞌe moneo rae Fureniro  
\p
\v 26 Elizabetaꞌa ene tiroteꞌe enogano bato fuꞌo tiba fare reirotene, Badiꞌaꞌa tuḡure viga Gabiriela Galilea habaꞌa Nazareta neḡano tuḡuniro.  
\v 27 ꞌOugadu ani roḡae ꞌahoga, niḡa Maria vaḡe onamiro. Mariaꞌe ohoze teite ꞌize mene baziroteꞌe nogobaḡa. Aniꞌe Davida mariga ꞌahoga, niḡa Iosefa teite iraꞌauniro.  
\v 28 Gabirielaꞌa Maria vaḡe aradu niro, “Badiꞌaꞌa manoḡa haroteꞌe roḡaeḡa, matuꞌoꞌi. Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ḡae teite radiuꞌohe.”  
\v 29 Mariaꞌa ḡoere eꞌe igirotene, zaguzagaro zu ꞌadaꞌadaniro, ebu “Ḡoere ꞌadi hugaꞌe nagini?” rae zamariro.  
\v 30 Ebu tuḡure viganiꞌa Maria niro, “Maria, ago rihanoꞌi, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa ḡae mazao manoḡa fureniro.  
\v 31 Ḡianoꞌi! Ḡaꞌe ene teadu ubugo ꞌahoga fureniꞌuma ebu niḡaꞌe Iesu rae turahiꞌuma.  
\v 32 Aniꞌe niḡa boro reꞌuma, ebu vazeꞌa aniꞌe Badiꞌa Hitaga Hune Ubuga rae huniꞌuma. Ebu ane vouḡa Davida teige, Zuhiꞌa Boro Badiꞌaꞌa aniꞌe kini iḡuri haꞌuma.  
\v 33 Aniꞌa Isaraela azaḡa\f + \fr 1:33 \fqa Iakobo ne \f* zuhiꞌaziꞌuma onamo tuḡutuḡu, ebu aniꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe mene hauḡiꞌuma.”  
\v 34 Ebu Mariaꞌa tuḡure viga niro, “Eꞌe ohoze teite bazoga ꞌize aḡuꞌa. Nougenouge ꞌuguḡaniꞌa fureraꞌuma?”  
\v 35 Ebu tuḡure viganiꞌa naenaeniro, “Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ḡae vaḡe ovaiꞌuma, zu Badiꞌa Hitaga Hune inaraḡaniꞌa ḡae zauhaḡadiꞌuma. Eꞌanoꞌo fureratiteꞌe tahiꞌaḡaꞌe zaḡoḡa reꞌuma zu Badiꞌa Ubuga rae huniꞌuma.  
\v 36 Ḡianoꞌi, ḡae nabugo Elizabeta zuni vouḡa ebu gabani rae huniro, rehano ene ohozeḡa teadu izidi bato fuꞌo tiba fare maha.  
\v 37 Badiꞌaꞌe gau niduꞌa haḡaogaꞌe idaḡa.”  
\v 38 Ebu Mariaꞌa naenaeniro, “Eꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure roḡaeḡa. Ḡaeꞌa rateꞌeꞌa eḡe mazao fureranoꞌi.” Ebu tuḡure viganiꞌa ani muhiniro.   
\s1 Mariaꞌa Elizabeta Vaḡe Onamiro  
\p
\v 39 Eꞌe ḡarugano Mariaꞌa iḡunadu Iudea habaꞌano guniꞌa neḡa ꞌahoga ḡarihe onamiro.  
\v 40 Ebu aniꞌa feurirotene, Zekaria ne diuḡadu Elizabeta niro, “Manoḡahe?”  
\v 41 Elizabetaꞌa Maria ago igirotene, ubugaꞌe isi zamaḡano hagariro, ebu Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa Elizabeta mazao iriꞌaviro.  
\v 42 Ebu Elizabetaꞌa Maria ḡihau niro, “Ḡaeꞌa roḡae niduꞌa boꞌaḡano manohuga ufeta hidiro. Ḡaꞌa fureniteꞌe tahiꞌaḡa zuni manohuga hidiro.  
\v 43 Eḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro viꞌaꞌe eḡe vaḡe areha. Badiꞌaꞌa eḡe mazao manoḡa fureneha!  
\v 44 Eḡeꞌa ḡae ago egatene, eḡe isi zamaḡano tahiꞌa komeꞌaꞌe matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa, hagareha.  
\v 45 Ḡa matuꞌe rudauꞌohe, mazaḡa ḡa Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ḡaniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaꞌuma rae mae ḡihiniro.”   
\s1 Mariaꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro Niguniro  
\p
\v 46 Ebu Mariaꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 “E Zuhiꞌa Boro niguneꞌohe,   
\q2
\v 47 ebu vineheꞌe eḡe ḡaboheꞌeteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa uꞌano matuꞌe rudauꞌohe,   
\q1
\v 48 mazaḡa eꞌe tuḡure roḡaeḡa zu nihe zuhuꞌa rehano, Badiꞌaꞌa eḡe zamariro.  
\q2 Izidionoꞌo onamo mada niduꞌa, vaze niduꞌa ꞌahige rae reꞌuma, 'Gaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa matuꞌoḡaniro.'   
\q1
\v 49 Mazaḡa Badiꞌa Gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa eḡe veize gau boro haḡairo.  
\q2 Ani niꞌe zaḡoḡa.   
\q1
\v 50 Aniꞌe ani gubaneꞌeteꞌe azaḡa vetuḡaziꞌohe,  
\q2 zu zeḡe mariga niduꞌa vetuḡaziꞌohe.   
\q1
\v 51 Aniꞌe ꞌevoꞌa hina haḡai gigiꞌaḡa haḡairo,  
\q2 ebu iniu zeḡeꞌa bare nize mae iteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa hegoze ḡururuziro.   
\q1
\v 52 Aniꞌe kini niduꞌa zeḡe ehoro habaꞌanonoꞌo hegoze vaḡiziro,  
\q2 u iniu zeḡeꞌa bare nize mae ovoeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mae ḡihiziro.   
\q1
\v 53 Aniꞌa vinizeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazao ḡau manoḡa iriꞌavoniro,  
\q2 u maꞌora azaḡaꞌe ꞌevoreze isoḡa tuḡuze buziro.   
\q1
\v 54 Aniꞌa ane mone azaḡa vetuḡaziꞌuma rae ḡoitorirotaꞌaꞌe zamaradu  
\q2 ane tuḡure azaḡa, Isaraela azaḡa danaziro.   
\q1
\v 55 Badiꞌaꞌa emeḡe vouḡa ziroteꞌe idunaḡano,  
\q2 Aberahamo zu ane mariga vetuḡaziro ebu vetuḡaziꞌuma onamo tuḡutuḡu.”   
\p
\v 56 Ebu Mariaꞌe Elizabeta teite bato uḡidu heuḡa radadu neḡa bare onamiro.   
\s1 Ioane Babatisoꞌa Fureraro  
\p
\v 57 Elizabetaꞌa ene fureniteꞌe madaḡa meirotene, ubuga fureniro.  
\v 58 Ebu neḡa azaḡa zu nabuga duḡuruꞌa Elizabeta mazao Badiꞌaꞌa manoḡa fureniroteꞌe egadu ane teite matuꞌiro.  
\v 59 Eꞌe enogano mada fuꞌo uḡidu fare meirotene, ze tahiꞌa ahiꞌa rana iḡuri haḡaihi radu ariro, ebu tahiꞌa niḡaꞌe moga Zekaria ni turahihi reiro.  
\v 60 Rehano viꞌaniꞌa ziro, “Mene, ani niꞌe Ioane rae turahiꞌuma.”  
\v 61 Ebu zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Ḡae nabugo niduꞌa boꞌaḡano eꞌeguḡa niḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.”  
\v 62 Ebu ze ꞌevore hina moga ḡoreniro, “Ḡa niḡa iniu turahihi raꞌohe?”  
\v 63 Ebu Zekariaꞌa ire rafaḡa umizadu eꞌe rana ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “Niḡaꞌe Ioane.” Ze eꞌe horonirotene, zeḡe niduꞌa zaguzagaro.  
\v 64 Eꞌe madaḡano Zekaria hebeꞌa ꞌai zogone nahanadu ḡoerirotene agoḡaniꞌa buaro, ebu Badiꞌa niguniro.  
\v 65 Ne azaḡa niduꞌa eꞌe horonadu riharo. Ebu Iudea habaꞌano guniꞌa neḡa azaḡa niduꞌa zuni eꞌe hariḡa niduꞌa igiro.  
\v 66 Eꞌe igiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe eꞌe moneo zamaradu ꞌahige rae ḡadimutitiro, “Tahiꞌa ꞌadiꞌe zama moneo vaze nagiga reꞌuma?” Mazaḡa Zuhiꞌa Boro gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa hube hune ane mazao radiunu.   
\s1 Zekariaꞌa Badiꞌa Ḡoere rae Fureniro  
\p
\v 67 Eꞌe enogano Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa Ioane moga Zekaria zamao iriꞌavadu Zekariaꞌa Badiꞌa ḡoere rae fureniro,   
\q1
\v 68 “Zuhiꞌa Boro Isaraela azaḡa Badiꞌa nigunihi.  
\q2 Mazaḡa aniꞌe Isaraela azaḡa vaḡe aradu haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo bohaze buziro.   
\q1
\v 69 Badiꞌaꞌe ane tuḡure vazeḡa Davida marigaonoꞌo  
\q2 emeḡe ḡabofiteꞌe vazeḡa inaraḡa tuḡuniro.   
\q1
\v 70 Ibite madaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa ane peroveta azaḡa zaḡoḡaonoꞌo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudaroteꞌe teige,   
\q1
\v 71 aniꞌe emeḡe agire azaḡa mazaonoꞌo,  
\q2 ebu emeḡe heꞌeheꞌefeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ꞌevoreonoꞌo ḡabofiꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 72 Aniꞌe vouḡafe vetuḡaziro,  
\q2 ebu zeḡe teite ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa zaḡoḡa zamariro.   
\q1
\v 73 Aꞌe vouḡafe Aberahamo mazao ḡoere rinede tiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa.   
\q1
\v 74 ꞌOugadu aniꞌe emeḡe agire azaḡa ꞌevoreonoꞌo ḡabofiro,  
\q2 ebu emeꞌa mene rihauꞌenaꞌa, ane veize gauifine danafiro.   
\q1
\v 75 Eꞌanoꞌo emeḡe ḡabone niduꞌa zamaḡano emeꞌe Badiꞌa ubumao zaḡozaḡiꞌuma,  
\q2 ebu duduḡano radiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 76 Ebu Zekariaꞌa ubuga niro,  
\q1 “Eḡe ubude, ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa Hitaga Hune veize gaueꞌeteꞌe peroveta vazeḡa rae huḡadiꞌuma.  
\q2 Mazaḡa ḡaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro ibi ruhiboga veize ane zamao onamiꞌuma,   
\q1
\v 77 ebu vaze haḡai sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡabone ziniꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa  
\q2 Badiꞌa mone azaḡa ihoziꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 78 Emeḡe Badiꞌaꞌe vetuḡafiꞌohe zu emeḡe zamare borofeꞌohe.  
\q2 Adureonoꞌo madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe teige, aniꞌa emeḡe mazao vaze ꞌahoga tuḡuniꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 79 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa uzabo zu rune zauhaḡa zamaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa agaḡa ziniꞌuma,  
\q2 ebu uniho manoḡa ibiḡano odafe ibitofiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 80 Ene aꞌe bororaro ebu vine moneo inariro. Aniꞌe haba bohaꞌano radiro, onamo hunio Isaraela azaḡa mazao fureraro.   
\c 2  
\s1 Iesuꞌa Fureraro  
\r (Mataio 1:18-25)  
\p
\v 1 Eꞌe madaḡano Roma kiniḡa niḡaꞌe Augusto. Aniꞌe ane gau azaḡa mazao ḡoere ꞌahi tuḡuriro, “Roma habaꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa nize moꞌi.”  
\v 2 Nize maꞌeteꞌe gauḡa ꞌahiꞌe Kurenioꞌe Siria habaꞌa gavana vazeḡa reiroteꞌe madaḡano ḡae ibiꞌano haḡairo.  
\v 3 Eꞌanoꞌo vaze niduꞌaꞌe nize zounifine, zeḡezeḡe haba onamiro.   
\p
\v 4 Iosefaꞌe Galilea habaꞌano Nazareta neḡano radiunu. Aniꞌe Davida mariga. Betelehema neḡaꞌe Davida neḡa ꞌahine, aniꞌe Iudea habaꞌano Betelehema neḡa onamiro.  
\v 5 Iosefaꞌe Maria teite iraꞌauniro, eꞌanoꞌo Maria teite nize zounoga veize onamiro. Mariaꞌe ahiꞌeta.  
\v 6 Ze eꞌea radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano, ene fureniteꞌe madaḡa meiro.  
\v 7 Ebu Mariaꞌe ubuga ibiꞌa fureniro zu dabua hina ꞌumadu boromakau ḡubuneꞌeteꞌe siuvaḡa zamaḡano ufi tiro, mazaḡa iꞌudo ne zamaḡano zeḡe bazuni habaꞌaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.   
\s1 Mamoe Taufeꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa zu Badiꞌa Tuḡure Viga  
\p
\v 8 Eꞌe oheꞌano mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Betelehema neḡa uhiḡano haba bohaꞌano radiuꞌenaꞌa, mamoe taufinu.  
\v 9 Ebu Zuhiꞌa Boro tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa zeḡe mazao fureraro. Ebu Zuhiꞌa Boro agaḡaniꞌa agazirotene, zeꞌe rihau rudaro.  
\v 10 Rehano tuḡure viganiꞌa ziro, “Ago rihanoꞌi. E hari manoḡa zae ihozoga radu areha. Vaze niduꞌa eꞌe igine matuꞌiꞌuma.  
\v 11 Izidi Davida neḡano zae ḡaboziteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa zae veize fureraro. Aniꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro Keriso.\f + \fr 2:11 \fqa Mesia \f*  
\v 12 Za ene guraḡa dabua hina ꞌumadu boromakau ḡubuneꞌeteꞌe siuvaḡa zamaḡano bazunoga horonine, aniꞌe Keriso rae ederiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 13 Tabara adureonoꞌo tuḡure viga ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa fureranadu tuḡure viga eꞌe teite Badiꞌa niguneꞌenaꞌa, ꞌahige rae reiro,   
\q1
\v 14 “Hitana huneoꞌe Badiꞌa ni mae ḡihineꞌohe,  
\q2 ebu rahaoꞌe Badiꞌa matuꞌohauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano uniho manofeꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 15 Tuḡure viga niduꞌa mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa muhizadu adure itirotene, mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare neneḡaniro, “Eme Betelehema neḡa onamadu Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa edemafeateꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa hudanateꞌe ḡianihi.” \fig Tuḡure viga ḡuḡuvaḡa|src="CN01621B.TIF" size="col" ref="2:8, 13" \fig*   
\p
\v 16 Eꞌanoꞌo ze ḡarihe Betelehema neḡa onamiro. ꞌOugadu ze Maria zu Iosefa ohoziro, ebu boromakau ḡubuneꞌeteꞌe siuvaḡa zamaḡano bazeꞌeteꞌe tahiꞌaḡa komeꞌa zuni horoniro.  
\v 17 Ze tahiꞌa komeꞌa horonirotene, ani moneo tuḡure viganiꞌa ḡoeriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ihoziro.  
\v 18 Ḡoere eꞌe igiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa uꞌano zaguzagau ḡouriro.  
\v 19 Rehano Mariaꞌe eꞌe hariḡa niduꞌa mae zamao ofadu zamare radiunu.  
\v 20 Mamoe taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe tuḡure viganiꞌa ziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa fureraroteꞌe horoniro zu igiro. Eꞌanoꞌo ze Badiꞌa ni mae ḡihineꞌenaꞌa zu niguneꞌenaꞌa, bare oname ḡouriro.   
\s1 Niḡaꞌe Iesu rae Turahiro  
\p
\v 21 Mada fuꞌo uḡidu fare meirotene, tahiꞌa ꞌadiꞌe ahiꞌa rana iḡuri haḡairo, ebu niḡaꞌe Iesu rae turahiro. Aꞌe, viꞌa ꞌizema ene tougano tuḡure viganiꞌa haroteꞌe niḡa.   
\s1 Iesu Ierusalema Zamahu Itiro  
\p
\v 22 Mariaꞌa Iesu fureniroteꞌe enogano, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa idunaḡano Iosefa zu Mariaꞌe ahirize deheneꞌeteꞌe madaḡa meiro. ꞌOugirotene, ze Iesu Zuhiꞌa Boro zamao ohonifine, Ierusalema zamahu itiro.  
\v 23 Mazaḡa Zuhiꞌa Boro goro ḡoeꞌano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “Ene ohozeḡa ibiꞌa niduꞌaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro veize zaḡozaḡoziꞌuma zu ḡaboneze Zuhiꞌa Boro haꞌuma.”  
\v 24 Ebu Zuhiꞌa Boro goro ḡoeꞌano, “Tubugo niniḡa aheu ga nini komeḡa aheu Badiꞌa dibuꞌohaꞌuma,” rae reiroteꞌe idunaḡano haḡaifine, ze Iesu zamahanadu Ierusalema itiro.   
\p
\v 25 Eꞌe madaḡano Ierusalemao vaze ꞌahoga, niḡa Simeonaꞌa radiunu. Aniꞌe haḡaiḡa duduḡa zu Badiꞌa ḡoere hegoteꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Aniꞌe Isaraela azaḡa ḡaboziteꞌe vazeḡa guhine radiunu, ebu Vine Zaḡoḡaꞌe ani teite radiunu.  
\v 26 Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa Simeona ibite ꞌahige rae ihoniro, “Ḡaꞌe mene rudaꞌuma, onamo Keriso horoniꞌuma.”  
\v 27 Ebu Simeonaꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ibitohanadu kuru neḡa diuḡiro. ꞌOugirotene, Iesu viꞌa moganiꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa idunaḡano haḡaoga veize eneze Iesuꞌe zamahu diuḡiro.  
\v 28 Ebu Simeonaꞌa ꞌevoꞌa hina Iesu mae ohanadu Badiꞌa niguniro,   
\q1
\v 29 “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡaꞌa ibite ḡoitoriroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa idunaḡano,  
\q2 izidi ḡaeꞌa eḡe, ḡae tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe zama roḡeḡaheta runeo tuḡuhe onamiꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 30 Mazaḡa e ubumahe hina ḡaeꞌa tuḡunadu vaze ḡaboziteꞌe vazeḡa horoniro.   
\q2
\v 31 Aniꞌe ḡaeꞌa vaze niduꞌa zamao ruhibiro,   
\q1
\v 32 zu aniꞌe Iuda mene azaḡa Badiꞌa ihoziteꞌe agaḡa.  
\q2 Ani uꞌano, ḡae mone azaḡa, Isaraela azaḡa nize mae ḡihiniꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 33 Iesu viꞌa mogaꞌe Simeonaꞌa Iesu moneo reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa igirotene zaguzagaro.  
\v 34 Ebu Simeonaꞌa ze manohuga hidifine kuraro, ebu viꞌa Maria niro, “Tahiꞌa ꞌadiꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ohoniro. Isaraela azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ani mene mae ḡihiniro ꞌahine, ḡabone ibiḡanonoꞌo buaꞌuma. U vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ani mae ḡihinadu ḡabone ibiḡano edaꞌuma. Ebu vazeꞌa ani uꞌano Badiꞌaꞌa gaueꞌeteꞌe horoniꞌuma, rehano vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ani rae sausauniꞌuma.  
\v 35 Eꞌe uꞌano, vaze zamaroneze sauꞌa niduꞌa fureraꞌuma. Ebu tahiꞌa ꞌahi uꞌano, benisiꞌa ḡouꞌiꞌeteꞌe teige, zamaḡoꞌe adudaꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 36 Peroveta roḡaeḡa ꞌahoga, niḡa Ana zuni Ierusalemao radiunu. Aniꞌe Fanuela aboḡa ebu Asere urabo roḡaeḡa. Aniꞌe roḡae ufeta vouḡa. Ani hahuradu muri fuꞌo aheu fare enogano iꞌaniꞌa rudaro.  
\v 37 Ebu ḡozoba radiu onamo izidi muriḡa 84 ꞌai meiro. Aniꞌe iḡaiḡa kuru neḡa onaminu, ebu ohere zu madai ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡeꞌenaꞌa, Badiꞌa mazao kuraunu.  
\v 38 Simeonaꞌe Maria zu Iosefa teite ḡoereꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano, Anaꞌa zeḡe vaḡe aradu Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi rae reiro. Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa Ierusalemaꞌe agire azaḡa mazaonoꞌo bohane buniteꞌe madaḡa guhineꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazao tahiꞌa ꞌadi moneo ihoziro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Nazareta Neḡa Bariro  
\p
\v 39 Iosefa zu Mariaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro goro goeꞌa idunaḡano Ierusalemao gau niduꞌa hauḡirotene, ze Galilea habaꞌa onamadu zeḡe ne Nazaretao bare feuriro.  
\v 40 Tahiꞌa Iesu ꞌai bororaro zu inariro. Ebu aniꞌe tahiꞌa huhuzaḡa reiro, zu Badiꞌaꞌa ani mazao manoḡa fureniro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Kuru Neḡano Ḡoeriro  
\p
\v 41 Muri iḡaiḡa Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa madaḡano Iesu viꞌa mogaꞌe Ierusalema itido.  
\v 42 Iesuꞌe muri gaubanana aheu fare meirotene, ze ꞌouge haḡaidoteꞌe teige, Mui eꞌe auḡifine Ierusalema itiro.  
\v 43 Ebu Mui hauḡadu Iesu viꞌa mogaꞌe neze onamirotene, Iesuꞌe Ierusalemao radiro, rehano viꞌa mogaꞌe mene ederiro.  
\v 44 Zeꞌe ꞌahige rae zamariro, “Iesuꞌe vaze ḡunuḡano onameꞌohe.” Ze ibio onameꞌenaꞌa mada tiba vitinirotene, zeḡe nego nabudi boꞌaḡano Iesu vaḡiro.  
\v 45 Rehano ze ani mene horonadu ani vaḡeꞌenaꞌa Ierusalema bare itiro.  
\v 46 Ebu mada uḡidu enogano kuru neḡano Iesu horoniro. Aniꞌe Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teite ehoradu zeḡe ḡoere iginu zu ḡadimuzininu.  
\v 47 Ani ḡoere igiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe ane edeḡa zu aniꞌa naenaeziroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa uꞌano zaguzagaro.  
\v 48 Viꞌa moganiꞌa ani horonadu zeḡe zuni zaguzagaro. Viꞌaniꞌa niro, “Ubude, nougadu ꞌougeha? Mogo zu eḡeꞌa zamafe aduduꞌenaꞌa, ḡa vaḡeha.”  
\v 49 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Za nougadu e vaḡeha? E eḡe Mama neo raditaꞌaꞌe za mene ederirohe?”  
\v 50 Rehano viꞌa mogaꞌe aniꞌa nagini reirotaꞌaꞌe mene ederiro.   
\p
\v 51 Eꞌe enogano Iesuꞌe zeḡe teite Nazareta neḡa ovoiro ebu zeḡe ḡoere egoziniro. Viꞌaꞌe Iesu mazao fureraroteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa ane zamao zamare radiunu.  
\v 52 Iesu zamarone huhuzaḡa zu ahiꞌaniꞌa bororaro, ebu Badiꞌa zu vazeꞌa ani zamare borofiro. \fig Iesuꞌa ihore azaḡa teite ḡoeriro|src="CN01647B.TIF" size="col" ref="2:46-50" \fig*   
\c 3  
\s1 Ioaneꞌa Iesu Ibi Ruhiniro  
\r (Mataio 3:1-12; Mareko 1:1-8; Ioane 1:19-28)  
\p
\v 1 Roma kiniḡa Tiberioꞌe Roma habaꞌa niduꞌa kiniḡa radu muri 15 zuhiꞌazinu. Eꞌe madaḡano Pontio Pilato'e Iudea habaꞌa gavanaḡa, Heroda'e Galilea habaꞌa kiniḡa negoḡa Filipi'e Iturea zu Tarakonito habaꞌa kiniḡa, ebu Rusaniaꞌe Abilene habaꞌa kiniḡa reiro.  
\v 2 U Anasi zu Kaiafaꞌe dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihi'aḡaḡihiꞌaḡa reiro. E'e madaḡano Zekaria ubuga Ioane'a haba boha'ano radiunu, ebu Badiꞌa ḡoere'a ane mazao buaro.  
\v 3 Ani'e Ioridana vuḡa uhiḡano haba'ahaba'a nidu'a onamadu ꞌahige rae haramiro, “Haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihuradu babatiso moꞌi! ꞌOugine, Badi'a'a haḡaize sau'a rae modiꞌuma!”   
\p
\v 4 Peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaꞌa rae fureniroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa mirihiroteꞌe bukaḡano ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa haba boha'ano ḡihau ḡoere'ohe, raenaꞌa,  
\q1 'Zuhiꞌa Boro veize ibi ruhiboꞌi,  
\q2 ani veize ibi mae dudunoꞌi.   
\q1
\v 5 Do'oḡa nidu'a tuniꞌuma,  
\q2 ebu maḡa boro zu maḡa zuhu'a nidu'a mae sebaniꞌuma.  
\q1 Ibi beꞌoḡabeꞌoḡa duduniꞌuma,  
\q2 ebu ibi sauꞌasauꞌa fainiꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 6 Ebu vaze nidu'a Badiꞌa'a zeḡe ḡaboze'ete'e horoni'uma.'”\x + \xo 3:4-6 \xt Isaia 40:3-5 \x*   
\p
\v 7 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Ioane mazaonoꞌo babatiso mouga radu Ioane vaḡe arirotene, aniꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe Zarama ubugaubuga! Iniuꞌa zae mazao, 'Badiꞌa zama ḡugiꞌanonoꞌo ferau muhinoꞌi,' rae reiro? Aꞌe mene idaḡa!  
\v 8 Rehano ibite haḡaize sau'anono'o ḡihuniroteꞌe haḡaiḡa izidi furenoꞌi. Ebu ꞌahige ago zamaroꞌi, 'Emeꞌe Aberahamo mariga, eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa emeḡe mazao mene maḡuniꞌuma.' Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Badi'a'a hadi ꞌadi hina Aberahamo mariga haḡaoga zuni idaḡa.  
\v 9 Ḡiro 'ai ire taigano amahi tiro. Eꞌanoꞌo huga manoḡa mene iniꞌeteꞌe ireḡa niduꞌa'e udi higonadu ire rogao feuniꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 10 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡani'a Ioane ḡadiniro, “Eme nougine manoḡa?”  
\v 11 Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Iniu dabuaḡa aheu ro'idene tibaꞌe dabuaḡa o'o'a vazeḡa hano'i. Ebu iniu ogomuḡeta roꞌidene vinineꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa teite ḡahugotito'i.”   
\p
\v 12 Takesi azaḡa zuni babatiso mouga veize aradu Ioane ḡadiniro, “Ihore vazeḡa, eme nougine manoḡa?”  
\v 13 Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Takesi ufoꞌidene, gavamaniꞌa reiroteꞌe idunaḡano daꞌo ufo'i. Ago vitau ufoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 14 Ebu uti azaḡani'a zuni ḡadiniro, “Eme nougine manoḡa?” Ani'a naenaeziro, “Vaze hadi ago meize tauḡo'i, ebu veꞌoḡa oꞌoꞌa vazeḡa kotao ago ohonoꞌi. Zae gau hadiḡa daꞌo madu matu'o'i.”   
\p
\v 15 Vaze ḡehaḡaꞌe Kerisoꞌa\f + \fr 3:15 \fqa Mesia \f* ariteꞌe guhininu, eꞌanoꞌo zeꞌe, “Ioaneꞌe Keriso gaogi,” rae zamariro.  
\v 16 Eꞌanoꞌo Ioane'a zeḡe nidu'a naenaeziro, “E'e vu hina babatisoziꞌohe. Rehano ariteꞌe vazeḡa'e gigi'aḡa boro hune. Aniꞌe eḡe vitihoga, zu eḡe'a ani tamaka miniḡa fuhiꞌeꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa vazeḡa rae rouga zuni mene idaḡa. Ani'e Vine Zaḡoḡa zu ire roga hina babatisozi'uma.  
\v 17 Maho hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡano\f + \fr 3:17 \fqa Vuidi hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡano \f* vazeꞌa kari hina rouḡa tenadu maho huꞌiꞌohe. Ebu iguḡa manoneꞌohe ebu meba hare deheneꞌohe. Ebu hugaꞌe nuꞌonadu suaba zamaḡano tiꞌohe, rehano iguḡaꞌe mene vidauꞌeteꞌe ire rogao hufi haoneꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 18 Ebu Ioane'a ḡoere ḡehaḡa nunu hina iraduguzeꞌenaꞌa, hari manoḡa haramoziro.  
\v 19 Rehano Ioane'a Galilea habaꞌa kiniḡa Heroda roniro, mazaḡa Herodaꞌe negoḡa inuga Herodia meiro zu haḡai sau'a nunu haḡairo.  
\v 20 Ebu Heroda'e haḡaiḡa sauꞌa eꞌe nidu'a ranao ꞌahoga ragatiro, mazaḡa Ioane ḡu'a neḡano mae ohoniro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Babatiso Meiro  
\r (Mataio 3:13-17; Mareko 1:9-11)  
\p
\v 21 Ioaneꞌe ꞌizema ḡuꞌa neḡano mae ohonogano, ani vaze nidu'a babatisoziro ebu Iesu zuni babatisoniro. Ebu Iesuꞌa kurau'eteꞌe zamaḡano adure'a bohataro,  
\v 22 ebu Vine Zaḡoḡani'a Tubugo niniḡa teige ane rana kami ovairo. Ebu ago ꞌahoganiꞌa adureonoꞌo ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ḡa'e eḡe zamarone ubude. Eḡeꞌa ḡae mazao matu'e rudau'ohe.”   
\s1 Iesu Mariga Duḡuru  
\r (Mataio 1:1-17)  
\p
\v 23 Iesu muriꞌe 30 reirotene, ani gauḡa ḡadaheniro. Vazeꞌa ani'e Iosefa ubuga rae zamariro.  
\li1 Iosefa'e Heli ubuga,  
\v 24 Heli'e Matata ubuga,  
\li1 Matata'e Levi ubuga, Levi'e Meleki ubuga,  
\li1 Meleki'e Ianai ubuga, Ianai'e Iosefa ubuga,   
\li1
\v 25 Iosefa'e Matataia ubuga, Matataiaꞌe Amosa ubuga,  
\li1 Amosaꞌe Nahumu ubuga, Nahumuꞌe Eseli ubuga,  
\li1 Eseliꞌe Nagai ubuga,  
\v 26 Nagaiꞌe Mahata ubuga,  
\li1 Mahataꞌe Matataia ubuga, Matataiaꞌe Semeina ubuga,  
\li1 Semeinaꞌe Ioseka ubuga, Iosekaꞌe Ioda ubuga,   
\li1
\v 27 Iodaꞌe Ioanana ubuga, Ioananaꞌe Resa ubuga,  
\li1 Resaꞌe Zerubabele ubuga, Zerubabeleꞌe Sealetiele ubuga,  
\li1 Sealetieleꞌe Neri ubuga,  
\v 28 Neriꞌe Meleki ubuga,  
\li1 Melekiꞌe Adi ubuga, Adiꞌe Kosama ubuga,  
\li1 Kosamaꞌe Elamadama ubuga, Elamadamaꞌe Ere ubuga,   
\li1
\v 29 Ereꞌe Iosua ubuga, Iosuaꞌe Eliezere ubuga,  
\li1 Eliezereꞌe Iorima ubuga, Iorimaꞌe Matata ubuga,  
\li1 Matataꞌe Levi ubuga,  
\v 30 Leviꞌe Simeona ubuga,  
\li1 Simeonaꞌe Iuda ubuga, Iudaꞌe Iosefa ubuga,  
\li1 Iosefaꞌe Ionama ubuga, Ionamaꞌe Eliakimi ubuga,   
\li1
\v 31 Eliakimiꞌe Melea ubuga, Meleaꞌe Mena ubuga,  
\li1 Menaꞌe Matata ubuga, Matataꞌe Natana ubuga,  
\li1 Natanaꞌe Davida ubuga,  
\v 32 Davidaꞌe Iese ubuga,  
\li1 Ieseꞌe Obeda ubuga, Obedaꞌe Boazi ubuga,  
\li1 Boaziꞌe Salamona ubuga, Salamonaꞌe Nasona ubuga,   
\li1
\v 33 Nasonaꞌe Aminadaba ubuga, Aminadabaꞌe Adamina ubuga,  
\li1 Adaminaꞌe Areni ubuga, Areniꞌe Hezarona ubuga,  
\li1 Hezaronaꞌe Pereze ubuga, Perezeꞌe Iuda ubuga,   
\li1
\v 34 Iudaꞌe Iakobo ubuga, Iakoboꞌe Isako ubuga,  
\li1 Isakoꞌe Aberahamo ubuga, Aberahamoꞌe Tera ubuga,  
\li1 Teraꞌe Nahoro ubuga,  
\v 35 Nahoroꞌe Seruga ubuga,  
\li1 Serugaꞌe Reu ubuga, Reuꞌe Pelega ubuga,  
\li1 Pelegaꞌe Ebere ubuga, Ebereꞌe Sela ubuga,   
\li1
\v 36 Selaꞌe Kainana ubuga, Kainanaꞌe Afasada ubuga,  
\li1 Afasadaꞌe Semu ubuga, Semuꞌe Noa ubuga,  
\li1 Noaꞌe Lameka ubuga,  
\v 37 Lamekaꞌe Metusela ubuga,  
\li1 Metuselaꞌe Enoka ubuga, Enokaꞌe Iareda ubuga,  
\li1 Iaredaꞌe Mahalalela ubuga, Mahalalelaꞌe Kainana ubuga,   
\li1
\v 38 Kainanaꞌe Enosi ubuga, Enosiꞌe Seta ubuga,  
\li1 Setaꞌe Adamu ubuga, Adamuꞌe Badiꞌa ubuga.   
\c 4  
\s1 Diaboloꞌa Iesu Tuhune Nuriro  
\r (Mataio 4:1-11; Mareko 1:12-13)  
\p
\v 1 Iesuꞌe Ioridana vuḡa mode iḡunirotene, Vine Zaḡoḡani'a ane rana iriꞌavadu Iesu tutune haba boha'a onamiro.  
\v 2 E'ea mada 40 zamaḡano Diaboloꞌa Iesu tuhune nuriro. E'e madaḡano ani ogomu 'ahoga mene aro, eꞌanoꞌo mada ḡonagano ani vinine runiro.   
\p
\v 3 Ebu Diaboloꞌa Iesu niro, “Ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga roꞌidene, hadi ꞌadi mazao ꞌahige noꞌi, 'Ḡihuradu ꞌuvahu odogano roꞌi.'”  
\v 4 Iesu'a naenaeniro, “Mene, Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Vaze'e ꞌuvahu odogano da'o mene ḡabode radi'uma.'\x + \xo 4:4 \xt Goro 8:3\x*”   
\p
\v 5 Ebu Diaboloꞌa Iesu hitaga haba'a tutune itadu zogone kini'a zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe habaꞌahabaꞌa niduꞌa ihoniro.  
\v 6 Ebu aniꞌa Iesu niro, “Eḡeꞌa haba niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe gigi'aḡa zu ḡau naeḡa boroboro niduꞌa ḡae ḡani'uma. Aꞌe eḡe iniroteꞌe ḡauḡa 'ahine, eḡe'a urateꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga hau tauḡogaꞌe idaḡa.  
\v 7 E'ano'o ḡaeꞌa eḡe mazao kuraune, eꞌe nidu'a ḡaniꞌuma.”  
\v 8 Iesu'a naenaeniro, “Mene, Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro,  
\q1 'Zuhiꞌa Boro ḡae Badiꞌa mazao da'o kurano'i,  
\q2 zu ane veize daꞌo gauoꞌi.'\x + \xo 4:8 \xt Goro 6:13\x*”   
\p
\v 9 Ebu Diabolo'a Iesu Ierusalema tutune onamiro ebu kuru neḡa hitaga huneo ohonadu niro, “Ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa Ubuga ro'idene, ꞌadaono'o rafato'i.  
\v 10 Mazaḡa Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro,  
\q1 'Badi'aꞌa ḡaꞌe faine duguoga veize  
\q2 ane tuḡure vigaviga ḡae vaḡe tuḡuziꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 11 Ze'a ꞌevoreze hina ḡae mae ḡihi'i'uma ꞌahine,  
\q2 odaḡoꞌe hadio mene tutuhaꞌuma.'\x + \xo 4:10-11 \xt Salamo 91:11-12\x*”   
\p
\v 12 Rehano Iesu'a naenaeniro, “Mene, Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro ḡae Badiꞌa ago tuhuno'i.'\x + \xo 4:12 \xt Goro 6:16 \x*”   
\p
\v 13 Diaboloꞌa Iesu tuhunoga niduꞌa hauḡirotene, mada manoḡa 'ahogano bare tuhuniꞌuma radu muhine iḡuniro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Galilea Habaꞌano Gauḡa Ḡadaheniro  
\r (Mataio 4:12-17; Mareko 1:14-15)  
\p
\v 14 Iesuꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡa gigi'aḡani'a iri'avonadu Galilea habaꞌa bare onamiro. Ebu ane hariꞌe haba nidu'a zamaḡano bororaro.  
\v 15 Aniꞌe Iuda azaḡa nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano ihoziro, ebu vaze niduꞌaꞌe ani niguniro.   
\s1 Nazareta Azaḡaniꞌa Iesu Hezahoharo  
\r (Mataio 13:53-58; Mareko 6:1-6)  
\p
\v 16 Ebu Iesuꞌe Nazareta neḡa onamiro. Eꞌe neḡaꞌe ane'a bororarote'e neḡa. Bana Madaḡano ane'a iḡaiḡa haḡainute teige, nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano diuḡi onamiro. Ebu Buka Zaḡoḡa meꞌodoga radu iḡune edaro.  
\v 17 Ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa peroveta vazeḡa Isaiaꞌa mirihiroteꞌe soꞌa ḡuaḡa mae haro. Ebu Iesuꞌa eꞌe vavaꞌadu meꞌoditeꞌe ḡoeꞌa horoniro. Aꞌe ꞌahige rae mirihiro,   
\q1
\v 18 “Zuhiꞌa Boro Vigaꞌe eḡe vaḡe ovairo.  
\q2 Zahara azaḡa mazao hari manoḡa haramoga veize  
\q2 aniꞌa eḡe ohohiro.  
\q1 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa tuḡuhadu eḡeꞌa ꞌahige rae fureneꞌohe, 'Agire ḡauḡaniꞌa batuziroteꞌe azaḡa fuhiꞌe ahetiꞌuma,  
\q2 ebu ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa raꞌanoziniꞌuma,  
\q2 ebu aduganiꞌa ḡahiziroteꞌe azaḡa adugazeonoꞌo mae bohaziꞌuma,   
\q1
\v 19 ebu izidi muriḡaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ane mone azaḡa ḡaboziteꞌe madaḡa reꞌuma.'”\x + \xo 4:18-19 \xt Isaia 61:1-2 \x*   
\p
\v 20 Iesuꞌa soꞌa ḡuaḡa eꞌe ꞌuadu nuꞌonuꞌo neḡa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa bare haro ebu ehoriro. Nu'onu'o neḡa zamaḡano vaze niduꞌa ani ḡiaḡianiro.  
\v 21 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadahe ziro, “Zaꞌa egateꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡano ḡoeꞌa ꞌai izidi ꞌada hudaneha.”  
\v 22 Zeḡe niduꞌa ani hebeonoꞌo buaroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa manoḡa egadu zaguzagaro. Rehano ze ꞌahige rae reiro, “Aniꞌe Iosefa ubuga, oꞌehe?”   
\p
\v 23 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “E edeḡa, zaꞌe eḡe mazao iradugu ḡoeꞌa ꞌahi reꞌuma, 'Gohe vazeḡa, ibite geno ḡae bare fainoꞌi.' Ebu eḡe bare ihiꞌuma, 'Emeꞌa igiroteꞌe teige, ḡaeꞌa Kaperanauma neḡano haḡairoteꞌe haḡai gigiꞌaḡa ḡae haba ꞌadao zuni haḡaoꞌi.'”  
\v 24 Ebu aniꞌa bare ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, peroveta vazeḡaꞌe ane haba azaḡaniꞌa mene mae ḡihineꞌohe.  
\v 25 Rehano eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe. Elia madaḡano muri uḡidu zu ḡahaꞌa zamaḡano adure ꞌuadu iruguꞌa mene ruꞌaro, eꞌanoꞌo Isaraela habaꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano zahara boroꞌa buaro. Eꞌe madaḡano ḡozoba ḡehaḡaniꞌa radiunu.  
\v 26 Rehano Elia'e Badiꞌa'a Isaraela habaꞌano ḡozoba ḡehaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga mazao mene tuḡuniro, rehano Sidono haba'a uhiḡano Sarepata neḡano radiunuteꞌe ḡozobaḡa 'ahoga mazao daꞌo tuḡuniro.  
\v 27 Ebu peroveta vazeḡa Elisa madaḡano Isaraela habaꞌano refera azaḡa ḡehaḡaniꞌa radiunu. Rehano zeḡe boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga zuni mene fainiro, rehano Siria habaꞌa vazeḡa, niḡa Naamana da'o fainiro.”   
\p
\v 28 Iesuꞌa ꞌouge reirotene, nu'onu'o neḡa zamaḡano vaze nidu'a maḡune rudaro.  
\v 29 Zeḡe nidu'a iḡunadu e'e haba'anono'o ani tuḡune vaḡiniro. Ebu dofarao duine feunoga radu neze ogorarote'e maḡa komeꞌa hitaga tutune itiro.  
\v 30 Rehano Iesuꞌa vaze ḡunuḡano onamadu ane ibio onamiro.   
\s1 Iesu'a Vine Sau'a Hegone Buniro  
\r (Mareko 1:21-28)  
\p
\v 31 Ebu Iesuꞌa Galilea haba'ano Kaperanauma ovoadu Bana Madaḡano nu'onu'o neḡano vaze ihoziro.  
\v 32 Zeꞌa ane ihoreḡa igirotene zaguzagaro, mazaḡa aniꞌa Badiꞌa gigiꞌaḡa hina ihoziro.  
\v 33 Eꞌe madaḡano vine sau'aḡeta vazeḡa ꞌahogaꞌe nu'onu'o neḡano radiunu, ebu agoḡa boro hina ḡoeriro,  
\v 34 “A! Nazareta vazeḡa Iesu! Ḡa emeḡe mazao nougihi raꞌohe? Ḡa eme ruifoga radu arahe? E edeḡa ḡaꞌe iniu. Ḡa'e Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ariroteꞌe vazeḡa zaḡoḡa!”  
\v 35 Iesu'a vine sau'a roniro, “Hezo'a! Vaze e'e mazaono'o buanoꞌi!” Ebu vine sau'ani'a vaze nidu'a boꞌaḡano vaze e'e mae rahao higonadu buau dauḡiro. Rehano vaze eꞌe mene sausauniro.   
\p
\v 36 Vaze nidu'a zaguzagaro ebu ze zeḡe'a bare reiro, “Ihoreḡa ꞌadiꞌe nagiga? Aniꞌa Badiꞌa inaraḡa zu gigiꞌaḡa hina vine sauꞌasauꞌa riḡa ziꞌetene, ze egohanadu buauꞌohe!”  
\v 37 Ebu Iesu hariḡaꞌe uhiḡauhiḡa haba'a niduꞌa bororaro.   
\s1 Ugi Azaḡa Ḡehaḡa Faiziro  
\r (Mataio 8:14-17; Mareko 1:29-34)  
\p
\v 38 Iesu'a nu'onu'o neḡa modadu Simona ne onamiro. E'ea Simona emoḡa roḡaeḡaꞌe ahiꞌaniꞌa gigine runiro, eꞌanoꞌo ani fainoga veize ze Iesu uminiro.  
\v 39 Ebu Iesuꞌa ani uhiḡano edanadu ahiꞌa gigiꞌa eꞌe ḡoere riga hina hegone buniro. ꞌOugadu ugi e'e'a ani mazaonoꞌo vaḡiniro, ebu aniꞌa zogone iḡunadu zeḡe veize ogomu ruhibiro.   
\p
\v 40 Mada'a ovoirotene, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ugi nunu meiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa Iesu vaḡe tutuze ariro. Ebu Iesuꞌa ꞌevo'a zeḡe tibatiba rana teadu faiziro.  
\v 41 Ebu vine sau'asau'aniꞌa vaze ḡehaḡa mazaonoꞌo buanadu ꞌahige rae huaro, “Ḡa'e Badiꞌa Ubuga!” Rehano Iesuꞌa ze roziro zu ḡoeroga garariro, mazaḡa ze aniꞌe Keriso\f + \fr 4:41 \fqa Mesia \f* rae ederiro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Harame Ragaviro  
\r (Mareko 1:35-39)  
\p
\v 42 Oherebau uzeuze Iesuꞌa vaze oꞌoꞌa habaꞌa onamiro. ꞌOugadu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesu vaḡiro, ebu aniꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa aradu ani zeḡe mene muhize iḡunoga veize uminiro.  
\v 43 Rehano Iesuꞌa ziro, “E haba nunuo zuni Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo hari manoḡa harame huniꞌuma. Eꞌe uꞌano, eḡe tuḡuhiro.”  
\v 44 Ebu ani Iudea habaꞌano nu'onu'o neḡano harame ragaviro.   
\c 5  
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Tahiꞌatahiꞌa Huziro  
\r (Mataio 4:18-22; Mareko 1:16-20)  
\p
\v 1 Mada ꞌahogano Iesu'a Genesareta\f + \fr 5:1 \fqa Galilea \f* duꞌura genaḡano edanadu Badiꞌa ḡoere haraminu. Ebu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaꞌe ani haramo abitoga veize bibitite ariro.  
\v 2 Iesuꞌa duꞌura genaḡano ḡasi aheu horoniro. Ḡasi azaḡaꞌe buanadu re'evaze vuzuꞌe radiunu.  
\v 3 Iesu'e ḡasi aheu boꞌaḡano Simona ḡasio tiradu uminiro, “Ḡasiḡo hesaonoꞌo tahiḡa duine buno'i.” Ebu Iesuꞌe ḡasi zamaḡano ehoradu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa haramoziro.   
\p
\v 4 Iesuꞌa harame hauḡirotene, Simona niro, “Hoeꞌa mone onamoꞌi, ebu reꞌevaḡo feunadu ḡozone reꞌevanoꞌi.”  
\v 5 Simonaꞌa naenaeniro, “Vaze boro, eme ohere faḡa gau boro haḡaeꞌenaꞌa reꞌeveha, rehano mene maneha. Rehano e ḡae ḡoere mae ḡihinadu reꞌeva feuniꞌuma.”  
\v 6 Ebu zeꞌa reꞌeva feunirotene, reꞌeva zamaḡanoꞌe ḡozone ḡehaḡaniꞌa oḡanadu reꞌevaꞌe zigaro.  
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo zeḡe danazoga veize ꞌevoreze hina ḡasi ꞌahogano nabudize huze zaveziro. Ebu ze aradu ḡasi aheuꞌe ḡozone hina iriꞌavonirotene, ḡasiꞌa nariga zuburiro.   
\p
\v 8 Simona Peteroꞌa eꞌe horonadu Iesu oda babaḡano ḡuḡuriro ebu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, e'e haḡai sauꞌa vazeḡa. Eḡe mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi.”  
\v 9 Simona zu ane teite radiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe zeꞌa maroteꞌe ḡozoneḡaꞌe ḡehaḡa hune radu ufeta zaguzagaroteꞌe uꞌano, ꞌouge reiro.  
\v 10 Zebedeo ubuga aheu, Iakobo zu Ioaneꞌe Petero teite gauinu ꞌahine, zeḡe zuni zaguzagaro. Ebu Iesuꞌa Simona naenaeniro, “Ago rihanoꞌi. Izidionoꞌo onamo mada niduꞌa ḡaꞌe vaze reꞌevaziꞌuma.”  
\v 11 Ebu ze ḡasize hesao hebenadu ḡauze niduꞌa modiro ebu ane hegote onamiro.   
\s1 Refera Vazeḡa Fainiro  
\r (Mataio 8:1-4; Mareko 1:40-45)  
\p
\v 12 Iesuꞌe ne 'ahogano radiuꞌeteꞌea, ahiꞌano referaꞌa iriꞌaviroteꞌe vazeḡa 'ahoganiꞌa ani vaḡe ariro. Ani'a Iesu horonadu ane zamao rahao ḡuḡuriro ebu uminiro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡa uratine, eḡe faihogaꞌe idaḡa.”  
\v 13 Ebu Iesuꞌa ꞌevoꞌa einadu vaze eꞌe oboniro ebu niro, “E urateꞌohe. Ḡaꞌe deheru manoroꞌi!” ꞌOugadu refera eꞌeꞌa zogone manoriro.  
\v 14 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡoere riḡa niro, “Vazeni ꞌahoga ago noꞌi. Rehano dibuꞌo vazeḡa vaḡe onamadu ahiriḡo ihonoꞌi. Ebu ḡaeꞌa deheru manorataꞌaꞌe vazeꞌa ederifine, Moseꞌa reiroteꞌe dibuꞌoḡa mae onamadu Badiꞌa dibuꞌohanoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 15 Rehano Iesu hariꞌe ufeta bororu onamiro. Eꞌanoꞌo vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesu ḡoere abitoga zu ugizeꞌa manoroga veize ane vaḡe ariro.  
\v 16 Rehano Iesuꞌe vaze oꞌoꞌa habaꞌa onamadu eꞌea kuraro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ahiꞌa Mene Haganeꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa Fainiro  
\r (Mataio 9:1-8; Mareko 2:1-12)  
\p
\v 17 Mada ꞌahogano Iesuꞌa harameꞌeteꞌea, Farisea azaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Iesu uhiḡano ehore radiunu. Zeꞌe Galilea zu Iudea habaꞌano ne nunuonoꞌo ebu Ierusalemaonoꞌo ariro. Zuhiꞌa Boro gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa Iesu rana radadu ugi azaḡa faiziro.   
\p
\v 18 Eꞌe madaḡano vaze nuꞌa ahiꞌa mene haganeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahogaꞌe faratao bazune teadu herate onamiro, ebu ne zamaḡa diuḡadu Iesu zamao bazune tihi reiro.  
\v 19 Rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ꞌahine, ze ibihetaonoꞌo odohe diuḡoga mene idararo. Eꞌanoꞌo ze binu hitaga itadu binu mae bohaniro. Ebu binu bohaꞌanonoꞌo ugi vazeḡa farataḡa miniḡa hina ovoe dabanadu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa boꞌaḡano Iesu zamao bazune tiro.  
\v 20 Zeꞌa Iesu mazao fieꞌeteꞌe Iesuꞌa horonadu ugi vazeḡa niro, “Eḡe vaze, ḡae haḡai sauꞌa ꞌai rae modeha.”   
\p
\v 21 ꞌOugirotene, Farisea azaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ꞌahige rae zamariro, “Aniꞌe vaze nagiga radu Badiꞌa rae sausauneꞌohe? Badiꞌaꞌa daꞌo vaze haḡai sauꞌa rae modeꞌohe!”  
\v 22 Iesuꞌe zeḡeꞌa nagini zamareꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederadu ḡadiziro, “Za nougadu zamazeo eḡe ḡoere ꞌadi zamareꞌohe?  
\v 23 Ugi vazeḡa mazao noꞌe ḡoeꞌa nine, ufiḡa? 'Ḡae haḡai sauꞌa ꞌai rae modeha,' rae niꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ga 'Iḡunadu onamoꞌi' rae niꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa?  
\v 24 Rehano Vaze Ubugaꞌe raha ꞌadao haḡai sauꞌa rae modeꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa meirotaꞌaꞌe zaeꞌa ederiꞌuma.” Ebu Iesuꞌa ahiꞌa mene haganeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa niro, “Eḡeꞌa ḡaꞌohe. Iḡunoꞌi ebu farataḡo madu neḡo onamoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 25 Ebu ugi vazeḡa ꞌai zogone zeḡe zamao iḡune edaro, zu aneꞌa baze radiroteꞌe farataḡa madu Badiꞌa niguneꞌenaꞌa, neḡa onamiro.  
\v 26 Vaze niduꞌaꞌe zaguzagaro zu Badiꞌa niguniro. Ebu ze rihau rudauꞌenaꞌa, ꞌahige rae reiro, “Eme izidi haḡai gigiꞌaḡa horoneha!”   
\s1 Levi Huniro  
\r (Mataio 9:9-13; Mareko 2:13-17)  
\p
\v 27 Eꞌe enogano Iesuꞌe haba eꞌe mode iḡuniro, ebu takesi vazeḡa ꞌahoga, niḡa Levi horoniro. Aniꞌe takesi fataḡa uhiḡano ehore radiunu. Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Eḡe hegotoꞌi.”  
\v 28 Ebu Leviꞌa ḡauḡa niduꞌa modadu Iesu hegotiro.   
\p
\v 29 Leviꞌa ane neo Iesu veize mui boro haḡairo. Eꞌea takesi azaḡa ḡehaḡa zu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesu zu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite ogau tiburaro.  
\v 30 Rehano Farisea azaḡa zu zeḡe mone Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌa mazao maḡunadu ziro, “Zaꞌe nougadu takesi azaḡa zu haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa teite ogau tiburuꞌohe?”   
\p
\v 31 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Ugi oꞌoꞌa azaḡaꞌe gohe vazeḡa mene vaḡeꞌohe, rehano ugi azaḡaꞌe gohe vazeḡa vaḡeꞌohe.  
\v 32 Eꞌe teige, e iniu zeḡeꞌa bare duduḡa azaḡa rae zamareꞌeteꞌe azaḡa huzoga veize mene ariro, rehano iniu zeḡeꞌa bare haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa rae zamareꞌeteꞌe azaḡa huzadu zeꞌa haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihuroga veize ariro.”   
\s1 Ihore Iziga  
\r (Mataio 9:14-17; Mareko 2:18-22)  
\p
\v 33 Ebu vaze nuꞌa Iesu niro, “Ioane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe ḡae ḡehaḡa ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡeꞌohe zu kurauꞌohe. Farisea azaḡa tahiꞌatahiꞌa zuni ꞌougeꞌohe. Rehano ḡae tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe iḡaiḡa ogauꞌohe zu gageꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 34 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Hahu muiḡa madaḡano, hahu ohozeḡa iziganiꞌa huziroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe hahu ohozeḡa iziga teite radiuꞌeteꞌea ze ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡiꞌumahe?  
\v 35 Rehano zeḡe mazaonoꞌo hahu ohozeḡa izigaꞌe mae vaḡiniteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa arine, ze ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 36 Ebu Iesuꞌa bare hari ꞌahoga idane ziro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa dabua iziga variꞌe madu dabua amahiḡa mene banineꞌohe. Baninine, dabua izigaꞌe mae borofe zigiꞌuma, ebu dabua izigaꞌe amahiḡa teite horone tibunoga zuni mene manoḡa reꞌuma.  
\v 37 Ebu vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa vaini vuḡa fuse\f + \fr 5:37 \ft Vaini vuḡa fuseꞌe boromakau ga gouti ogaḡa hina haḡairo. \f* amahiḡa zamaḡano vaini vuḡa iziga mene beꞌune ufiꞌohe. Beꞌune ufine, vaini vuḡa iziganiꞌa bare busure bororanadu vaini vuḡa fuse amahiḡaniꞌa zigaꞌuma, ebu vaini vuḡaꞌe sore rururaꞌuma zu vaini vuḡa fuse amahiḡa sausauniꞌuma.  
\v 38 Eꞌanoꞌo vaini vuḡa izigaꞌe vaini vuḡa fuse izigano beuꞌe ufiꞌuma.  
\v 39 Rehano vaini vuḡa amahiḡa gagidoteꞌe azaḡaꞌe vaini vuḡa iziga mene urateꞌohe, mazaḡa zeꞌe ꞌahige rae raꞌohe, 'Amahiḡaꞌe ufeta manoḡa.'”   
\c 6  
\s1 Bana Madaḡa Zuhiꞌaḡa  
\r (Mataio 12:1-8; Mareko 2:23-28)  
\p
\v 1 Bana Madaḡa ꞌahogano Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite vuidi mebaḡa zamaḡano onamiro. Ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa vuidi maḡa ririꞌe meiro, zu ꞌevoreze hina hasiga mute vaḡinadu huga aro.  
\v 2 ꞌOugirotene, Farisea azaḡa nuꞌa ḡadiziro, “Zaꞌe nougadu Bana Madaḡa goroḡa varadeꞌohe?”   
\p
\v 3 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Zaꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡa mene meꞌodirohe? Davida zu ani ḡatiniroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe vinize ruzirotene, Davidaꞌa nougiro?  
\v 4 Aniꞌe Badiꞌa ne diuḡadu dibuꞌo azaḡaniꞌa daꞌo auꞌeteꞌe dibuꞌo ꞌuvahuḡa odoga aro, ebu ani ḡatiniroteꞌe azaḡa zuni ziniro.”  
\v 5 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Vaze Ubugaꞌe Bana Madaḡa Zuhiꞌaḡa.”   
\s1 ꞌEvoꞌa Hoega Vazeḡa Fainiro  
\r (Mataio 12:9-14; Mareko 3:1-6)  
\p
\v 6 Ebu Bana Madaḡa ꞌahogano, Iesuꞌa nu'onu'o neḡa diuḡadu vaze ḡehaḡa ihozinu. Eꞌea edaꞌe nae ꞌevoꞌa hoega vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu.  
\v 7 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaꞌe Iesuꞌa Bana Madaḡano vaze eꞌe fainiꞌuma ga meneꞌe ḡianifine, ehamu radiro. Mazaḡa Iesuꞌa vaze eꞌe fainine, kotao ani ohonihi reiro.  
\v 8 Rehano Iesuꞌe zeꞌa nouge rae zamareꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederadu ꞌevoꞌa hoega vazeḡa niro, “Iḡunadu vaze niduꞌa zamao edanoꞌi.” Ebu ani iḡunadu edaro.  
\v 9 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “E ḡadiziꞌohe. Bana Madaḡano nagini haḡaine duduḡa? Manoḡa haḡaiꞌuma ga sauꞌa haḡaiꞌuma? Vaze ḡaboziꞌuma ga zimiꞌuma?”  
\v 10 Aniꞌa zeḡe niduꞌa ḡiaziroteꞌe enogano vaze eꞌe niro, “ꞌEvoꞌo ꞌeinoꞌi.” Aniꞌa ꞌevoꞌa ꞌeinirotene, ꞌevoꞌaniꞌa manoriro.   
\p
\v 11 Rehano ze maḡune rudanadu Iesu mazao nagini haḡaiteꞌe moneo ḡadahe ḡoꞌane tiburaro.   
\s1 Apostolo Azaḡa Gaubanana Aheu Fare Ohotiro  
\r (Mataio 10:1-4; Mareko 3:13-19)  
\p
\v 12 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌa kuranoga veize maḡa ꞌahoga onamadu ohere faḡa Badiꞌa mazao kuraro.  
\v 13 Ebu irarirotene, aniꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa huze nuꞌoziro. Ebu zeḡe boꞌaḡano tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare ohotadu Apostolo azaḡa rae huziro.  
\v 14 Nizeꞌe Simona(niḡa ꞌahogaꞌe Petero), Petero negoḡa Anderea, Iakobo, Ioane, Filipi, Batolomeo,  
\v 15 Mataio, Tomasi, Alefeo ubuga Iakobo, Zelota\f + \fr 6:15 \ft Roma gavamani utitoziniroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Zelota duḡuru rae huziro. \f* vazeḡa Simona,  
\v 16 Iakobo ubuga Iuda ebu Iesu revoharoteꞌe vazeḡa, Isakariota vazeḡa Iuda.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Vaze Ihoziro zu Faiziro  
\r (Mataio 4:23-25)  
\p
\v 17 Eꞌe enogano, Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite maḡanonoꞌo ovaradu haba sebaḡano edaro. Eꞌea ane hegoteꞌeteꞌe vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ebu haba nunuonoꞌo vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa radiunu. Zeꞌe Iudea habaꞌa, Ierusalema zu davara genaḡano ne boro Turo ebu Sidonoonoꞌo ariro.  
\v 18 Zeꞌe Iesu ḡoere igifine zu ugizeonoꞌo manorifine ariro. Iesuꞌa Vine sauꞌaniꞌa diuḡadu sausauziroteꞌe azaḡa zuni faiziro.  
\v 19 Ebu zeḡe niduꞌa ani ahiri obonihi reiro, mazaḡa ugi faineꞌeteꞌe inaraḡaꞌe ani mazaonoꞌo buanadu zeḡe niduꞌa manoriro.   
\s1 Matuꞌu ebu Aduga  
\r (Mataio 5:1-12)  
\p
\v 20 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ḡiazeꞌenaꞌa ziro,  
\q1 “Za, zahara azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,  
\q2 mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌohe.   
\q1
\v 21 Za, izidi vinizeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,  
\q2 mazaḡa isize miniꞌuma.  
\q1 Za, izidi niauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe,  
\q2 mazaḡa vesuꞌu matuꞌe eḡofiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 22 Vaze Ubuga uꞌano, vazeꞌa zaꞌe heꞌeheꞌezine, hezahozine, ḡoere sauꞌa zine, ebu zaꞌe sauꞌa rae reine, zaꞌe matuꞌiꞌuma.  
\v 23 ꞌUguḡaniꞌa zae mazao fureranoꞌidene, matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa zavonoꞌi, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa adureo naeḡa boro bagaḡa ziniꞌuma. Zeḡe vouḡaniꞌa peroveta azaḡa deꞌuge sausauzido.   
\q1
\v 24 Rehano za, maꞌora azaḡaꞌe aduga hidiꞌuma,  
\q2 mazaḡa zaꞌe ibite ḡau manoḡa niduꞌa mae hauḡiro ꞌahine, vesuꞌu mene bare meꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 25 Za, izidi ogau isi miniꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe aduga hidiꞌuma,  
\q2 mazaḡa vesuꞌu viniziꞌuma.  
\q1 Za, izidi matuꞌe eḡofeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe aduga hidiꞌuma,  
\q2 mazaḡa vesuꞌu zamazeꞌa areꞌenaꞌa, niaꞌuma.   
\p
\v 26 Vaze niduꞌa zae niguzine aduga hidiꞌuma, mazaḡa zeḡe vouḡaniꞌa ḡuriro peroveta azaḡa ꞌouge niguzido.”   
\s1 Agire Azaḡa Zamare Borofoꞌi  
\r (Mataio 5:38-48, 7:12a)  
\p
\v 27 “Rehano e eḡe ḡoere igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, za ziꞌohe. Zae agire azaḡa zamare borofoꞌi, zu zae heꞌeheꞌezeꞌeteꞋe azaḡa mazao manoḡa haḡaoꞌi.  
\v 28 Zae mazao, 'Radiu tuḡutuḡu adugaḡa hidoꞌi,' rae zoꞌidene, ze manohuga hidoga veize uminoꞌi, zu zae mazao haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa veize kuranoꞌi.  
\v 29 Iniuꞌa zae ḡanineze faꞌonoꞌidene, naeḡa zuni notonohanoꞌi, ebu iniuꞌa zae raga dabuaḡa meinadu hena bare zae zizuni dabuaḡa meihi roꞌidene, eꞌe zuni hanoꞌi.  
\v 30 Iniuꞌa nagini umizoꞌidene hau tauḡoꞌi, ebu iniuꞌa ḡauze moꞌidene, ago bare moꞌi.  
\v 31 Vazeꞌa zae mazao manoḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe uratoꞌidene, zae zuni zeḡe mazao manoḡa haḡaoꞌi.   
\p
\v 32 Zaeꞌa zae zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa daꞌo zamare borofine, Badiꞌaꞌa eꞌe naeḡa mene ziniꞌuma. Haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa zuni zeḡe zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zamare borofeꞌohe.  
\v 33 Zaeꞌa zae mazao manoḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazao daꞌo manoḡa haḡaine, Badiꞌaꞌa eꞌe naeḡa mene ziniꞌuma. Haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa zuni ꞌouge haḡaeꞌohe.  
\v 34 Zaeꞌa ḡauze baroniꞌuma rae raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa daꞌo zinine, Badiꞌaꞌa eꞌe naeḡa za mene ziniꞌuma. Haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa zuni ḡauze bare meꞌuma rae zamareꞌenaꞌa, ḡauze sauꞌa azaḡa ziniꞌohe.  
\v 35 Rehano zae agire azaḡa zamare borofoꞌi, zu zeḡe mazao manoḡa haḡaoꞌi. Ebu zeꞌa eḡe mazao bare naenaehiꞌuma rae mene zamareꞌenaꞌa, zini tauḡoꞌi. ꞌOugine, Badiꞌaꞌa naeḡa boro ziniꞌuma, ebu zaꞌe Ḡihiꞌa Hune Badiꞌaḡa ubuga reꞌuma. Mazaḡa Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi rae mene raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ebu sauꞌa azaḡa zuni Badiꞌaꞌa vetuḡaziꞌohe.  
\v 36 Zae Mama, Badiꞌaꞌa vaze vetuḡaziꞌeteꞌe teige, zae zuni vaze vetuḡazoꞌi.”   
\s1 Vaze mazao Sauꞌa rae Ago Zoꞌi  
\r (Mataio 7:1-5)  
\p
\v 37 “Vaze mazao sauꞌa azaḡa rae ago zoꞌi. ꞌOugine, Badiꞌaꞌa zuni zae mazao sauꞌa azaḡa rae mene ziꞌuma. Vaze mazao veꞌoḡa rae ago zoꞌi. ꞌOugine, Badiꞌaꞌa zae mazao veꞌoḡa rae mene ziꞌuma. Vaze haḡai sauꞌa rae modoꞌi. ꞌOugine Badiꞌaꞌa zae haḡai sauꞌa rae modiꞌuma.  
\v 38 Ḡauze zenoꞌi, ꞌougine Badiꞌaꞌa manohuga ziniꞌuma. Aniꞌa zaꞌe iriꞌavone fosafosanoga, taugoga, zuꞌizuꞌinoga ebu foraꞌaḡa beuꞌe ruruno ziniꞌuma. Zaeꞌa vaze nagini hauꞌeteꞌe idunaḡano Badiꞌaꞌa ꞌouge zae ziniꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 39 Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga idane ziro, “Ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡaniꞌa ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡa ibitohanogaꞌe idaḡahe? ꞌOugine, anianine hoꞌona uite ovoiꞌuma.  
\v 40 Tahiꞌaꞌe ani ihore vazeḡa mene vitinoga. Rehano tahiꞌaꞌa edeḡa niduꞌa meine, aniꞌe ane ihore vazeḡa teigiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 41 Zaꞌe nabudize ubuma beꞌa dinunuḡa ḡianeꞌohe. Rehano nougadu zae ubuma beꞌa gado ireḡa mene horoneꞌohe?  
\v 42 Zaꞌe zae ubuma beꞌa gado ireḡa mene horoneꞌe rehano, nabudize mazao ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Eḡe nabudi, eḡeꞌa ubumaḡo beꞌa dinunu eꞌe mae vaḡinihi.' Zaꞌe zama guhi azaḡa! Ibite geno zae ubuma beꞌa gado ireḡa eꞌe mae vaḡinoꞌi, ꞌougine zaeꞌa faine ehamanadu nabudize ubuma beꞌa dinunuḡa mae vaḡiniꞌuma.”   
\s1 Ire ebu Ire Maḡa  
\r (Mataio 7:16-20, 12:34-35)  
\p
\v 43 “Ire manoḡaꞌe maḡa sauꞌa mene iniꞌohe, zu ire sauꞌaꞌe maḡa manoḡa mene iniꞌohe.  
\v 44 Ireꞌe maḡa horonadu nagi ireḡa edereꞌohe. Figi maḡaꞌe ire renoganonoꞌo mene iniꞌohe, zu vaini maḡaꞌe ḡunu renoganonoꞌo mene iniꞌohe.  
\v 45 Eꞌe teige, vaze manoḡaꞌe ani zamao manoḡa nuꞌonadu manoḡa fureneꞌohe, ebu sauꞌa vazeḡaꞌe ani zamao sauꞌa nuꞌonadu sauꞌa fureneꞌohe. Mazaḡa naginiꞌa ane zamao iriꞌave radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe hebeꞌanonoꞌo buauꞌohe.”   
\s1 Egadu Haḡaeꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa  
\r (Mataio 7:24-27)  
\p
\v 46 “Zaꞌe eḡe mazao, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro, Zuhiꞌa Boro,' rae huheꞌohe, rehano nougadu eḡeꞌa ḡoereꞌeteꞌe mene haḡaeꞌohe?  
\v 47 Eḡe vaḡe aradu ḡoerehe igiꞌeteꞌe ebu ꞌouge haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe iniu heuḡa rae ihoziꞌuma.  
\v 48 Aniꞌe raha vohutuna huꞌi ovoadu vatava riḡa rana neḡa ogoraroteꞌe vazeḡa heuḡa. Zobozoboꞌa feuradu ne haganirotene, ne aꞌe mene hagariro, mazaḡa haba riḡano faine ogoraro.  
\v 49 Rehano eḡe ḡoere egadu ꞌouge mene haḡaeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe, raha mene faine hoꞌadu haba zoreḡano neḡa ogoraroteꞌe vazeḡa heuḡa. Zobozoboꞌa feuradu ne eꞌe haganirotene, zogone higanadu fahau ḡuzuhiro.”   
\c 7  
\s1 Uti Vazeḡa Boroꞌa Iesu mazao Firo  
\r (Mataio 8:5-13; Ioane 4:43-54)  
\p
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ane ḡoere niduꞌa zeḡe mazao ḡoeriroteꞌe enogano, Kaperanauma diuḡiro.  
\v 2 Eꞌea uti vazeḡa boro ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu. Aneꞌa zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe tuḡureḡa vazeḡaꞌe ugine sausaunadu nariga rudaro.  
\v 3 Uti vazeḡa boroꞌe Iesu hariḡa igirotene, Iesuꞌa aradu ani tuḡure vazeḡa fainoga uratiro. Eꞌanoꞌo ani Iuda azaḡa boroboro Iesu uminoga veize tuḡuziro.  
\v 4 Ebu zeꞌe Iesu mazao feuradu zamaze niduꞌa hina uminiro, “Ḡa ani dananine manoḡa,  
\v 5 mazaḡa aniꞌe eme, Iuda azaḡa zamare borofeꞌohe ebu emeḡe veize nu'onu'o neḡa ogoraro.”  
\v 6 Eꞌanoꞌo Iesuꞌa zeḡe teite uti vazeḡa boro ne onamiro.  
\p Ze uti vazeḡa boro ne uhiḡano feurirotene, uti vazeḡa boroꞌa ane vaze nu Iesu vaḡe tuḡuziro. Ebu zeꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu niro, “Uti vazeḡa boroꞌa ꞌahige rae raha, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro, ago ufeta zamaroꞌi. Eꞌe mene vaze manoḡa ꞌahine, ḡaeꞌa eḡe ne diuḡogaꞌe mene idaḡa.  
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo e ḡa vaḡe amiꞌuma rae mene zamareha. Rehano ḡa ḡoere daꞌo roꞌi, ꞌougine eḡe tuḡure vazeḡaniꞌa manoriꞌuma.  
\v 8 Mazaḡa eḡe zuni vaze ꞌahoga ꞌuꞌuḡano gaueꞌohe, ebu uti azaḡa zuni eḡe ꞌuꞌuḡano gaueꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa vaze ꞌahi ninaꞌa, “Onamoꞌi,” raꞌetene aniꞌe onameꞌohe, ebu ꞌahoga ꞌomo ninaꞌa, “Aroꞌi,” raꞌetene aniꞌe areꞌohe. Eḡeꞌa eḡe tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahoga ninaꞌa, “ꞌAdi haḡaoꞌi,” raꞌetene aniꞌe haḡaeꞌohe.'”   
\p
\v 9 Iesuꞌa ani ḡoere igirotene, ani ḡoere uꞌano zaguzagaro. Ebu vaetadu ane hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Isaraela azaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahige fie gigaruꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ꞌize mene horoneha.”  
\v 10 Ebu ze bare uti vazeḡa boro ne onamirotene, tuḡure vazeḡaniꞌa manoriroteꞌe horoniro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ḡozoba Ubuga Runeonoꞌo Ḡaboniro  
\p
\v 11 Eꞌe enogano, Iesuꞌa ne ꞌahoga niḡa Naina onamiro. Ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa zu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ani ḡatiniro.  
\v 12 Ebu Iesuꞌa ne ḡutuꞌaḡano feurirotene, ne azaḡaꞌe rune vazeḡa ꞌahoga herate buni ariro. Aniꞌe ḡozoba ꞌahoga ubuga tibuhuga. Ebu ne azaḡa ḡehaḡa zuni ḡozoba eꞌe teite ariro.  
\v 13 Iesuꞌa ḡozoba eꞌe horonirotene, ani vetuḡaneadu niro, “Ago nianoꞌi.”  
\v 14 Ebu hena Iesuꞌa rune ahiꞌa mauḡa herateꞌeteꞌe azaḡa vaḡe onamadu mauḡa obonirotene, ze tue edaro. Ebu aniꞌa rune vazeḡa niro, “Tahiꞌa iziga, eḡeꞌa ḡaꞌohe, iḡunoꞌi!”  
\v 15 ꞌOugirotene, rune vazeḡaniꞌa iḡune ehoradu ḡoeꞌa ḡadaheniro, ebu Iesuꞌa bare viꞌa ꞌevoreo riꞌiniro.   
\p
\v 16 ꞌOugadu zeḡe niduꞌa rihau rudaro zu Badiꞌa niguniro. Ze ꞌahige rae reiro, “Peroveta vazeḡa boroꞌa emeḡe boꞌaḡano fureraneha!” ebu “Badiꞌaꞌa ane mone azaḡa danazifine areha!”  
\v 17 Ebu Iesuꞌa nagini haḡairoteꞌe hariḡaniꞌa Iuda habaꞌa ebu uhiḡa habaꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano bororaro. \fig Iesuꞌa ḡozoba ubuga ḡaboniro|src="DN00449b.tif" size="col" ref="7:11-17" \fig*   
\s1 Iesu zu Ioane Babatiso  
\r (Mataio 11:2-19)  
\p
\v 18 Ioane Babatisoꞌe ḡuꞌa neḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ane vaḡe onamadu Iesuꞌa haḡairoteꞌe hariḡa niduꞌa meꞌodoharo. Ebu Ioaneꞌa ane tahiꞌa aheu huzadu ziro,  
\v 19 “Zuhiꞌa Boro vaḡe onamadu ꞌahige ḡadinoꞌi, 'Ariꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡahe? Mene reine, eme vaze ꞌahoga guhiniꞌumahe?'”   
\p
\v 20 Ebu ze Iesu vaḡe onamadu ḡadiniro, “Ioane Babatisoꞌa ḡadiꞌoga veize eme tuḡufeha. 'Ariꞌuma rae reiroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡahe? Mene reine, eme vaze ꞌahoga guhiniꞌumahe?'”   
\p
\v 21 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌa ugi nunu zu vine sauꞌa meiroteꞌe azaḡa ḡehaḡa faiziro, ebu ubuma kuruḡa azaḡa ḡehaḡa faizadu ze bare ehamaro.  
\v 22 Eꞌanoꞌo Iesuꞌa Ioane tahiꞌa aheu naenaeziro, “Bare onamadu zaeꞌa nagini horonateꞌe zu egateꞌe Ioane ihonoꞌi. Ubuma kuru azaḡaꞌe ehamuꞌohe, oda sauꞌa azaḡaꞌe edau ragaveꞌohe, refera azaḡaꞌe manoreꞌohe, teḡaze uhuḡa azaḡaꞌe igiꞌohe, rune azaḡaꞌe bare ḡabodeꞌohe, ebu zahara azaḡaꞌe hari manoḡa igiꞌohe.  
\v 23 Eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe mene modeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe matuꞌiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 24 Ioaneꞌa tuḡuziroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa iḡuniroteꞌe enogano, Iesuꞌa Ioane moneo vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ḡadahe ziro, “Za nagini horonoga veize haba bohaꞌa onamiro? Zavaraꞌa imi veḡa hudi naeninaeniꞌeteꞌe horonoga radu onamirohe?  
\v 25 Mene reine, za nagini horonoga veize onamiro? Dabua manomano vidaroteꞌe vazeḡa horonoga veize onamirohe? Naeḡa boro dabuaḡa vidaroteꞌe zu ḡau manomanoḡeta radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe kini neo radiuꞌohe.  
\v 26 ꞌOugadu nagini horonoga veize onamiro? Peroveta vazeḡahe? Oꞌe, eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Ioaneꞌe peroveta azaḡa vitizoga.  
\v 27 Ioane moneo Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro,  
\q1 'Ḡianoꞌi, eḡeꞌa ḡae zamao vaze ꞌahoga ibite tuḡuniꞌuma.  
\q2 Aniꞌe ḡae zamao ḡae ibi ruhibiꞌuma.'\x + \xo 7:27 \xt Malaki 3:1 \x*   
\m
\v 28 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Ioaneꞌe rahao ꞌada fureraroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa vitizoga. Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡanoꞌe ḡonaga vazeḡa zuni Ioane vitinoga.”   
\p
\v 29 (Ebu Iesu ḡoere igiroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa zu takesi azaḡa zuni Ioane mazaonoꞌo babatiso meiro. Ebu zeꞌe ꞌahige rae reiro, “Badiꞌa gau ibiḡaꞌe duduḡa!”  
\v 30 U Farisea azaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Ioane mazaonoꞌo babatiso mene meiro. ꞌOugadu ze zeḡe veize Badiꞌaꞌa haḡaiteꞌe haḡaiḡa hezahoharo.)   
\p
\v 31 Iesuꞌa bare ziro, “Izidi azaḡaꞌe naginio idaziꞌuma? Ze iniu heuḡa?  
\v 32 Zeꞌe tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌaniꞌa ne hunio ehoradu araheꞌeteꞌe heuḡa. Ze rovozadu none tahiꞌaḡaniꞌa mone tahiꞌaḡa mazao ꞌahige huauꞌohe,  
\q1 'Eme muio suraꞌi hodeha, rehano za mene zavoneha.  
\q2 Ebu eme rune habaꞌano niau ḡoinaheha, rehano za mene nianeha.'   
\m
\v 33 Ioane babatisoꞌa aradu ogomu mene audo zu vaini vuḡa mene gagido. ꞌOugadu za ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Ioaneꞌe vine sauꞌaḡeta.'  
\v 34 U Vaze Ubugaꞌe aradu ogomu auꞌohe ebu vaini vuḡa gageꞌohe. ꞌOugeꞌetene, za bare ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Ḡianoꞌi, aniꞌe ogomu fuꞌa zu vaini vuḡa fuꞌa. Ebu ani takesi azaḡa zu haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa teite tiburuꞌohe.'  
\v 35 Rehano Badiꞌa zamarone huhuzaḡa hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ane zamarone huhuzaḡaꞌe duduḡa rae fureneꞌohe.”   
\s1 Haḡai Sauꞌa Roḡaeḡaniꞌa Iesu Odaḡa rana Dehoro Beꞌuniro  
\p
\v 36 Mada ꞌahogano Farisea vazeḡa ꞌahoga, Simonaꞌa Iesu teite oganoga veize Iesu huniro. Ebu Iesuꞌa Farisea vazeḡa ne onamadu ogomu fataḡa babaḡano tave ehoriro.  
\v 37 Eꞌe neḡanoꞌe haḡai sauꞌa roḡaeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu. Aniꞌe Iesuꞌa Farisea vazeḡa neo ogauꞌeteꞌe ederirotene, dehoro hohoga manoḡa naeḡa boro bio komeꞌa manohuga iriꞌavonadu mae ariro.  
\v 38 Ebu roḡae eꞌeꞌa ne diuḡadu Iesu ḡarugano niauꞌenaꞌa, odaḡa babaḡano ḡuḡuriro. Ebu niḡa vuḡaniꞌa Iesu oda rana sore buanadu abune vanirotene, iguḡa hina odaḡa zauhiro. Ebu gubaneꞌenaꞌa, odaḡa furaꞌinadu dehoro beuꞌiro.   
\p
\v 39 Iesu huniroteꞌe Farisea vazeḡa Simonaꞌa eꞌe horonirotene, ani aneꞌa bare ꞌahige rae reiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe peroveta vazeḡa reifone, ani oboneꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡaꞌe roḡae nagiga rae ederifo. Roḡae ꞌahiꞌe haḡai sauꞌa roḡaeḡa rae ederifo.”  
\v 40 Iesuꞌa niro, “Simona, e hari ꞌahoga ḡeꞌuma.” Simonaꞌa naenaeniro, “Ihore vazeḡa, ehoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 41 Ebu Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga meꞌodoharo, “Vaze aheuꞌa vaze ꞌahoga mazaonoꞌo hadi nu madu vesu baroniꞌuma rae reiro. ꞌAhogaꞌe hadi silivaḡa\f + \fr 7:41 \fqa denari. \ft Denari tibaꞌe mada tiba gauḡa hadiḡa. \f* niduꞌa 500 meiro, u ꞌahogaꞌe hadi silivaḡa niduꞌa 50 meiro.  
\v 42 Ebu vaze aheuꞌe hadi vazeḡa mazao hadi baronoga mene idararo, eꞌanoꞌo hadi vazeḡaniꞌa ziro, 'Ahiḡa, ago baronoꞌi.' ꞌOugine, anianine boꞌaḡano iniuꞌa hadi vazeḡa ufeta zamare borofiꞌuma?”  
\v 43 Simonaꞌa naenaeniro, “E zamarone, hadi silivaḡa 500 meiroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa hadi vazeḡa ufeta zamare borofiꞌuma. Mazaḡa hadi vazeḡaniꞌa ane hadi boro ago baronoꞌi rae reiro.”  
\p Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡae naenaeꞌe duduḡa.”  
\v 44 Ebu Iesuꞌa roḡae tehe ḡianadu Simona niro, “Ḡa roḡae ꞌadi horoneꞌehe? E ḡae ne diuḡatene, ḡaꞌe odahe vuzuꞌoga veize vu mene eneha. Rehano roḡae ꞌahiꞌe eḡe oda ani ni vuḡa hina abunadu iguḡa hina zauhe imineha.  
\v 45 Ḡaꞌe mene gubahe furaꞌiheha, rehano roḡae ꞌahiꞌe eḡeꞌa diuḡi arateꞌeanoꞌo odahe ꞌauꞌaune furaꞌineha.  
\v 46 Ḡaꞌe vadiniheo dehoro mene beuꞌeha, rehano aniꞌe eḡe odao dehoro hohoḡa manoḡa beuꞌeha.  
\v 47 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ḡaꞌohe, roḡae ꞌahi haḡaiḡa sauꞌa ḡehaḡa ꞌai rae modeha, mazaḡa ani eḡe zamare borofadu eḡe mazao ꞌouge haḡaeha. U eḡeꞌa iniu haḡaiḡa sauꞌa tahiḡa daꞌo rae modine, aniꞌa eḡe tahiḡa daꞌo zamariꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 48 Ebu Iesuꞌa roḡae eꞌe niro, “Ḡae haḡai sauꞌa ꞌai rae modeha.”  
\v 49 ꞌOugirotene, Iesu teite ogauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare zamariro, “ꞌAhiꞌe iniu? Ani vaze haḡai sauꞌa zuni rae modeꞌehe?”   
\p
\v 50 Ebu Iesuꞌa roḡae eꞌe niro, “Ḡaeꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano ḡabone hideha. Zamaḡo roḡenadu onamoꞌi.”   
\c 8  
\s1 Roḡaeroḡaeꞌa Iesu Dananiro  
\p
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano Iesuꞌe haba nunu zu ne nunu ragave onamadu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo hari manoḡa haramiro, ebu tahiꞌaḡa gaubanana aheu fare zuni ani ḡatiniro.  
\v 2 Ebu vine sauꞌaniꞌa ragano reiroteꞌe zu ugi nunuꞌa meiroteꞌe roḡaeḡa nuꞌe ugize manoradu Iesu ḡatiniro. Zeḡe boꞌaḡano Magadala roḡaeḡa Mariaꞌe ibite vine sauꞌa fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa ani mazaonoꞌo buaroteꞌe roḡaeḡa.  
\v 3 Ebu Kuza inuga, niḡa Ioana zuni Iesu ḡatiniro. Kuzaꞌe kini Heroda ne taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Ebu roḡae ꞌahoga, niḡa Susana zu roḡae nunuꞌa Iesu ḡatiniro. Zeḡeꞌa ḡauze hina Iesu ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa danaziro.   
\s1 Ezone Feune Ḡorauꞌeteꞌe Hari Idaidaḡa  
\r (Mataio 13:1-17; Mareko 4:1-12)  
\p
\v 4 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa nuꞌoraro, ebu ne nunuonoꞌo vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa Iesu vaḡe ariro. ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga idane ziro,   
\p
\v 5 “Hihi vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa mebaḡano ezone ḡora onamiro. Ani ezone feune ḡorarotene, nuꞌe ibio rururaro. ꞌOugadu vazeꞌa eꞌe ezoneḡa rana edau oname onairo, zu nini'a au hauḡiro.  
\v 6 Ezone nuꞌe hadi habaꞌano rururaro. Eꞌe ezoneḡaꞌe ḡuhuriro, rehano roraro, mazaḡa rahaꞌe mene abuꞌa.  
\v 7 Ezone nuꞌe ve renogano rururaro. Ebu ezone eꞌe zu ve renogaꞌe tibano ḡuhure bororanadu ve renoganiꞌa ezone ḡuhuḡa simariniro.  
\v 8 U ezone nuꞌe raha manoḡano rururanadu faine ḡuhure bororaro, ebu hugaꞌe ḡae 100 hudaro.” Iesuꞌa ḡoere hauḡirotene, ḡihau ziro, “Teḡaḡeta vazeḡaꞌe faine egadu huga ederoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 9 Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa hari idaidaḡa huga ḡadiniro.  
\v 10 Ebu Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo ꞌuꞌuru tirotaꞌaꞌe zae mazao fureniro, rehano vaze nunu mazaoꞌe hari idaidaḡa hina ḡoreziro. ꞌOugadu ze ḡoere huga aḡuꞌa. Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 'Zeꞌe horoneꞌe rehano, hugaꞌe mene horoniꞌuma.  
\q1 Zeꞌe igiꞌe rehano, hugaꞌe mene ederiꞌuma.'\x + \xo 8:10 \xt Isaia 6:9\x*”   
\s1 Ezone Feune Ḡorauꞌeteꞌe Hari Idaidaḡa Huga  
\r (Mataio 13:18-23; Mareko 4:13-20)  
\p
\v 11 “Eḡeꞌa ezone feune ḡorauꞌeteꞌe hariḡa idaidaḡa huga ihoziꞌuma. Ezoneꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere.  
\v 12 Vaze nuꞌe ibio rururaroteꞌe ezoga heuḡa. Zeꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere igiꞌe rehano, Sataniꞌa aradu zeḡe zama mazaonoꞌo Badiꞌa ḡoere mae vaḡineꞌe ꞌahine, Badiꞌa ḡoere mene mae ḡihinadu ḡabone mene hideꞌohe.  
\v 13 Vaze nuꞌe hadi habaꞌano rururaroteꞌe ezoga heuḡa. Zeꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere igiꞌetene matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa, mae ḡihineꞌohe. Rehano zeꞌa fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe taiga oꞌoꞌa radu mada tahiḡa daꞌo fieꞌohe. Ebu Sataniꞌa tuhuze nuriꞌetene uiteꞌohe.  
\v 14 Vaze nuꞌe ve renogano rururaroteꞌe ezoga heuḡa. Zeꞌe Badiꞌa ḡoere igiꞌe rehano, ḡaboneze zamaḡano zamaze aduga borofeꞌohe, haba toheḡa ufeta zamareꞌohe zu haba ḡauḡa manomano hina ufeta matuꞌeꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo zeꞌe mene iniꞌohe.  
\v 15 Vaze nuꞌe raha manoḡano rururaroteꞌe ezoga heuḡa. Ze zamaze manoḡa zu duduḡa hina Badiꞌa ḡoere igiꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo zeꞌe aduga hideꞌetene, ḡoere eꞌe oboneꞌenaꞌa zu zamaze obone giganeꞌenaꞌa, hudauꞌohe.”   
\s1 Ihure Hari Idaidaḡa  
\r (Mareko 4:21-25)  
\p
\v 16 “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ihure hofadu siuva hina mene ogone tiꞌe ga vazuni fataḡa ꞌuꞌuḡano mene tiꞌohe. Rehano ne diuḡeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa agaḡa horonoga veize ihure odaḡa rana tiꞌohe.  
\v 17 Ihureꞌa ḡau niduꞌa aganeꞌeteꞌe teige, ꞌuꞌuru radiroteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa fureraꞌuma, ebu ogone ḡahiniroteꞌe ḡauḡa zuni ederiꞌuma zu horoniꞌuma.  
\v 18 Eꞌano'o zaeꞌa igiꞌeteꞌe ḡoeꞌa faine zamaroꞌi. Faifaine zamare igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa edeḡa ufeta boro ziniꞌuma. U mene faine zamare igiꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zeḡeꞌa tahiḡa edeḡa rae zamareꞌeteꞌe zuni mae vaḡiniꞌuma.”   
\s1 Iesu Viꞌa ebu Negoḡa  
\r (Mataio 12:46-50; Mareko 3:31-35)  
\p
\v 19 Eꞌe enogano Iesu viꞌa ebu negoḡa duḡuruꞌa ani vaḡe onamiro, rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ꞌahine ani uhiḡa onamoga mene idararo.  
\v 20 Ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu niro, “Viꞌu zu negoḡo duḡuruꞌa ḡiaꞌihi radu ne enogano edau radiuꞌohe.”  
\v 21 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Badiꞌa ḡoere egadu ꞌouge haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe eḡe nanu zu eḡe nego.”   
\s1 Zavara ꞌUiro  
\r (Mataio 8:23-27; Mareko 4:35-41)  
\p
\v 22 Mada ꞌahogano Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite ḡasio tiradu ziro, “Eme duꞌura moneafa fare onamihi.” Ebu ze fare onamiro.  
\v 23 Ze ḡasio fare onameꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano Iesuꞌe baziro. Ebu zavara boroꞌa feuradu vuꞌa ḡasi kafere diuḡiro zu foꞌariro. Eꞌanoꞌo zeꞌe nariga ꞌomatiro.  
\v 24 ꞌOugirotene, Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ane vaḡe onamadu evaniro, “Ihore vazeḡa! Ihore vazeḡa! Eme izidi hunuhuneꞌohe!”  
\p Ebu Iesuꞌa evatadu zavara zu saꞌu riḡa roziro. ꞌOugirotene, zavara zu saꞌuꞌa hauḡiro zu niduꞌa roḡeraro.  
\v 25 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Za eḡe mazao mene fieꞌehe?” Ebu zeḡe niduꞌa rihauꞌenaꞌa zu zaguzagauꞌenaꞌa, ḡadimutitiro, “ꞌAhiꞌe iniu? Aniꞌa zavara zu saꞌu riḡa ḡorezeꞌetene, ane ḡoere egohauꞌohe!”   
\s1 Vine Sauꞌaḡeta Vazeḡa Fainiro  
\r (Mataio 8:28-34; Mareko 5:1-20)  
\p
\v 26 Ebu Iesu zu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa Galilea duꞌuraḡa moneafa ruhau faradu Gerasa azaḡa habao hebetiro.  
\v 27 Iesuꞌa ḡasionoꞌo buarotene, eꞌe habaꞌano vine sauꞌaḡeta vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu hidiro. Aniꞌe mada faḡa firina zu neḡano mene radiunu, rehano idu habaꞌano radiunu.  
\v 28 Ani Iesu horonirotene, ani zamao higau bauradu ḡihau ḡaniḡanaro, “Iesu, Ḡihiꞌa Hune Badiꞌaḡa Ubuga! Ḡaꞌe eḡe mazao nagini urateꞌohe? E umiꞌeꞌohe, aduga ago enoꞌi!”  
\v 29 Aniꞌa ꞌouge reirotaꞌaꞌe mazaḡa Iesuꞌa vine sauꞌa riḡa ḡoreniro, “Ani mazaonoꞌo buanoꞌi!” Vine sauꞌaniꞌa ḡae ḡehaḡa ani ragano reiroteꞌe uꞌano, haba eꞌe azaḡaniꞌa auri adiriḡa riḡa hina ꞌevoꞌa zu odaḡa batune teadu ḡiane radiudo. Rehano aniꞌa miniḡa riꞌi ḡuzuhadu vine sauꞌaniꞌa tuḡune haba bohaꞌa onamido.  
\v 30 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ḡa niḡo iniu?” Aniꞌa naenaeniro, “E niꞌe Legioni,”\f + \fr 8:30 \ft Uti azaḡa ḡehaḡa. Zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe 6,000 heuḡa. \f* mazaḡa vine sauꞌa ḡehaḡaniꞌa ani ragano radiunu.  
\v 31 Ebu vine sauꞌasauꞌaniꞌa Iesu uminiro, “Eme hoꞌone ḡonaga oꞌoꞌano\f + \fr 8:31 \fqa Abisi \f* ago tuḡufoꞌi!”   
\p
\v 32 Eꞌe madaḡano aba ḡuḡuvaḡaꞌe maḡa komeꞌano ogaunu. Eꞌanoꞌo vine sauꞌasauꞌaniꞌa Iesu uminiro, “Eme aba ḡuḡuvaḡa mazao diuḡoga tuḡufoꞌi.” Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Idaḡa, buanadu onamoꞌi.”  
\v 33 Ebu vine sauꞌasauꞌa ꞌai vaze eꞌe mazaonoꞌo buanadu aba ḡuḡuvaḡa mazao diuḡe ḡouriro. Ebu aba ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa maḡa komeꞌa gagaḡanonoꞌo dure ovoradu duꞌurao hunuhune rudaro. \fig Aba ḡehaḡaniꞌa davarao dure diuḡiro|src="WA03846b.tif" size="col" ref="8:32" \fig*   
\p
\v 34 Aba taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe horonirotene, ferau manahadu ne boro zu ne komeꞌa azaḡa meꞌodoziniro.  
\v 35 Ebu vaze ḡehaḡaꞌe naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe ḡianoga veize Iesu vaḡe onamiro. Ze onamirotene, vine sauꞌanonoꞌo manoriroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa dabua vidanadu zamarone manoḡano Iesu oda babaḡano ehoreꞌeteꞌe horoniro. Eꞌanoꞌo ze rihau ḡouriro.  
\v 36 Ebu naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe niduꞌa horoniroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa haba nunuonoꞌo ariroteꞌe azaḡa mazao vine sauꞌaḡeta vazeḡaꞌe nougenouge manoriroteꞌe meꞌodoziniro.  
\v 37 ꞌOugadu Gerasa habaꞌa azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe rihau rudanadu Iesuꞌa eꞌe habaꞌanonoꞌo vaḡinoga uminiro. Eꞌanoꞌo Iesuꞌe ḡasio tiradu bare duꞌura moneafa fare onamiro.   
\p
\v 38 Vine sauꞌanonoꞌo manoriroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe Iesu teite onamoga veize uminiro. Rehano Iesuꞌa ani tuḡuneꞌenaꞌa, niro,  
\v 39 “Ḡa bare neḡo onamoꞌi, ebu Badiꞌaꞌa ḡae mazao manoḡa borofe haḡateꞌe ne azaḡa ihozoꞌi.” Eꞌanoꞌo ani bare onamadu ne niduꞌa ragaveꞌenaꞌa, Iesuꞌa ani mazao manoḡa borofe haḡairoteꞌe hariḡa niduꞌa meꞌodoziniro.   
\s1 Iairo Aboḡa ebu Ugi Roḡaeḡa  
\r (Mataio 9:18-26; Mareko 5:21-43)  
\p
\v 40 Iesuꞌa barirotene, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ani mae zouniro, mazaḡa zeḡe niduꞌa ani guhine radiro.  
\v 41 Eꞌe madaḡano vaze ꞌahoga, niḡa Iairoꞌa ariro. Aniꞌe nu'onu'o neḡa vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ꞌahoga. Aniꞌa Iesu oda babaḡano ḡuḡuradu uminiro, “Eḡe teite nehe onamihi!”  
\v 42 Mazaḡa aboḡa tibuhugaꞌe uginadu nariga rudaro. Ani muriꞌe gaubanana aheu fare.  
\p Ebu Iesuꞌa Iairo teite ane ne onameꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa naenaenoꞌo bibine varahe onamiro.  
\v 43 Vaze ḡehaḡa boꞌaḡano roḡae ꞌahogaꞌe roḡae ugiꞌa madu muri gaubanana aheu fare adugano radiunu. Rehano gohe vazeḡa ꞌahoga zuni fainoga mene idararo.  
\v 44 Aniꞌa Iesu ḡaruna aradu dabuaḡa ꞌariḡa tahiḡa oboniro. ꞌOugirotene, ugiḡaniꞌa zogone hauḡiro.  
\v 45 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadimaro, “Iniuꞌa oboheha?” Vaze niduꞌa naenaeniro, “Eme mene.” Ebu Peteroꞌa naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ḡae bibiꞌe varaheꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa ḡa tuꞌiꞌeha.”  
\v 46 Rehano Iesuꞌa reiro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa oboheha. E edeḡa, eḡe mazaonoꞌo gigiꞌaheꞌa buau vaḡiniro.”  
\v 47 ꞌOugadu roḡae aꞌe ani mazao naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe uꞌuranoga mene idaḡa rae zamariro. Ebu ani rihauꞌenaꞌa rereru Iesu vaḡe aradu ani oda babaḡano ḡuḡuriro. Ebu ani nougadu Iesu dabua oboniroteꞌe, zu nougenouge ugiḡaniꞌa zogone manoriroteꞌe vaze niduꞌa zamao ziro.  
\v 48 Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Aboe, ḡaeꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, ugiḡoꞌa manoreha. Zamaḡo roḡeḡano onamoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 49 Iesuꞌa ꞌize ḡoereꞌeteꞌea, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Iairo neonoꞌo aradu Iairo niro, “Aboḡo ꞌai rudaneha. Ihore vazeḡa barebare ago uminoꞌi.”  
\v 50 Rehano Iesuꞌa hari eꞌe egadu Iairo niro, “Ago rihanoꞌi. Fie tauḡoꞌi, ꞌougine, aboḡoꞌe bare ḡabodiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 51 Ebu Iesuꞌa Iairo neo feurirotene, Petero, Ioane, Iakobo zu roḡae komeꞌa viꞌa moga daꞌo neo zamaze diuḡiro, u vaze ꞌahogaꞌahogaꞌe diuḡoga mene idaḡa reiro.  
\v 52 Ze diuḡirotene, vaze niduꞌa ne zamaḡano niau kuau radiunu. Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Ago niau kuanoꞌi. Aniꞌe mene rudaneha, rehano bazeꞌohe.”  
\v 53 Ze ani eḡofoharo, mazaḡa zeꞌe roḡae komeꞌa aꞌe rudarotaꞌaꞌe ederiro.  
\v 54 Rehano Iesuꞌa roḡae komeꞌa ꞌevoꞌa obonadu niro, “Roḡae komeꞌa, iḡunoꞌi.”  
\v 55 ꞌOugirotene, ani viganiꞌa bare aradu zogone ḡabode iḡuniro. Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Ogomu nu hanoꞌi.”  
\v 56 Ani viꞌa mogaꞌe ufeta zaguzagaro. Rehano Iesuꞌa riḡa ḡoreziro, “Naginiꞌa fureranateꞌe vazeni ꞌahoga ago noꞌi.”   
\c 9  
\s1 Iesuꞌa Tahiꞌaḡa Gaubanana Aheu Fare Tuḡuziro  
\r (Mataio 10:5-15; Mareko 6:7-13)  
\p
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare huze nuꞌoziro. Ebu vine sauꞌa niduꞌa hegoze buzeꞌeteꞌe zu ugi nunu faineꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa zu inaraḡa ziniro.  
\v 2 Ebu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo haramozenoga zu ugi azaḡa faizoga veize tuḡuziro.  
\v 3 Aniꞌa ziro, “Zae ragavo zamaḡano ḡau ꞌahoga ago moꞌi. Tuḡu, nihara, ogomu, hadi zu dabua ꞌahoga ago odohoꞌi.  
\v 4 Noꞌe neḡa diuḡoꞌidene, eꞌea daꞌo radoꞌi, onamo ne eꞌe mode iḡunoꞌi.  
\v 5 Ne azaḡaniꞌa zae mene mae zouzadu za ne eꞌe modoꞌidene, odaze huꞌuruḡa zauhe mode manahoꞌi. ꞌOuge haḡadu zeḡeꞌa zae mazao sauꞌa haḡairoteꞌe ihoziꞌuma.”  
\v 6 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa iḡunadu neḡaneḡa ragave onameꞌenaꞌa, haba niduꞌa zamaḡano hari manoḡa haramiro zu ugi azaḡa faiziro.   
\s1 Herodaꞌa Iesu moneo ꞌAdaꞌadaniro  
\r (Mataio 14:1-12; Mareko 6:14-29)  
\p
\v 7 Galilea habaꞌa kiniḡa, Herodaꞌa Iesu moneo hari niduꞌa igirotene, zamaḡaniꞌa ꞌadaꞌadaniro. Mazaḡa vaze nuꞌe ꞌahige rae reiro, “Iesuꞌe Ioane Babatiso. Aniꞌa rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡabodeha,”  
\v 8 ebu vaze nuꞌe raenaꞌa, “Aniꞌe Elia. Ani bare fureraneha,” ebu vaze nuꞌe raenaꞌa, “Amahi peroveta azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa bare ḡabodeha.”  
\v 9 Rehano Herodaꞌe ꞌahige rae reiro, “Ioaneꞌe eḡeꞌa ꞌunuḡa variꞌe riꞌadu gouniro. Ze iniu moneo ꞌouge ḡoereꞌohe?” Ebu ani Iesu ḡianihi reiro.   
\s1 Vaze 5,000 Ḡubuziro  
\r (Mataio 14:13-21; Mareko 6:30-44; Ioane 6:1-14)  
\p
\v 10 Apostolo azaḡaniꞌa Iesu vaḡe bare arirotene, zeḡeꞌa nagini haḡairoteꞌe niduꞌa Iesu meꞌodoharo. Ebu Iesuꞌa zeḡe teite daꞌo vaḡinadu Betesaida onamiro.  
\v 11 Rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa aniꞌe noꞌe onameꞌeteꞌe ederadu ani hegotiro. Ebu Iesuꞌa ze mae ḡihizadu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo haramiro, zu ugize fainiteꞌe azaḡa faiziro.   
\p
\v 12 Ḡoravararotene, Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fareꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu niro, “ꞌAhiꞌe haba bohaꞌa. Ogomu vaḡoga ebu ohere bazoga veize vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ne uhiḡauhiḡano tuḡuze vaḡizoꞌi.”  
\v 13 Rehano Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaeꞌa ogomu zenoꞌi.” Ebu zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Eme mazaoꞌe ꞌuvahu odoga fuꞌo ebu ḡozone aheu daꞌo. Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ꞌahi ḡubuzoga veize, emeꞌa onamadu ogomu hoitiꞌumahe?”  
\v 14 Eꞌea vaze niduꞌa boꞌaḡano ohoze niduꞌa daꞌoꞌe 5,000.  
\p Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Zeꞌa vaze 50 rovonerovone ehorifine ihozoꞌi.”  
\v 15 Ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ihozadu vaze niduꞌa ꞌouge ehoriro.  
\v 16 Eꞌe ḡarugano Iesuꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga fuꞌo zu ḡozone aheu madu adure ḡianeꞌenaꞌa, Badiꞌa mazao manoḡa tauḡi rae reiro. Ebu ꞌuvahu odoga zu ḡozone tahitahe vahegadu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziniro, ebu ze vaze niduꞌa ḡahuge ziniro.  
\v 17 ꞌOugadu zeḡe niduꞌa au ubararo. Ebu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ogomu ḡahaꞌaḡahaꞌaꞌe nuꞌonadu tunahu niduꞌa gaubanana aheu fare iri'avoniro.   
\s1 Peteroꞌa Iesuꞌe Keriso rae Reiro  
\r (Mataio 16:13-20; Mareko 8:27-30)  
\p
\v 18 Mada ꞌahogano Iesuꞌe ane daꞌo kurau radiro, ebu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe ane teite radiro. Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “Vazeꞌa eꞌe iniu rae raꞌohe?”  
\v 19 Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Vaze nuꞌe ḡaꞌe Ioane Babatiso, nuꞌe Elia, ebu nuꞌe amahi peroveta azaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa ḡabode iḡuniro rae raꞌohe.”  
\v 20 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “U zaꞌe eꞌe iniu rae raꞌohe?” Peteroꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa tuḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡa, Keriso.”  
\v 21 Ebu aniꞌa ḡoere riḡa ziro, “Ḡoere ꞌahi vazeni ꞌahoga ago noꞌi.”   
\s1 Iesu Rune moneo Ihoziro  
\r (Mataio 16:21-28; Mareko 8:31-9:1)  
\p
\v 22 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Vaze Ubuganiꞌa aduga ḡehaḡa hidiꞌuma. Ebu vaze boroboro, dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa hezahohaꞌuma zu goruniꞌuma. Ebu aniꞌa mada uḡiduḡano bare ḡabodiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 23 Ebu hena Iesuꞌa zeḡe niduꞌa ziro, “Iniuꞌa eḡe ḡaruna hegotihi rae roꞌidene, ane ura niduꞌa modadu mada niduꞌa ane satauro odoheꞌenaꞌa, eḡe hegotoꞌi.  
\v 24 Mazaḡa iniu ane ḡabone obone giganine, ani ḡabone tuḡutuḡu mene hidiꞌuma. Rehano iniu ane ḡabone eḡe veize ahetine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma.  
\v 25 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa haba niduꞌa madu ḡaboneḡa daunine ga mae vaḡinine, nagi manoḡa hidiꞌuma?  
\v 26 Iniuꞌa eḡe zu eḡe ḡoere uꞌano mazagaronine, Vaze Ubuga zuni ane agaḡano, Moga agaḡano ebu tuḡure viga zaḡoḡa niduꞌa agaḡano ariteꞌe madaḡano vaze eꞌe uꞌano mazagaroniꞌuma.  
\v 27 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, izidi ꞌada edau radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze nuꞌa ꞌizema rudanogano Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe horoniꞌuma.”   
\s1 Iesu Iraḡaniꞌa Nufiro  
\r (Mataio 17:1-8; Mareko 9:2-8)  
\p
\v 28 Iesuꞌa ꞌouge ziroteꞌe enogano mada fuꞌo uḡidu fare meiro. Aniꞌa Petero, Ioane zu Iakobo zamazadu kuranoga veize maḡa ꞌahoga itiro.  
\v 29 Ani kurauꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano, iraḡaniꞌa nufiro zu dabuaḡaniꞌa ꞌuranadu vazavazahiro.  
\v 30 Eꞌe madaḡano vaze aheu, Mose zu Eliaꞌa fureranadu Iesu teite ḡoeriro.  
\v 31 Ze agaḡa boro zamaḡano fureraro, ebu Iesuꞌa Ierusalema onamadu eꞌea haḡaiteꞌe haḡaiḡa, ane rune moneo ḡoeriro.  
\v 32 Petero zu Iesu tahiꞌa aheuꞌe baze rudaro. Ebu ze evatirotene Iesu agaḡa zu ani uhiḡano vaze aheuꞌa edau radiuꞌeteꞌe horoziro.  
\v 33 Mose ebu Eliaꞌa Iesu muhinihi reirotene, Peteroꞌa Iesu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, eme ꞌahao radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe manoḡa. Emeḡe uḡiduꞌa nugo taruha uḡidu ogoratihi, tibaꞌe ḡae veize, tibaꞌe Mose veize, ebu tibaꞌe Elia veize.” Peteroꞌe aniꞌa nagini raꞌeteꞌe mene ederiro.   
\p
\v 34 Aniꞌa ꞌize ḡoereꞌeteꞌea, ḡozeꞌa ovadu ogoziro ebu ze ḡoze zamaḡano diuḡadu rihau rudaro.  
\v 35 Ebu ḡozeonoꞌo ago ꞌahoganiꞌa buanadu ziro, “ꞌAhiꞌe eḡe Ubude, eḡeꞌa ohotiroteꞌe vazeḡa. Za ani ḡoere egohanoꞌi.”  
\v 36 Ago eꞌeꞌa hauḡirotene, ze Iesu daꞌo horoniro. Ane tahiꞌa uḡiduꞌa sifu radiuꞌenaꞌa, ze nagini horoniroteꞌe vazeni ꞌahoga mazao mada nu mene rae fureniro.   
\s1 Tahiꞌa Komeꞌa Vine Sauꞌaḡeta Fainiro  
\r (Mataio 17:14-18; Mareko 9:14-27)  
\p
\v 37 Irarirotene, Iesu zu ane tahiꞌa uḡiduꞌa maḡanonoꞌo ovairo ebu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa hidiro.  
\v 38 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu huniro, “Ihore vazeḡa, e ḡa umiꞌeꞌohe. Eḡe ubude tibuhuga ꞌadi ḡabonoꞌi.  
\v 39 Vine sauꞌaniꞌa ani agatohauꞌetene, aniꞌe tabara ḡaniḡanauꞌenaꞌa, beroꞌudeꞌohe zu hebeꞌanonoꞌo busureꞌohe. Vine sauꞌaniꞌa mada niduꞌa ani zamaḡano radiuꞌenaꞌa, ahiꞌa sausauneꞌohe.  
\v 40 Eḡeꞌa ḡae tahiꞌatahiꞌa mazao vine sauꞌa eꞌe hegone bunoga radu umizeha, rehano ze mene idaraneha.”   
\p
\v 41 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Zaꞌe Badiꞌa mazao mene fiꞌeꞌeteꞌe zu veꞌoḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa! E noꞌe faḡa zae teite radiꞌuma, zu zae mazao zamahe obone tiꞌma?” Ebu tahiꞌa eꞌe moga niro, “Ubugo tutune ꞌahi aroꞌi.”  
\v 42 Ebu tahiꞌa eꞌeꞌa Iesu vaḡe areꞌeteꞌea, vine sauꞌaniꞌa ane agatohanadu ani higau bauriro zu beroꞌudiro. ꞌOugirotene, Iesuꞌa vine sauꞌa ronadu tahiꞌa eꞌe fainiro ebu ani moga bare haro.  
\v 43 Ebu vaze niduꞌa Badiꞌa gigiꞌaḡa boro horonadu zaguzagaro.  
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Rune moneo Bare Reiro  
\r (Mataio 17:22-23; Mareko 9:30-32)  
\p Vaze niduꞌa Iesuꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa horonadu zaguzagarotene, Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro,  
\v 44 “Ḡoere ꞌadi faifaine egoꞌi. Vaze Ubugaꞌe agireḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌiniꞌuma.”  
\v 45 Rehano Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe ane ḡoere huga mene ederiro, mazaḡa ḡoere huga aꞌe ꞌuꞌuruḡa radu aniꞌa nagini zirotaꞌaꞌe mene ederiro. Ebu ze ane ḡoere moneo bare ḡadimanoga zuni riharo.   
\s1 Iniuꞌe Ḡihiꞌa Hune?  
\r (Mataio 18:1-5; Mareko 9:33-37)  
\p
\v 46 Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌa boꞌaḡano iniuꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune radu ze zeḡeꞌa bare taꞌirotitiro.  
\v 47 Iesuꞌa ze nagini zamareꞌeteꞌe ederadu tahiꞌa komeꞌa ꞌahoga zamaharo ebu ane babaḡano ohoniro.  
\v 48 Aniꞌa ziro, “Iniuꞌa eḡe niḡano tahiꞌa komeꞌa ꞌahiguḡa mae ḡihinine, aniꞌe eḡe mae ḡihiheꞌohe. Ebu iniuꞌa eḡe mae ḡihihine, aniꞌe eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa mae ḡihineꞌohe. Zae boaḡano iniuꞌa aneꞌa bare niḡa mae ovoine, aniꞌe vaze ḡihiꞌa hune.”   
\s1 Emeḡe none Vazeḡa  
\r (Mareko 9:38-40)  
\p
\v 49 Ioaneꞌa Iesu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, eme vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ḡae niḡano vine sauꞌasauꞌa hegoze buziroteꞌe horoniro. ꞌOugadu eme ani garariro, mazaḡa aniꞌe mene emeḡe none vazeḡa.”  
\v 50 Rehano Iesuꞌa niro, “Ani ago gararoꞌi. Za mene agiroziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe zae mone vazeḡa.”   
\s1 Samaria Azaḡaniꞌa Iesu Hezahoharo  
\p
\v 51 Iesuꞌe adure ititeꞌe madaḡaniꞌa hanitirotene, ani Ierusalema onamihi radu zamaḡa ohoniro.  
\v 52 Ebu ani vaze nu ibite tuḡuzadu ze ani veize ḡau nu ruhibifine Samaria azaḡa habaꞌano ne ꞌahoga diuḡiro.  
\v 53 Rehano Iesuꞌe Ierusalema onamihi reiro ꞌahine, ne azaḡaniꞌa ani mene mae ḡihiniro.  
\v 54 Iesu tahiꞌa aheu, Iakobo zu Ioaneꞌa horonadu Iesu ḡadiniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡa emeꞌa Badiꞌa uminadu adureonoꞌo ire roga tuḡunoga zu ze hufi haozoga urateꞌehe?”  
\v 55 Rehano ani tehadu roziro.  
\v 56 Ebu ze ne ꞌahoga onamiro.   
\s1 Iesu Hegoteꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa  
\r (Mataio 8:19-22)  
\p
\v 57 Ze ibio onameꞌeteꞌea, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa aradu Iesu niro, “Ḡaeꞌa noꞌe onamine, e ḡa hegotiꞌuma.”  
\v 58 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Butu ḡuniḡaꞌe bazuni habaꞌazeta, ebu hitana niniḡaꞌe nezeta. Rehano Vaze Ubugaꞌe bazuni habaꞌa oꞌoꞌa.”   
\p
\v 59 Ebu Iesuꞌa vaze ꞌahoga niro, “Eḡe hegotoꞌi.” Rehano vaze eꞌeꞌa naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, e ibite geno mamahe guri onamihi.”  
\v 60 Rehano Iesuꞌa niro, “Rune azaḡaniꞌa rune azaḡa guriꞌuma. U ḡaꞌe onamadu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo rae furenoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 61 Ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, e ḡa hegotiꞌuma. Rehano e ibite geno negohe nabudihe uhizi onamihi.”  
\v 62 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Iniuꞌa teheꞌenaꞌa mebaḡa afidaune, mene faine afidaꞌuma. Eꞌe teige, iniuꞌa teheꞌenaꞌa, gau nunu zamarine, aniꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌazoga veize gauogaꞌe mene idaḡa.”   
\c 10  
\s1 Iesuꞌa Tahiꞌa 72 Tuḡuziro  
\p
\v 1 Eꞌe enogano, Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa vaze ꞌahoga 72 ohozadu aneꞌa onamihi reiroteꞌe neḡa niduꞌa zu habaꞌa niduꞌa aheuaheu ibite tuḡuziro.  
\v 2 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Hiriviteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe ḡehaḡa bagaḡa, rehano gau azaḡaꞌe tahiḡa. Eꞌanoꞌo hiriveꞌeteꞌe Zuhiꞌaḡa Boro mazao gau azaḡa ane mebao tuḡuzoga veize uminoꞌi.  
\v 3 Onamoꞌi. Butu ḡuniḡa boꞌaḡano mamoe tuḡuzeꞌeteꞌe teige, e za agire azaḡa boꞌaḡano tuḡuzeꞌohe.  
\v 4 Hadi niharaḡa ga fuse ga tamaka ago odohoꞌi. Ebu ibio vaze ꞌahoga hidoꞌidene, ani teite faḡa ḡoereꞌenaꞌa, mada ago hauḡoꞌi.   
\p
\v 5 Vaze ꞌahoga ne diuḡoꞌidene, ibite geno ꞌahige roꞌi, 'Badiꞌaꞌa zama roḡeḡa zenoꞌi.'  
\v 6 Ne eꞌe zamaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa zama roḡeḡa urateꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa reine, zaꞌa rateꞌe zama roḡeḡaꞌe ani rana radiꞌuma. U mene reine, zama roḡeḡa eꞌeꞌa zae bare vaḡiꞌuma.  
\v 7 Ne tiba zamaḡano daꞌo radoꞌi, ebu zeḡeꞌa ziniꞌeteꞌe ogomuḡa anoꞌi zu gagoꞌi, mazaḡa gau azaḡaniꞌa gauze naeḡa meꞌuma. Ne ꞌahogaꞌahogano ago ragave onamoꞌi.   
\p
\v 8 Ne ꞌahoga onamadu za mae ḡihizoꞌidene, nagi ogomu ziniꞌeteꞌe anoꞌi.  
\v 9 Ebu eꞌea ugi azaḡa faizadu ꞌahige haramozenoꞌi, 'Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa zae mazao haniteha.'  
\v 10 Rehano ne ꞌahoga onamadu za mene mae ḡihizoꞌidene, ne ibi boro onamoꞌi,  
\v 11 ebu ꞌahige zoꞌi, 'Badiꞌaꞌa zae haḡai sauꞌa ederifine, eme zae haba konoḡa odafeo kadaranateꞌe ꞌada zauhe modadu iḡuneꞌohe. Rehano ederoꞌi, Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa haniteha.'”  
\v 12 Ebu Iesuꞌa bare ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, Badiꞌa kota madaḡano za mene mae ḡihiziroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Sodoma azaḡa ufeta vitize aduga boro hidiꞌuma.   
\s1 Haḡai Sauꞌanonoꞌo Mene Ḡihureꞌeteꞌe Habaꞌa  
\r (Mataio 11:20-24)  
\p
\v 13 “Korasini azaḡa, za aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Betesaida azaḡa, za aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Eḡeꞌa zae mazao haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa gigiꞌaꞌe Turo zu Sidono azaḡa mazao haḡaifone, ze dabuaze ḡuꞌa vidau ehoradu vega vadinizeo ase ḡuzuheꞌenaꞌa, haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihurifo.  
\v 14 Rehano Badiꞌa kota madaḡano zaꞌe Turo zu Sidono azaḡa ufeta vitize aduga boro hidiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 15 Kaperanauma azaḡa, zaꞌe adureo Badiꞌa habaꞌa tutuze itiꞌuma rae zamareꞌehe? Mene! Zaꞌe rune habaꞌano mae feuziꞌuma.  
\v 16 Za egoziniꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe egoniꞌohe, ebu za hezahoziniꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe hezahoniꞌohe. Ebu eḡe hezahohiꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe tuḡuhiroteꞌe Badiꞌaḡa hezahohauꞌohe.”   
\s1 Iesu Tahiꞌaḡa 72ꞌa Bariro  
\p
\v 17 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌa 72 onamadu Iesu vaḡe barirotene, matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eme ḡae niḡano vine sauꞌa hegoze buzirotene, ze emeḡe ḡoere egofiro.”  
\v 18 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Vazabu agaḡa teige, Sataniꞌa adureonoꞌo ḡarihe fase buauꞌeteꞌe horoniro.  
\v 19 Ḡianoꞌi, e zaeꞌa mohe zu asiasi edeze ruzeꞌeteꞌe zu emeḡe agire Satani gigiꞌaḡa raharahaneꞌeteꞌe inaraḡa ziniro. Ḡau ꞌahoganiꞌa za mene sausauziꞌuma.  
\v 20 Rehano vine sauꞌasauꞌaniꞌa zae ḡoere egoziniꞌeteꞌe uꞌano ago matuꞌoꞌi, rehano zae niꞌe adureo mirihiroteꞌe uꞌano matuꞌoꞌi.”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Matuꞌe Kuraro  
\r (Mataio 11:25-27, 13:16-17)  
\p
\v 21 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesuꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa iriꞌavonadu matuꞌe rudaro, ebu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Mama, ḡaꞌe adure zu raha Zuhiꞌaḡa. E niguꞌeꞌohe, mazaḡa ḡaeꞌa vaze huhuzaḡa zu edeḡa boro azaḡa mazaoꞌe ḡoere huga ꞌahiguḡa ꞌuꞌuru tiro, rehano tahiꞌa komeꞌa teigeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazaoꞌe rae fureniro. Mama, a hube, ꞌouge haḡairotaꞌaꞌe ḡae ura.  
\v 22 Eḡe Mamaꞌa ḡau niduꞌa eḡe iniro. Vazeni ꞌahoga Ubuga aḡuꞌa, rehano Moga daꞌo Ubuga edeḡa. Ebu vazeni ꞌahoga Moga aḡuꞌa, rehano Ubuga daꞌo zu Ubuganiꞌa Moga moneo ihozoga veize ohotiroteꞌe azaḡa daꞌo Moga edeḡa.”   
\p
\v 23 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa tehe ḡiazadu sifu ziro, “Zaꞌe matuꞌoꞌi, mazaḡa naginiꞌa fureruꞌeteꞌe ubumaze hina horoneꞌohe.  
\v 24 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, peroveta azaḡa zu kini azaḡaꞌe zaeꞌa izidi nagini horoneꞌeteꞌe horonihi rae reiro, rehano mene horoniro, ebu zaeꞌa izidi nagini igiꞌeteꞌe igihi rae reiro, rehano mene igiro.”   
\s1 Samaria Vazeḡa Manoḡa Hari Idaidaḡa  
\p
\v 25 Mada ꞌahogano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa iḡunadu Iesu tuhune nuroga veize ḡadiniro, “Ihore vazeḡa, e nougine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma?”  
\v 26 Iesuꞌa niro, “Mose goro ḡoeꞌanoꞌe nouge rae mirihiro? Ḡa nougenouge meꞌode horoneꞌohe?”  
\v 27 Aniꞌa naenaeniro, “Mose goro ḡoeꞌano ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Zamaḡo niduꞌa hina, vineḡo niduꞌa hina, inaraḡo niduꞌa hina zu zamaroneḡo niduꞌa hina ḡae Badiꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro zamare borofoꞌi,' ebu 'Ḡa ḡae bare zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe teige, nabugo zamare borofoꞌi.'”  
\v 28 Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡae naenaeꞌe duduḡa. Ḡa ꞌouge haḡaine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 29 Rehano ani Iesuꞌa ani mazao duduḡa rae rouga uratadu bare ḡadiniro, “Iniuꞌe eḡe nabudi?”  
\v 30 Iesuꞌa ꞌahige naenaeniro,  
\p “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Ierusalemaonoꞌo Ieriko ovoinu. Ebu ibio aniꞌe ḡonore azaḡa hidiro. Ze dabuaḡa fuhiꞌadu ḡauḡa niduꞌa meiro, zu bounadu nariga mau runiro, ebu eꞌea bazune mode feraro.  
\v 31 Eꞌe madaḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa eꞌe ibiḡano ovoiro. Ebu vaze eꞌe horonirotene, ibi genaḡano vitau onamiro.  
\v 32 Eꞌe teige, Levi mariga vazeḡa\f + \fr 10:32 \ft Levi marigaꞌe kuru neḡano gauiro. \f* ꞌahoga zuni eꞌe ibiḡano ovoadu vaze eꞌe horoniro, rehano ane zuni ibi genaḡano vitau onamiro.  
\v 33 Rehano Samaria vazeḡa ꞌahogaꞌe ragave onameꞌeteꞌea, eꞌe ibiḡano ovoadu vaze eꞌe horoniro ebu vetuḡani runiro.  
\v 34 Ebu ane vaḡe onamadu dehoro zu vaini vuḡa hina idiriḡa rana beuꞌadu ꞌumiro. Ebu ane doniki rana mae ohonadu iꞌudo neḡa tutune onamiro, zu eꞌea ani taufe radiro.  
\v 35 Irarirotene, aniꞌa hadi nu\f + \fr 10:35 \fqa denari aheu. \ft Aꞌe mada aheu gauḡa naeḡa. \f* madu iꞌudo neḡa vazeḡa hanadu niro, 'Ani taufe radoꞌi. Hadi ꞌahiꞌe mene idaḡa roꞌidene, eḡeꞌa baradu bare ḡaniꞌuma.'”   
\p
\v 36 Iesuꞌa eꞌe hariḡa hauḡirotene, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ḡadiniro, “Vaze uḡidu ꞌadi boꞌaḡano ḡae zamaroneꞌe iniuꞌe ḡonore azaḡa hidiroteꞌe vazeḡa nabuga?”  
\v 37 Aniꞌa naenaeniro, “Ani vetuḡaneadu dananiroteꞌe vazeḡa.” Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡa zuni onamadu ꞌouge haḡaoꞌi.” \fig Samaria vazeḡa manoḡa|src="DN00479b.tif" size="col" ref="10:37" \fig*   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Mareta zu Maria Ne Diuḡiro  
\p
\v 38 Iesu zu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ragave onamadu ne ꞌahogano feuriro. Ebu roḡae ꞌahoga, niḡa Maretaꞌa neḡano Iesu mae zouniro.  
\v 39 Maretaꞌe negoḡeta zu niḡaꞌe Maria. Mariaꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boro oda babaḡano ehoradu nagini reiroteꞌe igi radiro.  
\v 40 U Maretaꞌe vaze ḡubuzoga veize gau ḡehaḡa haḡainuteꞌe uꞌano zamaḡaniꞌa adudaro. Eꞌanoꞌo ani Iesu vaḡe aradu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, negoheꞌa eḡe daꞌo gaueꞌeteꞌe horohe tauḡeꞌohe. Ḡa eꞌe mene zamareꞌehe? Ani e danahoga veize noꞌi!”   
\p
\v 41 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa naenaeniro, “Mareta, Mareta, ḡaꞌe gau ḡehaḡa uꞌano zamaḡoꞌe aduduꞌohe zu maḡuneꞌohe.  
\v 42 Rehano gau boroꞌe tiba daꞌo, ebu Mariaꞌa gau eꞌe ohotiro. Eꞌanoꞌo vazeni ꞌahoga aniꞌa ꞌouge haḡaeꞌeteꞌe mene garariꞌuma.”   
\c 11  
\s1 Iesuꞌa Kuru Ihoziro  
\r (Mataio 6:9-15, 7:7-11)  
\p
\v 1 Mada ꞌahogano Iesuꞌe haba ꞌahogano kurau radiro. Kuru hauḡirotene, ane tahiꞌa ꞌahoganiꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, Ioane Babatisoꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa kuru ihoziroteꞌe teige, emeḡe zuni kuru ihofoꞌi.”  
\v 2 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe kuranoꞌidene, ꞌahige kuranoꞌi:  
\q1 'Mama,  
\q1 eme umiꞌeꞌohe, ḡae niꞌe zaḡoḡa reꞌuma,  
\q1 ebu ḡaeꞌa ḡau niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌuma.   
\q1
\v 3 Mada niduꞌa emeḡeꞌa atiteꞌe ogomuḡa rifiꞌenoꞌi,   
\q1
\v 4 ebu emeꞌa emeḡe mazao sauꞌa haḡairoteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa haḡaize sauꞌa rae modeꞌeteꞌe teige,  
\q2 emeḡe haḡai sauꞌa rae modoꞌi.  
\q1 Ebu eme haḡai sauꞌa haḡaihi raꞌeteꞌe zamaroneḡanonoꞌo mae tutufe vaḡifoꞌi.'”   
\p
\v 5 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Hari idaidaḡa ꞌahi zamaroꞌi. Zae boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahogaꞌe nabudiḡeta. Ohe nema ꞌahogano nabuganiꞌa ane vaze ne onamadu uminiro, 'Eḡe vaze, ꞌuvahu odoga uḡidu enoꞌi,  
\v 6 mazaḡa eḡe vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ragaveꞌeteꞌea iziduꞌu eḡe vaḡe areha, rehano e hatiteꞌe ogomuḡa oꞌoꞌa.'  
\v 7 Ebu ne vazeḡaniꞌa naenaeniro, 'Zamahe ago adudunoꞌi. Ibiheta ꞌai bireha, ebu e eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite bazeꞌe ꞌahine, iḡunadu ḡau ꞌahoga ḡanogaꞌe mene idaḡa.'” Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ḡadiziro, “Za zuni ꞌouge naenaeniꞌumahe?  
\v 8 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, aniꞌe nabuga veize daꞌoꞌe iḡunadu ꞌuvahu odoga mene haꞌuma, rehano nabuganiꞌa barebare umineꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, iḡunadu umideꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa haꞌuma.   
\p
\v 9 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, uminoꞌi, ꞌougine ziniꞌuma. Vaḡoꞌi, ꞌougine horoniꞌuma. Ibiheta toketokeroꞌi, ꞌougine ibiheta vavaoziniꞌuma.  
\v 10 Umineꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ziniꞌuma, vaḡeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa horoniꞌuma, ebu ibiheta toketokereꞌeteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌa ibiheta vavaoziniꞌuma.  
\v 11 Zae boꞌaḡano iniu ubuganiꞌa ḡozone umidine, moganiꞌa ḡozone mene hanadu mohe haꞌumahe?  
\v 12 Ebu ubuganiꞌa kokoroku maḡa umidine, moganiꞌa asiasi haꞌumahe?  
\v 13 Zaꞌe sauꞌa azaḡa rehano, ḡahunone manoḡa ubudeze zenoga urateꞌohe. Eꞌe teige, zae Moze adureo radiuꞌetaꞌaꞌe ane mazao umideꞌeteꞌe azaḡa hube hune Vine Zaḡoḡa ziniꞌuma.”   
\s1 Iesu zu Belezebulo  
\r (Mataio 12:22-30; Mareko 3:20-27)  
\p
\v 14 Mada ꞌahogano Iesuꞌa mumutafa vazeḡa ꞌahoga mazaonoꞌo vine sauꞌa hegone buniro. Vine sauꞌaniꞌa ani mode buarotene, mumutafa vazeḡaniꞌa bare ḡoeriro ebu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa zaguzagaro.  
\v 15 Rehano vaze nuꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Iesuꞌa vine sauꞌasauꞌa zuhiꞌaḡa, Belezebulo inaraḡa hina vine sauꞌasauꞌa hegoze buzeꞌohe.”  
\v 16 U nuꞌe Iesu tuhune nurihi radu uminiro, “Badiꞌa gigiꞌaḡa hina haḡai nu badeḡa haḡaoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 17 Rehano Iesuꞌa ze nouge rae zamarirotaꞌaꞌe ederadu ziro, “Haba tiba zamaḡano zeḡeꞌa rovotadu utitine, eꞌe habaꞌaꞌe aneꞌa bare ruiniꞌuma. Ebu ne tiba zamaḡano zeḡeꞌa rovotadu utitine, ne eꞌe aneꞌa bare higaꞌuma.  
\v 18 Sataniꞌe aneꞌa bare rovonadu ane zamaḡano utitine, aneꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe habaꞌaꞌe nougenouge edau gigaraꞌuma? Zaꞌe eḡeꞌa Belezebulo inaraḡa hina vine sauꞌa hegone buneꞌohe rae raꞌohe, rehano ꞌougine ani aneꞌa bare ruiniꞌuma.  
\v 19 Eḡeꞌa Belezebulo inaraḡa hina vine sauꞌa hegoze buzifone, zae tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe iniu inara hina vine sauꞌa hegoze buzifo? Zae tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare zaꞌe veꞌoḡa rae reꞌuma.  
\v 20 Rehano eḡeꞌa vine sauꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa inaraḡa hina hegoze buzine, Badiꞌaꞌa amahi zae zuhiꞌazi radiuꞌohe.   
\p
\v 21 Inara vazeḡaniꞌa uti ḡauḡa nunu hina neḡa taufine, ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe manoḡa radiꞌuma.  
\v 22 Rehano inara ufeta boro vazeḡaniꞌa arine, inara vazeḡa utite raharahaniꞌuma. Inara vazeḡaꞌe uti ḡauḡaniꞌa ani biriꞌuma rae zamariꞌuma. Rehano inara ufeta boro vazeḡaniꞌa inara vazeḡa uti ḡauḡa meiniꞌuma ebu ani ne ḡau niduꞌa zuni meinadu ḡahuge ḡuzuhiꞌuma.  
\v 23 Iniu eḡe teite mene reine, aniꞌe eḡe agirohiꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Ebu iniu eḡe teite Badiꞌa veize vaze mene nuꞌozine, ani Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo vaze rovozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa.”   
\s1 Vine Sauꞌaniꞌa Bariro  
\r (Mataio 12:43-45)  
\p
\v 24 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Vine sauꞌa ꞌahoganiꞌa vaze ꞌahoga mazaonoꞌo buauꞌetene, ahiꞌa ohonoga radu vu oꞌoꞌa habaꞌa vaḡe ragaveꞌohe. Rehano mene horoneꞌetene, ani ꞌahige rae raꞌohe, 'Eḡeꞌa ibite radiroteꞌe neḡa bare onamihi.'  
\v 25 Ebu ani baradu vaze eꞌe horoneꞌetene, aniꞌe neḡa deheḡa hune zu idaidane touga heuḡa.  
\v 26 Ebu vine sauꞌa eꞌeꞌa onamadu vine sauꞌa niduꞌa fuꞌo aheu fare, ufeta hune sauꞌa zamaze areꞌohe, ebu ze vaze eꞌe zamaḡano diuḡe radiuꞌohe. ꞌOugadu vaze eꞌeꞌa mada ibiꞌa vitine ufeta sautuꞌohe.”   
\s1 Matuꞌu Huga  
\p
\v 27 Iesuꞌa ḡoere eꞌe raꞌeteꞌea, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa boꞌaḡano roḡae ꞌahoganiꞌa agoḡa boro hina Iesu niro, “Ḡa fureꞌiroteꞌe zu ḡubuꞌe borofiroteꞌe roḡaeḡaniꞌa matuꞌe rudauꞌohe!”  
\v 28 Rehano Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Badiꞌa ḡoere egohauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa matuꞌe rudauꞌohe.”   
\s1 Iona Haḡai Nu Badeḡa  
\r (Mataio 12:38-42; Mareko 8:12)  
\p
\v 29 Iesu vaḡe ariroteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ufeta ḡehararotene, Iesuꞌa ziro, “Izidi egaꞌe sauꞌa, ebu ze haḡai nu badeḡa umideꞌohe. Rehano Iona mazao fureraroteꞌe haḡai nu badeḡa daꞌo furenoziniꞌuma.  
\v 30 Iona mazao naginiꞌa furerarotaꞌaꞌe Nineva azaḡa mazao haḡai nu badeḡa reiro. Eꞌe teige, Vaze Ubuga mazao naginiꞌa fureratitaꞌaꞌe izidi ega mazao haḡai nu badeḡa reꞌuma.  
\v 31 Badiꞌa kota madaḡano Siba habaꞌa kini roḡaeḡaniꞌa izidi ega azaḡa teite iḡune edanadu zeꞌe veꞌoḡa rae roziꞌuma. Mazaḡa ibite madaḡano Siba habaꞌa kini roḡaeḡaniꞌa haba ḡonaga faḡa huneonoꞌo kini Solomona zamarone huhuzaḡa abitoga veize onamiro. U izidi Solomona vitinoga vazeḡaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe, rehano ze ane ḡoere abitoga mene urateꞌohe.  
\v 32 Badiꞌa kota madaḡano Nineva azaḡaniꞌa izidi ega azaḡa teite iḡune edanadu zeꞌe veꞌoḡa rae roziꞌuma. Mazaḡa ibite madaḡano Nineva azaḡaꞌe Iona haramo abitadu haḡaize sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihure ḡouriro. Izidi Iona vitinoga vazeḡaꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe, rehano ze ane ḡoere mene abitadu mene ḡihureꞌohe.”   
\s1 Ahiri Agaḡa  
\r (Mataio 5:15, 6:22-23)  
\p
\v 33 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ihure hofadu mene ꞌuꞌuru tiꞌe ga siuva hina mene ogone tiꞌohe. Rehano ne diuḡeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa agaḡa horonoga veize ihure odaḡa rana tiꞌohe.  
\v 34 Zae ubumaꞌe ahirize ihureḡa. Ubumazeꞌe manoḡa reine, ahirizeꞌe agaḡaniꞌa iriꞌavoniꞌuma. Rehano ubumazeꞌe sauꞌa reine, ahirizeꞌe uzaboꞌa iriꞌavoniꞌuma.  
\v 35 Eꞌanoꞌo zae zamao agaḡaꞌe uzabo ga meneꞌe faine ḡianoꞌi.  
\v 36 Zae ahiriꞌe agaḡaniꞌa iriꞌavonadu uzabo ꞌahoga oꞌoꞌa reine, ihure agaḡaniꞌa zae rana agaruꞌeteꞌe teige, ahirize niduꞌaꞌe agaḡaniꞌa iriꞌavoniꞌuma.”   
\s1 Farisea Azaḡa zu Mose Goro Ḡoeꞌa Ihozeꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa Roziro  
\r (Mataio 23:1-36; Mareko 12:38-40; Luka 20:45-47)  
\p
\v 37 Iesuꞌa ḡoere hauḡirotene, Farisea vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ane teite oganoga uminiro. Ebu Iesuꞌa ani ne onamadu ogomu fataḡa uhiḡano ehoriro.  
\v 38 Ebu Farisea vazeḡaꞌe Iesuꞌa ꞌizema oganogano ꞌevoꞌa mene vuzuꞌiroteꞌe horonirotene zaguzagaro.  
\v 39 Ebu Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa Farisea vazeḡa eꞌe niro, “Farisea azaḡa, izidi zaꞌe bioze zu siuvaze enoga daꞌo vuzuꞌe deheneꞌohe. Rehano zamazeoꞌe ununu zu sauꞌaniꞌa iriꞌaveꞌohe.  
\v 40 Zaꞌe mene huhuzaḡa! Badiꞌaꞌa enone daꞌo mene haḡairo, rehano zama zuni haḡairo.  
\v 41 Eꞌanoꞌo ḡauze zahara azaḡa zenoꞌi, ꞌougine zae enone zu zama niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa ubumao deheḡa hune reꞌuma.   
\p
\v 42 Farisea azaḡa, za aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Mazaḡa zaꞌe tirara mebaḡano eḡa zu murari teige komeꞌa fase ogomuḡa niduꞌaonoꞌo sinu gaubananao rovonadu sinu tiba ḡauḡa Badiꞌa hauꞌohe. Rehano haḡai duduḡa haḡaoga zu Badiꞌa zamare borofogaꞌe igi modeꞌohe. Za ḡau boro ꞌadiꞌe haḡaifo ebu komeꞌakomeꞌa zuni mene igi modifo.  
\v 43 Farisea azaḡa, zaꞌe aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Mazaḡa zaꞌe nu'onu'o neḡano vaze boroboroꞌa ehoreꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano ehoroga urateꞌohe, zu vaze ḡehaḡa habaꞌano ze zae gubazeꞌenaꞌa, zae mazao unihoga urateꞌohe.  
\v 44 Zaꞌe aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Mazaḡa zaꞌe rune iduḡa ꞌuꞌuruḡa heuḡa. Rune ahiꞌaꞌe idu zamaḡano ruhuḡa rehano, vazeꞌa mene ederadu eꞌe rana oname onaeꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 45 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, ḡa ꞌouge ḡoereꞌetene, emeḡe zuni rae sausaufeꞌohe.”  
\v 46 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, zae zuni aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Mazaḡa zaꞌe ihore riga hune hina vaze aduga boro ziniꞌohe, rehano zae ꞌevore huduꞌa tiba hina zu mene hune danazeꞌohe.  
\v 47 Zaꞌe aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Mazaḡa vouḡazeꞌa ibite zimiroteꞌe peroveta azaḡa rune iduḡa zaeꞌa ogoruꞌohe.  
\v 48 Vouḡazeꞌa peroveta azaḡa zimiro ebu zaeꞌa iduze ogoruꞌohe. ꞌOugadu za vouḡazeꞌa haḡai duduḡa haḡairo rae fureneꞌohe zu ihozeꞌohe.  
\v 49 Eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌa huhuzaḡaniꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Eḡeꞌa peroveta azaḡa zu apostolo azaḡa nu zeḡe mazao tuḡuziꞌuma, rehano ze nuꞌe zimiꞌuma zu nuꞌe sausauziꞌuma.'  
\v 50 Badiꞌaꞌa raha ꞌadi haḡairoteꞌe madaḡanonoꞌo peroveta azaḡa zimiro. Eꞌanoꞌo eꞌe aduga niduꞌaꞌe izidi eganiꞌa odohiꞌuma.  
\v 51 Ze ibite Abela mau runiroteꞌeanoꞌo onao ḡonagano Zekaria maro. Zekariaꞌe dibuꞌo fataḡa zu kuru neḡano Haba Zaḡoḡa boꞌaḡano mau runiro. Oꞌe, eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, eꞌe aduga niduꞌaꞌe izidi eganiꞌa odohiꞌuma.  
\v 52 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa, zaꞌe aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Mazaḡa Badiꞌa edereꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa ibihetaḡa vavaꞌeꞌeteꞌe kiḡaꞌe zaeꞌa meiniro. Rehano za mene diuḡiro ebu diuḡihi raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zuni zaeꞌa garariro.”   
\p
\v 53 Iesuꞌe ḡoere hauḡadu ne beꞌanoꞌo buarotene, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡaniꞌa ani riḡa agiroharo ebu ḡadimu ḡehaḡa hina aduaduniro.  
\v 54 Mazaḡa Iesuꞌa ḡoere nu rae veꞌonine, ani obone tihi rae reiro.   
\c 12  
\s1 Iradugu Ḡoeꞌa Riḡa zu Inara Ḡoeꞌa  
\r (Mataio 10:26-33, 12:32, 10:19-20)  
\p
\v 1 Eꞌe madaḡano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa nuꞌoraro ꞌahine, nariga odaze rana edaro. Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ibite ziro, “Zaꞌe Farisea azaḡa ḡiazoꞌi, mazaḡa zeꞌe zama guhi azaḡa ebu isiti heuḡa.  
\v 2 Rehano ꞌuꞌuru radiroteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌa fureraꞌuma, ebu ogone ḡahiniroteꞌe ḡauḡa zuni ederiꞌuma.  
\v 3 Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌa uzabo zamaḡano nagini sifu reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌaꞌe vazeꞌa mada agaḡano igiꞌuma. Ebu zaꞌe bazuni neḡa zamaḡano nagini gumude reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa vazeꞌa ne binuḡa hitaganonoꞌo rae fureniꞌuma.   
\p
\v 4 Eḡe nego nabudi, eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe. Ahiri mauꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ago rihozoꞌi, mazaḡa zeꞌe vine sausaunogaꞌe mene idaḡa.  
\v 5 U za iniu rihoniteꞌe eḡeꞌa ihoziꞌuma. Aniꞌe vaze manadu ire roga radiu tuḡutuḡu zamaḡano mae feuzeꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa obone tiꞌohe. Ani rihonoꞌi. Hube hune eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, ani daꞌo rihonoꞌi.  
\v 6 Tiburi niniḡa fuꞌo hadi komeꞌa\f + \fr 12:6 \fqa asaria aheu \f* hina seroneꞌohe. Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa zeḡe boꞌaḡano tiba zuni mene aḡutu modeꞌohe.  
\v 7 Badiꞌaꞌa zae zamare borofadu vadinize iguḡa niduꞌa nugu zuni edeḡa. Eꞌano'o ago rihanoꞌi, mazaḡa zaꞌe Badiꞌa ubumao tiburi niniḡa ḡehaḡa ufeta vitize ḡihiꞌaḡa.   
\p
\v 8 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, iniuꞌa vaze ubumao eḡe moneo edaune, Vaze Ubuga zuni Badiꞌa tuḡure viga niduꞌa ubumao ani moneo edaꞌuma.  
\v 9 Rehano iniuꞌa vaze ubumao eḡe oꞌohine, eḡe zuni Badiꞌa tuḡure viga niduꞌa ubumao ani oꞌoniꞌuma.  
\v 10 Iniuꞌa Vaze Ubuga agirohauꞌenaꞌa rae sausaunine, Badiꞌaꞌa ane haḡai sauꞌa rae modiꞌuma, rehano iniuꞌa Vine Zaḡoḡa agirohauꞌenaꞌa rae sausaunine, ane haḡai sauꞌaꞌe mene rae modiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 11 Eḡe uꞌano, zaꞌe kotao tutuze onamadu nu'onu'o neḡano zuhiꞌaḡazuhiꞌaḡa zu inarazeta azaḡa zamao ohozoꞌidene, nougenouge zae bare biriteꞌe ga nagini rae ḡoeriteꞌe moneo zamaze ago adudanoꞌi.  
\v 12 Mazaḡa eꞌe madaḡano zaeꞌa nouge rae ḡoeriteꞌe moneo Vine Zaḡoḡaniꞌa ihoziꞌuma.”   
\s1 Maꞌora Vazeḡa Kauriḡa Hari Idaidaḡa  
\p
\v 13 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa boꞌaḡano Iesu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, mamafeꞌa mode rudaroteꞌe toheḡa nu rovonadu naeḡa eḡe enoga veize negohe noꞌi.”  
\v 14 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Nego, vazeni ꞌahoganiꞌa toheze ḡahugeꞌeteꞌe gauḡa veize e mene ohohiro.”  
\v 15 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Za ununu haḡaiḡa mene haḡaifine, zamaze obone giganoꞌi! Mazaḡa vazeꞌa tohe ḡehaḡaonoꞌo ḡabone mene hideꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 16 Ebu hari ꞌahoga idane ziro, “Maꞌora vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa mebaḡano ogomu manomano hiriviro.  
\v 17 Ebu ani aneꞌa bare zamariro, 'E ogomuhe godoḡo neḡaꞌe oꞌoꞌa. E nougiꞌuma?'  
\v 18 Ebu ani raenaꞌa, 'E ꞌahige haḡaine manoḡa! Ogomu godoḡo neḡa amahiḡaꞌe fahadu boro iziga ogoraꞌuma ebu ogomuhe zu tohehe niduꞌa eꞌea zouniꞌuma.'  
\v 19 Ebu ani aneꞌa bare raenaꞌa, ꞌE muri faḡa radoga veize ogomu boro hune ruhibe teha. Eꞌanoꞌo eꞌe ogauꞌenaꞌa zu gageꞌenaꞌa matuꞌe onamiꞌuma!'  
\v 20 Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa niro, 'Ḡaꞌe mene huhuzaḡa. Eḡeꞌa izidi ohere ḡae ḡabone mae vaḡinine, ḡa ruhibateꞌe toheḡa'e iniuꞌa meꞌuma?'”   
\p
\v 21 Iesuꞌa ḡonagano ḡoeriro, “ꞌUguḡa vazeḡaꞌe ane tohe daꞌo nuꞌoneꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa, rehano Badiꞌa ubumao aniꞌe mene maꞌora vazeḡa.” \fig Maꞌora vazeḡa kauriḡa|src="WA03852b.tif" size="col" ref="12:15-19" \fig*   
\s1 Ago Zamare Adudanoꞌi  
\r (Mataio 6:25-34, 19:21)  
\p
\v 22 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, zae ḡabone veize nagi ogomu aꞌuma, ga ahirize veize nagi dabua vidaꞌuma rae ago zamare adudanoꞌi.  
\v 23 Mazaḡa ḡaboneꞌe ogomu vitinoga, zu ahiriꞌe dabua vitinoga.  
\v 24 Nugo gaoza zamaroꞌi. Ze ezone mene ḡorauꞌohe, mene hiriveꞌohe, ebu ogomu godoḡo neḡa zu oꞌoꞌa. Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa ḡubuzeꞌohe. Zaꞌe nini vitize hunoga.  
\v 25 Zae boꞌaḡano iniuꞌa zamare adudu radiune, ḡaboneḡaꞌe tahiḡa nu faraꞌumahe?  
\v 26 Zaꞌe ḡau komeꞌa ꞌahoga haḡaoga zuni mene idaḡa. Nougadu ḡau ꞌahogaꞌahoga veize zamare aduduꞌohe?   
\p
\v 27 Butu kakaḡaꞌe nougenouge ḡuhureꞌeteꞌe zamaroꞌi. Ze mene gaueꞌohe ga dabuaze mene turineꞌohe. Rehano eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, butu kakaḡa ꞌahoga zuni maꞌora vazeḡa kini Solomonaꞌa haḡairoteꞌe dabuaḡa manomano vitine hunoga.  
\v 28 Ebu butu veḡaꞌe izidi ḡaboga, u ohoḡoreꞌe masinadu ireo hufi haoniꞌuma. Rehano Badiꞌaꞌa dabua vidohauꞌohe. Zaꞌe ve vitinoga, eꞌanoꞌo Badiꞌaꞌa dabua manoḡa ufeta vidoziniꞌuma. Rehano zaꞌa Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe tahiḡa fase!  
\v 29 Eꞌanoꞌo zaꞌe nagini aꞌuma ga nagini gagiꞌuma rae ago ufeta zamaroꞌi, zu zamaze ago adudanoꞌi.  
\v 30 Mazaḡa Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡaniꞌa eꞌeguḡa niduꞌa vaḡe inareꞌohe, rehano Mozeꞌe zaeꞌa eꞌeguḡa urateꞌeteꞌe edereꞌohe.  
\v 31 Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌazoga vaḡoꞌi, ꞌougine eꞌeguḡa niduꞌa zuni ziniꞌuma.   
\p
\v 32 Mamoe komeꞌakomeꞌa, za ago rihanoꞌi, mazaḡa zae Mamaꞌa za zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe uꞌano matuꞌe rudauꞌohe.  
\v 33 Ebu toheze seronadu hadiḡaꞌe zahara azaḡa zenoꞌi. Zae veize mene zigatiteꞌe hadi fuseḡa haḡaoꞌi, zu mene hauḡiteꞌe toheḡa adureo nuꞌone toꞌi. Eꞌea ḡonoreꞌa mene areꞌohe ebu zuhiꞌa mene sausauneꞌohe.  
\v 34 Mazaḡa za ḡauze naeḡa boro nouma tine, zamaroneze zuni eꞌea tiꞌohe.”   
\s1 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa Ariteꞌe veize Ruhiboꞌi  
\r (Mataio 24:45-51)  
\p
\v 35 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe gau dabuaḡa haḡadu ruhibe radoꞌi, ebu ihureze agane modoꞌi.  
\v 36 Zuhiꞌazeꞌa hahu muiḡanonoꞌo baradu ibihetao toketokerine, ibiheta ḡarihe vavaꞌoga veize guhineꞌeteꞌe azaḡa teigoꞌi.  
\v 37 Zuhiꞌazeꞌa baradu ane tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa ani guhine radiuꞌeteꞌe horozine, ane tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa matuꞌe rudaꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zuhiꞌazeꞌa gau dabuaḡa vidanadu ogauꞌeteꞌe fataḡa uhiḡano ane tuḡure azaḡa ohoziꞌuma, ebu zeḡe babaḡano edauꞌenaꞌa, ogomu ḡahugiꞌuma.  
\v 38 Ebu zuhiꞌazeꞌa ohere ga uzeuze feuradu tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa ani guhine radiuꞌeteꞌe horozine, ani tuḡure azaḡaniꞌa matuꞌe rudaꞌuma.   
\p
\v 39 Rehano za ꞌadi zamaroꞌi. Ne vazeḡaniꞌa ḡonore vazeḡaꞌe noꞌe madaḡano ani ne aritaꞌaꞌe ederifone, ḡonore vazeḡaniꞌa mene diuḡoga veize ani neḡa faine taufifo.  
\v 40 Eꞌe teige, zae zuni ruhibe radoꞌi, mazaḡa Vaze Ubugaꞌe za mene edereꞌeteꞌe madaḡano ariꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 41 Ebu Peteroꞌa niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡaeꞌa hari idaidaḡa ꞌadiꞌe emeḡe daꞌo veize ga vaze niduꞌa veize zuni?”  
\v 42 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa naenaeniro, “Iniuꞌe vaze huhuzaḡa zu zamaḡa niduꞌa hina gaueꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa? Tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahogaꞌe vaze ꞌuguḡa reine, zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa aniꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡano mae ohonadu ꞌahige niꞌuma, 'Ḡa tuḡure azaḡa niduꞌa taufoꞌi. Ogomuze zuni mada idunane zenoꞌi.'  
\v 43 Ebu tuḡure vazeḡa eꞌeꞌa ꞌouge gauine ebu zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa bare feuradu horonine, tuḡure vazeḡa aꞌe matuꞌe rudaꞌuma.  
\v 44 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, aniꞌe zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa ane tohe niduꞌa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡano ohoniꞌuma.  
\v 45 Rehano tuḡure vazeḡa aꞌe aneꞌa bare raenaꞌa, 'Eḡe zuhiꞌaꞌe vesuꞌu faḡanobuꞌu ariꞌuma,' rae zamaradu ohoze tuḡure azaḡa zu roḡae tuḡure azaḡa niduꞌa bouzine zu ufeta ogau gage baboraune, nougiꞌuma?  
\v 46 Aniꞌa mene zamareꞌeteꞌe zu mene edereꞌeteꞌe madaḡano zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa bare aradu ane ahiri variꞌe tahitahiꞌuma, ebu zama niduꞌa hina mene gaueꞌeteꞌe azaḡa habaꞌano ohonadu aduga boro haꞌuma.   
\p
\v 47 Tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe ane zuhiꞌaꞌa nagini urateꞌetaꞌaꞌe edereꞌe rehano, mene ruhibine zu mene haḡaine, aniꞌe boune sausauniꞌuma.  
\v 48 U tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe ane zuhiꞌa ura mene ederadu veꞌoḡa haḡaine, aniꞌe tahiḡa boune tauḡiꞌuma. Iniuꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ḡehaḡa hidine, Badiꞌaꞌe ani mazaonoꞌo ḡehaḡa mouga urateꞌohe. Ebu iniuꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa ane gau boro haune, Badiꞌaꞌe ani mazaonoꞌo ḡehaḡa umideꞌohe.”   
\s1 Mene Uniho Manoḡa, Rehano Rovotiꞌuma  
\r (Mataio 10:34-36)  
\p
\v 49 Iesuꞌa bare ziro, “Eḡeꞌa raha ꞌadi hofoga radu ire roga mae ariro. Ire rogaꞌa amahi raha ꞌadi iri radiune, e matuꞌe rudaꞌuma.  
\v 50 Rehano e aduga hiditeꞌe babatisoḡa meꞌuma, zu zamaheꞌe adudaꞌuma onamo ḡonaga meꞌuma.  
\v 51 Zaꞌe eḡeꞌa raha ꞌada uniho manoḡa mae ovairo rae zamareꞌehe? Mene. Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, e vaze rovoze ḡuzuhoga veize ovairo.  
\v 52 Izidionoꞌo onamo zama moneo eḡe uꞌano ne azaḡaꞌe rovotiꞌuma. Ne eꞌe azaḡaꞌe fuꞌo reine, zeḡe boꞌaḡano rovotadu uḡiduꞌa aheu teite agirotitiꞌuma, ga aheuꞌa uḡidu teite agirotitiꞌuma.  
\v 53 Moganiꞌa ubuga teite agirotitiꞌuma, ga ubuganiꞌa moga teite agirotitiꞌuma. Viꞌaniꞌa aboḡa teite agirotitiꞌuma, ga aboḡaniꞌa viꞌa teite agirotitiꞌuma. Viꞌaniꞌa ubuga inuga teite agirotitiꞌuma, ga ubuga inuganiꞌa iꞌa viꞌa teite agirotitiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Madaḡa Ederoꞌi  
\r (Mataio 16:2-3, 5:25-26)  
\p
\v 54 Iesuꞌa vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ziro, “Zaꞌe ḡozeꞌa ḡutanoga horoneꞌetene,\f + \fr 12:54 \fqa madaꞌa zubureꞌeteꞌe moneo ḡozeꞌa iteꞌetene \f* zogone ꞌahige raꞌohe, 'Iruguꞌa ruꞌaꞌuma.' A hube, iruguꞌa ruꞌauꞌohe.  
\v 55 Ebu ohere ḡozeꞌa bororanadu nahuduꞌetene,\f + \fr 12:55 \fqa ḡuzuonoꞌo zavara horoneꞌetene \f* zaꞌa raenaꞌa, 'Madaꞌa hiaꞌuma.' A hube, madaꞌa hiauꞌohe.  
\v 56 Zama guhi azaḡa! Zaꞌe adure zu raha iraḡa horoneꞌetene, naginiꞌa fureratitaꞌaꞌe edereꞌohe. Rehano izidi madaḡano naginiꞌa fureru radiuꞌeteꞌe moneo huga eꞌe mene edereꞌohe.   
\p
\v 57 Za nougadu zaeꞌa bare naginiꞌe duduḡa rae mene edereꞌohe?  
\v 58 Ḡaꞌe vaze ꞌahoga hadiḡa meiroteꞌe uꞌano aniꞌa kotao ohoꞌihi radu ani teite onamoꞌidene, ibio uniho manofoga veize inare hunoꞌi. Mene ꞌougine, aniꞌa oboꞌe teadu kota vazeḡa mazao tutuꞌe onamiꞌuma, ebu hena kota vazeḡaniꞌa ḡuꞌa neḡa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌevoreo ohoꞌadu ḡuꞌa neḡano ohoꞌiꞌuma.  
\v 59 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, za ḡuꞌa neḡanonoꞌo mene buaꞌuma, onamo zaeꞌa ani hadi niduꞌaꞌe baroniꞌuma.”   
\c 13  
\s1 Mene Ḡihurine Rudaꞌuma  
\p
\v 1 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesu teite radiroteꞌe azaḡa nuꞌa Iesu niro, “Galilea azaḡa nuꞌa Badiꞌa dibuꞌohauꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano Pilatoꞌa zemeha.”  
\v 2 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Zae zamarone, zeḡe haḡai sauꞌaꞌe Galilea azaḡa ꞌomo haḡaize sauꞌa roꞌanoga ꞌahine, ꞌouge rudaneha rae raꞌehe?  
\v 3 Mene. Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, zae zuni zae haḡai sauꞌanonoꞌo mene ḡihurine, zeḡe teige zae niduꞌa rudaꞌuma.  
\v 4 Ebu za edeḡa, Siloama habaꞌano ne hitaganiꞌa fahanadu vaze niduꞌa 18 rudaro. Zae zamarone, zeḡe haḡai sauꞌaꞌe Ierusalema azaḡa niduꞌa haḡaize sauꞌa roꞌanoga rae raꞌehe?  
\v 5 Mene. Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, zae zuni zae haḡai sauꞌanonoꞌo mene ḡihurine, zeḡe teige zae niduꞌa rudaꞌuma.”   
\s1 Figi Ireḡa Huga Oꞌoꞌa Hari Idaidaḡa  
\p
\v 6 Ebu Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga idaniro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa vaini mebaḡano figi ireḡa ḡoraro. Eꞌe enogano aniꞌa huga nu reꞌoga veize onamiro, rehano huga ꞌahoga mene horoniro.  
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo aniꞌa meba ḡianeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa niro, 'E muri uḡidu zamaḡano huga reꞌoga veize arido, rehano hugani ꞌahoga mene horonido. Eꞌanoꞌo udi higanoꞌi! Nougaꞌahi haba daꞌo iriꞌavone tauḡiꞌohe?'  
\v 8 Ebu meba ḡianeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa naenaeniro, 'Vaze boro, ge muri tiba daꞌo bare modoꞌi. Eḡeꞌa ire varahe hoꞌadu mazaḡano busi mumuḡa teadu ḡianiꞌuma.  
\v 9 ꞌOugine, muri tiba enogano manoḡa hudaꞌuma. Mene hudanoꞌidene, udi higonoꞌi.'”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Bana Madaḡano Ḡaruga Sauꞌa Roḡaeḡa Fainiro  
\p
\v 10 Bana Madaḡa ꞌahogano Iesuꞌe nu'onu'o neḡano ihoze radiunu.  
\v 11 Ebu eꞌea roḡae ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu. Vine sauꞌaniꞌa ani ragano radu ḡaruga mae beꞌoniro ꞌahine, aniꞌe muri 18 mene edau faraunu.  
\v 12 Iesuꞌa ani horonirotene, ane vaḡe aroga veize hunadu niro, “Roḡae, ḡae ugi ꞌai manoreha.”  
\v 13 Ebu Iesuꞌa ꞌevoꞌa ane rana tirotene, ani zogone edau fararo zu Badiꞌa niguniro.   
\p
\v 14 Rehano nu'onu'o neḡa vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaꞌe maḡuniro, mazaḡa Iesuꞌa Bana Madaḡano ugi roḡaeḡa fainiro. Aniꞌa vaze ziro, “Eme mada fuꞌo tiba fare zamaḡano gauiꞌuma. Eꞌanoꞌo ugi azaḡaꞌe eꞌe madaḡano aradu manoriꞌuma, u Bana Madaḡanoꞌe mene ꞌougiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 15 Ebu Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa naenaeniro, “Za, zama guhi azaḡa! Zae tibatiba zuni Bana Madaḡano boromakauze ga donikize maḡuzeonoꞌo fuiꞌe bunadu tutuze onamadu vu gagoziniꞌohe.  
\v 16 Tena Aberahamo mariga raꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡa ꞌadiꞌe nougiꞌuma? Aniꞌe Sataniꞌa muri 18 ogoru tiro. Bana Madaḡano ani fuiꞌe bunogaꞌe mene idaḡahe?”   
\p
\v 17 Iesuꞌa ꞌouge reirotene, ani agiroharoteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe mazagaroziro, u vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaꞌe aneꞌa haḡairoteꞌe haḡaiḡa manomano niduꞌa uꞌano, matuꞌiro.   
\s1 Badiꞌaꞌa Zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo Hari Idaidaniro  
\r (Mataio 13:31-33; Mareko 4:30-32)  
\p
\v 18 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe nagini heuḡa? Naginio idaniꞌuma?  
\v 19 Aꞌe Kuava\f + \fr 13:19 \fqa fufu. \ft Isaraela habaꞌano fufuꞌe ire. \f* maḡa komeꞌa tiba vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa madu mebaḡano ḡoraroteꞌe heuḡa. Ebu maḡa komeꞌa eꞌeꞌa ḡuhuradu ire boro reirotene, hitagano niniꞌa rafiu aradu ezagano neze ogoraro.”   
\p
\v 20 Iesuꞌa bare ziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌetaꞌaꞌe naginio idaniꞌuma?  
\v 21 Aꞌe isiti heuḡa. Roḡaeꞌa isiti tahiḡa madu ꞌuvahuḡa ḡehaḡa teite mirune tibunirotene ꞌuvahu niduꞌa ubararo.”   
\s1 Ibiheta Kokosiḡa  
\r (Mataio 7:13-14, 21-23)  
\p
\v 22 Iesuꞌa Ierusalema onameꞌeteꞌea, habaꞌahabaꞌano zu neḡaneḡano ihoze onamiro.  
\v 23 Ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu ḡadiniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, Badiꞌaꞌa vaze tahiḡa daꞌo ḡaboziꞌumahe?” Iesuꞌa naenaeziro,  
\v 24 “Ḡabone hidihi roꞌidene, ibiheta kokosiḡa diuḡoga veize inare hunoꞌi. Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, vaze ḡehaḡaꞌe eꞌe diuḡihi reꞌuma rehano, mene idaraꞌuma.  
\v 25 Ne vazeḡaniꞌa iḡunadu ibiheta haraune, zaꞌe enona edanadu toketokereꞌenaꞌa ꞌahige uminiꞌuma, 'Vaze boro, ibiheta vavaꞌoꞌi!' Rehano ani naenaeziꞌuma, 'E za noumanoꞌo arataꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa.'  
\v 26 Ebu za ꞌahige reꞌuma, 'Eme ḡae teite ogaro zu gagiro ebu ḡaꞌe ibio ihofiro.'  
\v 27 Rehano ani naenaeziꞌuma, 'Za noumanoꞌo arataꞌaꞌe e aḡuꞌa. Za, haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa, eḡe mazaonoꞌo vaḡinoꞌi!'   
\p
\v 28 Ebu za Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano Aberahamo, Isako, Iakobo zu peroveta azaḡa niduꞌa radiuꞌeteꞌe zu zaꞌe enona mae feuzeꞌeteꞌe horoziꞌuma. ꞌOugadu zaꞌe niaꞌuma zu ḡononeze atitiꞌuma.  
\v 29 Iuda mene azaḡaniꞌa madaꞌa iteꞌeteꞌe moneonoꞌo zu madaꞌa zubureꞌeteꞌe moneonoꞌo zu haba niduꞌaonoꞌo aradu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ogau tiburaꞌuma.  
\v 30 Hube hune, vaze ibiꞌaꞌe ḡonaga reꞌuma ebu vaze ḡonagaꞌe ibiꞌa reꞌuma.”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ierusalema uꞌano Niaro  
\r (Mataio 23:37-39)  
\p
\v 31 Eꞌe madaḡano Farisea azaḡa nuꞌa Iesu vaḡe aradu niro, “ꞌAdanoꞌo vaḡinadu haba ꞌahoga onamoꞌi, mazaḡa kini Herodaꞌa ḡamihi raꞌohe.”  
\v 32 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Aniꞌe butu ḡuniḡa soꞌosoꞌoḡa. Ani vaḡe onamadu ꞌahige noꞌi, 'E mada mene faḡano\f + \fr 13:32 \fqa izidi zu ohoḡore \f* vine sauꞌa hegoze buziꞌuma zu ugi azaḡa faiziꞌuma, ebu hena\f + \fr 13:32 \fqa mada uḡiduḡano \f* eḡe gau niduꞌa haḡae hauḡiꞌuma.'  
\v 33 Naginiꞌa eḡe mazao fureraune zuni, e izidi, ohoḡore, iḡano zu mada nu eḡe ibio onamiꞌuma, onamo Ierusalemao feuriꞌuma. Mazaḡa peroveta azaḡaꞌe Ierusalema habaꞌa enogano mene rudaꞌuma.   
\p
\v 34 O, Ierusalema, Ierusalema, zaꞌa peroveta azaḡa zimiro, zu Badiꞌaꞌa tuḡuziroteꞌe azaḡa hadi hina zimi ruziro. Kokorokuꞌa isaḡa zamaḡano ubuga gugubeꞌeteꞌe teige, eḡeꞌa ḡae ḡehaḡa zae taufihi reiro, rehano zaꞌe mene uratinu!  
\v 35 Ḡianoꞌi, neze fahadu mae modiꞌuma. Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, zaꞌe e mene bare horohiꞌuma, onamo zaeꞌa raenaꞌa, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro niḡano areꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune,' rae reiteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa meꞌuma.”   
\c 14  
\s1 Iesuꞌa Bana Madaḡano Ugi Vazeḡa Fainiro  
\p
\v 1 Bana Madaḡa ꞌahogano Iesuꞌa Farisea azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga neo ogomu anoga veize onamiro. Ebu vaze nuꞌa ani uhiḡano ḡiaḡiane radiro.  
\v 2 Eꞌea Iesu zamao vaze ꞌahogaꞌe uginadu ꞌevoꞌa zu odaḡaꞌe miniroteꞌeꞌa radiro.  
\v 3 Ebu Iesuꞌa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu Farisea azaḡa ḡadiziro, “Zaꞌa zamareꞌetene Bana Madaḡano ugi vazeḡa fainogaꞌe idaḡa ga mene?”  
\v 4 Zeꞌa mene naenaeniro. Iesuꞌa ꞌevoꞌa hina ugi vazeḡa oboneꞌenaꞌa, fainadu tuḡune vaḡiniro.  
\v 5 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zae boꞌaḡano Bana Madaḡano iniu ubuga ga boromakauꞌa idu vuḡa zamaḡano ovoine, ḡarihe mae ḡihiniꞌuma ga mene?”  
\v 6 ꞌOuge reirotene, ze mene naenaeniro.   
\s1 Nize mae Ovoroꞌi  
\p
\v 7 Muio huziroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa hitana ehoroḡano ehoroga Iesuꞌa horozirotene, hari ꞌahoga idaniro,  
\v 8 “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa hahu muiḡa auḡoga veize ḡa huḡadoꞌidene, hitana ehoroḡano ago ehoroꞌi. Mazaḡa ufeta hitaga vazeḡa zuni hunine,  
\v 9 ḡanine huzateꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ḡa vaḡe aradu ꞌahige ḡeꞌuma, 'Ḡae ehoro habaꞌa vaze ꞌadi hanoꞌi.' ꞌOugine, ḡa mazagaroꞌadu ḡonaga ehoroḡa onamiꞌuma.  
\v 10 Eꞌanoꞌo mui vazeḡaniꞌa huḡadoꞌidene, ḡonaga ehoroḡano ehoroꞌi. ꞌOugine, huḡadiroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa horoꞌadu ḡa vaḡe ariꞌuma, ebu ꞌahige ḡeꞌuma, 'Eḡe vaze, iḡunadu hitana ehoroḡano ehoroꞌi.' ꞌOugine, ḡae teite huziroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ḡa niguꞌiꞌuma.  
\v 11 Iniu vaze aneꞌa bare niḡa mae itine, Badiꞌaꞌa niḡa mae ovoiꞌuma, u iniu vaze aneꞌa bare niḡa mae ovoine, Badiꞌaꞌa niḡa mae itiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 12 Ebu Iesuꞌa ani huniroteꞌe vazeḡa niro, “Madai ogomu ga ḡorava ogomu veize vaze huzoꞌidene, vazeḡo, negoḡo, nabugo ga ḡae uhiḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe maꞌora azaḡa ago huzoꞌi. ꞌOugine zeꞌa ḡa bare naenae huḡadadu ḡaeꞌa haḡaiḡo naeḡa meꞌuma.  
\v 13 Rehano ḡa mui madaḡano zahara azaḡa, oda sauꞌa azaḡa, edanoga mene idaḡa azaḡa ebu ubumaze kuruḡa azaḡa huzoꞌi.  
\v 14 ꞌOugine ḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa manohuga ḡaniꞌuma. Zeꞌe baronoḡanogaꞌe mene idaḡa ꞌahine, duduḡa azaḡaniꞌa bare ḡaboditeꞌe madaḡano, ḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa haḡaiḡo naeḡa ḡaniꞌuma.”   
\s1 Mui Boro Hari Idaidaḡa  
\r (Mataio 22:1-10)  
\p
\v 15 Iesu teite ogau radiroteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu ḡoere egadu Iesu niro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ogau tiburuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe matuꞌeꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 16 Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Mada ꞌahogano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa mui boro ruhibadu vaze ḡehaḡa huziro.  
\v 17 Mui madaḡa reirotene, ani tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahoga huziroteꞌe azaḡa vaḡe tuḡunadu ꞌahige rae ziro, 'Mui boro veize ḡau niduꞌa izidi ruhibeha. Eꞌanoꞌo zae niduꞌa aroꞌi.'  
\v 18 Rehano zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe ḡoere nunufiro. Ibite huniroteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa raenaꞌa, 'E haba iziga hoiteha, eꞌanoꞌo e haba eꞌe ḡiani onamihi. E mene amateꞌe moneo ago maḡunoꞌi.'  
\v 19 Ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa raenaꞌa, 'E boromakau gaubanana hoiteha. Eꞌanoꞌo e ze manoga ga meneꞌe tuhune nurihi. E mene amateꞌe moneo ago maḡunoꞌi.'  
\v 20 Ebu vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa raenaꞌa, 'E iziduꞌu hahureha, eꞌanoꞌo e mene amiꞌuma.'   
\p
\v 21 Tuḡure vazeḡaniꞌa bare onamadu zeꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa zuhiꞌaḡa ihoniro. Ihonirotene mui vazeḡaꞌe maḡune rudaro ebu tuḡure vazeḡa niro, 'Ne ibi boroboro zu ibi komeꞌakomeꞌa ḡarihe onamadu zahara azaḡa, oda sauꞌa azaḡa, ubumaze kuruḡa azaḡa zu edanoga mene idaḡa azaḡa zamaze aroꞌi.'  
\v 22 Ebu tuḡure vazeḡaniꞌa onamadu ꞌouge haḡairo, ebu baradu zuhiꞌaḡa niro, 'Zuhiꞌa, ḡaꞌa ehateꞌe gauḡa haḡaeha, rehano ne ꞌize mene iriꞌaveha.'  
\v 23 Zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa tuḡure vazeḡa niro, 'Ibi boro zu ibi komeꞌa onamoꞌi ebu vaze niduꞌa teꞌoteꞌozadu zamaze aroꞌi. Vazeꞌe eḡe ne iri'avonoꞌi.  
\v 24 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, ibite mui veize huziroteꞌe azaḡa niduꞌaꞌe eḡe mui tahiḡa zuni mene auḡiꞌuma.'” \fig Mui boro hari idaidaḡa|src="DN00477b.tif" size="col" ref="14:16-24" \fig*   
\s1 Iesu Hegoteꞌeteꞌe Ibiḡa  
\r (Mataio 10:37-38)  
\p
\v 25 Mada ꞌahogano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesu teite ragavinu. Ebu Iesuꞌa vaetadu ziro,  
\v 26 “Iniuꞌa eḡe ḡaruna hegotoga uratoꞌidene, eḡe zamare borofoꞌi. Iniuꞌa moga zu viꞌa, inuga zu ubuga, negoḡa zu ezeḡa, ebu ḡaboneḡaꞌe eḡe ufeta vitihe zamare borofine, aniꞌe eḡe mene tahiꞌa reꞌuma.  
\v 27 Iniuꞌa ane satauro odohadu eḡe ḡaruna mene hegotine, aniꞌe eḡe mene tahiꞌa reꞌuma.   
\p
\v 28 Zae boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa hitaga neḡa ogoranoga uratine, ibite geno ehoradu hadi nugu hina ogoru hauḡiꞌuma rae zamariꞌuma, zu hadiḡaꞌe ne eꞌe ogoranoga veize idaḡa ga meneꞌe ḡianiꞌuma.  
\v 29 Aniꞌa iḡite ohonadu mene ogoru hauḡine, vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa eꞌe horonadu ḡirihohaꞌuma.  
\v 30 Zeꞌe ꞌahige reꞌuma, 'Vaze ꞌadiꞌe ne ohoniro, rehano hauḡogaꞌe mene idararo.'   
\p
\v 31 Ebu kini ꞌahoganiꞌa kini ꞌahoga teite uti onamine, ani ibite geno ehoradu ꞌahige rae zamariꞌuma, 'Eḡe uti azaḡaꞌe 10,000 ebu ani uti azaḡa 20,000. E kini eꞌe teite utitine, ani vitiniꞌuma ga mene?'  
\v 32 Ani vitinoga mene idaḡa reine, kini eꞌe ꞌize faḡano radiuꞌeteꞌea, ani teite uniho manoḡa mouga veize hari odohe dureꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa tuḡuniꞌuma.  
\v 33 Eꞌe teige, zae boꞌaḡano iniuꞌa ane ḡau niduꞌa moditeꞌe moneo ibite mene zamarine, aniꞌe eḡe mene tahiꞌa reꞌuma.”   
\s1 Dama Mene Iniga  
\r (Mataio 5:13; Mareko 9:50)  
\p
\v 34 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe dama heuḡa. Damaꞌe manoḡa, rehano iniganiꞌa dauḡine, nougenouge bare inidaꞌuma?  
\v 35 Dama mene inigaꞌe raha ga ogomu ḡuhuneꞌeteꞌe busiḡa veize zuni mene manoḡa ꞌahine, mae modeꞌohe. Teḡaḡeta vazeḡaꞌe faifaine egadu huga ederoꞌi.”   
\c 15  
\s1 Mamoe Dauḡoga Hari Idaidaḡa  
\r (Mataio 18:12-14)  
\p
\v 1 Mada ꞌahogano takesi azaḡa ebu haḡai sauꞌa azaḡaniꞌa Iesu ḡoere abitihi radu ani uhiḡano nuꞌoraro.  
\v 2 Rehano Farisea azaḡa ebu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe mene matuꞌiro ebu ufeta ḡoeriro, “Iesuꞌe haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa mae zouzadu zeḡe teite ogau tiburuꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 3 Eꞌanoꞌo Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga idane ziro,  
\v 4 “Zae boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoga mazao mamoeḡaꞌe 100. Rehano tibaniꞌa dauḡine, ani nougiꞌuma? Aniꞌe mamoe 99 haba bohaꞌano modadu mamoe dauḡoga vaḡe ragaviꞌuma onamo horoniꞌuma.  
\v 5 Mamoe dauḡoga horone meine, ani matuꞌe rudanadu mae ane herao tiꞌuma,  
\v 6 ebu ani bare ne onamiꞌuma. Ebu ane vaze, negoḡa zu nabuga huze nuꞌozadu ziꞌuma, 'Eꞌe eḡe mamoe dauḡoga horoneha. Eꞌanoꞌo eḡe teite matu'ihi.'  
\v 7 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, haḡai sauꞌa vazeḡa tibaniꞌa ḡihurine, adureo ani uꞌano matuꞌiꞌuma. Duduḡa azaḡaꞌe haḡaize sauꞌa oꞌoꞌa radu mene ḡihureꞌohe. Adureo duduḡa azaḡa 99 uꞌano matuꞌiꞌuma, rehano haḡai sauꞌa vazeḡa tibaniꞌa ḡihurine, ufeta matuꞌiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Hadi Dauḡoga Hari Idaidaḡa  
\p
\v 8 Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga idaniro, “Roḡae ꞌahoga mazao hadi niduꞌa\f + \fr 15:8 \fqa derakema niduꞌa gaubanana. \ft Derakema tibaꞌe mada tiba gauḡa naeḡa. \f* gaubanana, rehano tibaniꞌa dauḡine, ani nougiꞌuma? Aniꞌe ihureḡa tinadu ne fodeꞌenaꞌa, haba niduꞌa faine ḡiane vaḡiꞌuma onamo horoniꞌuma.  
\v 9 Ebu horone meine, ane vaze, negoḡa zu nabuga huzadu ziꞌuma, 'Eꞌe eḡe hadi dauḡoga horoneha, eꞌanoꞌo eḡe teite matuꞌihi.'  
\v 10 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, haḡai sauꞌa vazeḡa tibaniꞌa ḡihurine, Badiꞌa tuḡure viga niduꞌaꞌe matuꞌiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Ubuga Dauḡoga Hari Idaidaḡa  
\p
\v 11 Ebu Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga bare idaniro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ubuga aheu teite radiunu.  
\v 12 Mada ꞌahogano ubuga veḡaniꞌa moga niro, 'Mama, ḡae tohe zamaḡano initeꞌe toheḡa niduꞌa enoꞌi.' Eꞌanoꞌo moganiꞌa ane tohe ubuga aheu veize rovonadu ziniro.   
\p
\v 13 Mada nu enogano, ubuga veḡaniꞌa ḡauḡa niduꞌa nuꞌonadu haba faḡa ꞌahoga onamiro. Ebu eꞌea ani ane matuꞌu uꞌano radiu tauḡitauḡadu hadiḡa niduꞌa modiro.  
\v 14 Ani hadiḡa niduꞌa mode hauḡirotene, eꞌe habaꞌano zahara boroꞌa buaro ebu ani vinine runiro.  
\v 15 Eꞌanoꞌo ani gauoga veize eꞌe habaꞌa vazeḡa ꞌahoga vaḡe onamiro, ebu vaze eꞌeꞌa ani haba bohaꞌano aba taufeꞌeteꞌe gauḡa haro.  
\v 16 Ani eꞌea vinine runadu ani zama boroꞌe aba ogomu atihi reiro, rehano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa ogomu ꞌahoga mene haro.   
\p
\v 17 Ḡonagano zamaḡaniꞌa bohatanadu ani aneꞌa bare ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Eḡe mama veize gaueꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ogomuze ḡehaḡa bagaḡa, u eꞌe ahama vinihe ruheꞌohe.  
\v 18 E mama vaḡe bare onamadu ꞌahige niꞌuma, “Mama, e Badiꞌa zu ḡa mazao haḡai sauꞌa haḡairo.  
\v 19 Eꞌanoꞌo e ḡae ubugo rae ago huhoꞌi, rehano ḡae veize gaueꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze tiba teige huhoꞌi.”'  
\v 20 Ebu aniꞌa iḡunadu moga vaḡe bare onamiro. \fig Ubuga dauḡoga|src="WA03875b.tif" size="col" ref="15:15-17" \fig*  
\p Ani ꞌize faḡano ariroteꞌea, moganiꞌa horoniro. Mogaꞌe ubuga vetuḡaneadu ani ubuga uꞌa dure onamiro ebu ahainadu furaꞌiniro.  
\v 21 Ubuganiꞌa moga niro, 'Mama, eꞌe Badiꞌa zu ḡa mazao haḡai sauꞌa haḡairo, eꞌanoꞌo e ḡae ubugo rae ago huhoꞌi.'  
\v 22 Rehano moganiꞌa tuḡure azaḡa ziro, 'Dabua manoḡa ḡarihe odohe aradu ubudehe vidohanoꞌi. ꞌEvore adiriḡa redohanoꞌi zu tamaka redohanoꞌi.  
\v 23 Ebu boromakau modohuḡa iga odohe aradu manoꞌi. Eme matuꞌiꞌhi zu ogau tiburatihi.  
\v 24 Mazaḡa eḡe ubude ꞌahiꞌe rudanadu bare ḡabodeha, ebu ani dauḡadu bare horone maha.' Eꞌanoꞌo ze mui boro haḡadu zeḡe niduꞌa matuꞌe tiburaro.   
\p
\v 25 ꞌOugiroteꞌe zamaḡano ubuga ibiꞌaniꞌa mebao gaue radiunu. Ani ne uꞌa bare onamadu ne uhiḡano feurirotene, badahe zavoneꞌeteꞌe haraoḡa igiro.  
\v 26 Ebu ani tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahoga hunadu naginiꞌa fureruꞌeteꞌe ḡadiniro.  
\v 27 Tuḡure vazeḡaniꞌa naenaeniro, 'Negoḡoꞌa manoḡa bare feureha, eꞌanoꞌo mogoꞌa boromakau modohuḡa iga manadu mui boro haḡaeha.'  
\v 28 ꞌOuge reirotene ubuga ibiꞌaniꞌa maḡune rudaro ebu ne zamaḡa diuḡoga mene uratiro. Ebu moganiꞌa buanadu ne diuḡifine ani uminiro.  
\v 29 Rehano aniꞌa moga naenaeniro, 'Mama, zamaroꞌi! E muri ḡehaḡa tuḡure vazeḡa teige ḡae veize gaue areꞌohe zu ḡae ḡoere mene hezahohaunu. Rehano e eḡe nabudi teite matuꞌifine ḡaeꞌa gouti ubuga tiba zuni mene manoniro.  
\v 30 U ubugo ꞌahaꞌa daro fuꞌa roḡaeḡaroḡaeḡa teite ḡae tohe mode hauḡadu ne uꞌa bare aratene, ḡa boromakau modohuḡa iga mano haneha!'  
\v 31 Ebu moganiꞌa niro, 'Eḡe ubude, ḡa mada niduꞌa eḡe teite radiuꞌohe, eꞌanoꞌo eḡe ḡau niduꞌaꞌe ḡae veize raꞌohe.  
\v 32 U negoḡoꞌe rudanadu bare ḡabodeha zu dauḡadu bare horoneha. Eꞌanoꞌo emeḡeꞌa mui haḡadu matuꞌiꞌuma.'”   
\c 16  
\s1 Maꞌora Vazeḡa Ḡau Taufeꞌeteꞌe Vazeḡa Hari Idaidaḡa  
\p
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Maꞌora vazeḡa ꞌahoga ane ḡau niduꞌa taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu. Mada ꞌahogano maꞌora vazeḡaꞌe ane ḡau taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa ani hadi au hauḡinuteꞌe igiro.  
\v 2 ꞌOugirotene, maꞌora vazeḡaniꞌa ani hunadu niro, 'Ḡae moneo igiꞌeteꞌe hariḡaꞌe hubehe? Ḡaeꞌa eḡe hadi hina nougenouge gauinuteꞌe faine meꞌodonoꞌi, mazaḡa ḡaꞌe eḡe ḡau mene bare taufiꞌuma.'   
\p
\v 3 ꞌOuge nirotene, ani aneꞌa bare reiro, 'Eḡe zuhiꞌaꞌa gauhe eḡe mazaonoꞌo mae vaḡiniꞌuma. E izidi nougiꞌuma? E ahiri gauḡa moneo inarahe ꞌoꞌoꞌa zu hadi umidoga mazagaroheꞌohe.  
\v 4 O, e nougitaꞌaꞌe edereha. ꞌAhige haḡaine, gau ꞌahi moditeꞌe madaḡano vazeꞌa zeḡe neo huhe zouhiꞌuma.'   
\p
\v 5 ꞌOugadu aniꞌa ane zuhiꞌa ḡau meiroteꞌe azaḡa tibatiba huziro. Ebu zeḡe boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoga ḡadiniro, 'Ḡaꞌa eḡe zuhiꞌa ḡauꞌe nugu meiro?'  
\v 6 Vaze eꞌeꞌa naenaeniro, 'E olivi dehoroḡa 800 gareni meiro.' Zuhiꞌaḡa ḡau taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa niro, 'Ḡae soꞌa ꞌahi moꞌi, ebu ḡarihe ehoradu 400 gareni rae bare mirihoꞌi.'  
\v 7 Ebu hena vaze ꞌahoga ḡadiniro, 'Ḡa eḡe zuhiꞌa ḡauꞌe nugu meiro?' Vaze eꞌeꞌa naenaeniro, 'Vuidi fuseḡa niduꞌa 100 meiro.' Aniꞌa niro, 'Ḡae soꞌa ꞌahi madu fuse niduꞌa 80 rae bare mirihoꞌi.'   
\p
\v 8 Zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa ane ḡau taufeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaniꞌa nagini haḡairoteꞌe igirotene, ani ḡuriro vazeḡa rehano, niguniro, mazaḡa haḡaiḡaꞌe huhuzaḡa. Eꞌe teige, raha ꞌadao Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡaꞌe zeḡe veize gauoga ufeta huhuzaḡa. Zeꞌe agaḡa azaḡa vitizoga.  
\v 9 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, zaꞌe raha ꞌada ḡau madu vaze danazoꞌi, ꞌougine zeꞌe zae nabudi reꞌuma. Ebu ḡauze niduꞌa hauḡadu zae zuni rudaune, zeꞌe radiu tuḡutuḡu habaꞌano za horozadu mae zouziꞌuma.   
\p
\v 10 Iniuꞌa gau komeꞌa veize zamaḡa niduꞌa hina faine haḡaine, gau boro zuni ꞌouge haḡaiꞌuma. U iniuꞌa gau komeꞌano ḡuririne, gau boro veize zuni ḡuririꞌuma.  
\v 11 Za raha ḡauḡa madu zamaze niduꞌa hina mene faine taufine, iniuꞌa ḡau manomano zenadu taufoꞌi rae reꞌuma?  
\v 12 Ebu za vaze ḡau madu zamaze niduꞌa hina mene faine taufine, iniuꞌa zaeꞌa meiteꞌe gau naeḡa ziniꞌuma?   
\p
\v 13 Tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe zuhiꞌa aheu veize gauoga mene idaḡa. Ani ꞌahogaꞌe heꞌeheꞌeniꞌuma, u ꞌahogaꞌe zamare borofiꞌuma. Ebu ꞌahoga veize faine gauiꞌuma, u ꞌahogaꞌe turuniꞌuma. Eꞌe teige, zaꞌe Badiꞌa ebu hadi, aheu veize gauoga mene idaḡa.”   
\p
\v 14 Farisea azaḡaꞌe hadi zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe uꞌano Iesu ḡoere igirotene, Iesu eḡofoharo.  
\v 15 ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe vaze ubumao zaeꞌa bare duduḡa raꞌohe, rehano Badiꞌaꞌe zae zama sauꞌa edeḡa. Vazeꞌa ḡau boro raꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa heꞌeheꞌeneꞌohe.   
\p
\v 16 Ioane Babatisoꞌa ꞌizema arogano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa zu peroveta azaḡa ḡoere hina vaze ibitoziro. Eꞌe enogano Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe moneo hari manoḡaꞌe harameꞌohe, ebu vaze ḡehaḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano diuḡoga veize inareꞌohe.  
\v 17 Adure zu rahaꞌe dauḡiꞌuma, rehano Mose goro ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa boꞌaḡano komeꞌa ꞌahoga zuni mene hune dauḡiꞌuma.   
\p
\v 18 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ꞌahoganiꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Iniuꞌa inuga modadu roḡae ꞌahoga teite hahurine, aniꞌe ubuma ḡezauꞌohe. Ebu iniu iꞌaniꞌa modiroteꞌe roḡaeḡa teite hahurine, ani zuni ubuma ḡezauꞌohe.'”   
\s1 Maꞌora Vazeḡa ebu Lazaro  
\p
\v 19 Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga idaniro, “Maꞌora vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu. Ani dabua manoḡa naeḡa boro vidaunu zu mada niduꞌa ne manoḡa huneo ogomu manoḡa au radiunu.  
\v 20 U ani ne ḡabiriḡa ibihetaḡano zahara vazeḡa, niḡa Lazaroꞌa baze radiunu. Ani ahiriꞌe idiri ḡunuḡa.  
\v 21 Ani maꞌora vazeḡaniꞌa fatao oganadu mumuḡaniꞌa rururaudoteꞌe ufe atihi reinu. Ḡuniꞌa zuni aradu ane idiri ubidinu. \fig Maꞌora vazeḡa ebu Lazaro|src="43_Luke16:19_LazarusBegs" size="col" ref="16:19" \fig*   
\p
\v 22 Ebu hena Lazaroꞌa rudarotene, tuḡure viganiꞌa ovadu Aberahamo vaḡe zamahu itiro. Ebu maꞌora vazeḡa zuni rudanadu guriro.  
\v 23 Maꞌora vazeḡaꞌe rune azaḡa haba\f + \fr 16:23 \fqa Hadesi \f* onamadu gigiꞌa boro uꞌano huau ḡaniḡanaro. Ebu eꞌea ite ḡianirotene, faḡano Aberahamo horoniro zu ane babaḡano Lazaroꞌa ehore radiroteꞌe horoniro.  
\v 24 ꞌOugadu aniꞌa huau niro, 'Mama Aberahamo! Eḡe vetuḡahoꞌi! Lazaro tuḡunadu ane ꞌevore huduꞌa vuo taradu mazanehe amunanoꞌi. E ire roga duhuḡa zamaḡano gigiꞌa boro hideꞌohe.'  
\v 25 Rehano Aberahamoꞌa naenaeniro, 'Ubude, ḡa ꞌahi zamaroꞌi. Ḡaꞌa rahao ḡabode radiudoteꞌe madaḡano ḡau manomano hidinu, u Lazaroꞌe aduga nunu hidinu. Eꞌanoꞌo Lazaroꞌe izidi ꞌahao matuꞌe radiuꞌohe, u ḡaꞌe gigiꞌa hideꞌohe.  
\v 26 Mene eꞌe daꞌo, emeḡe zu zae boꞌaḡanoꞌe dofara boro. Vaze ꞌahoga ꞌahaonoꞌo zae mone fare amoga mene idaḡa, ebu ꞌomanoꞌo emeḡe none fare aroga zuni mene idaḡa.'   
\p
\v 27 ꞌOuge reirotene, maꞌora vazeḡaniꞌa naenaeniro, 'Mama Aberahamo, e ḡa umiꞌeꞌohe. Lazaro eḡe ne tuḡune onamoꞌi.  
\v 28 Negohe niduꞌaꞌe fuꞌo. Lazaroꞌa zeḡe vaḡe onamadu riḡa iraduguzine, ze eḡeꞌa gigiꞌa hideꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa ꞌada mene ariꞌuma.'  
\v 29 Rehano Aberahamoꞌa niro, 'Mose zu peroveta azaḡaniꞌa mirihiroteꞌe soꞌaḡaꞌe zeḡe mazao, eꞌanoꞌo ze eꞌe meꞌodadu faine ederiꞌuma.'  
\v 30 Ebu maꞌora vazeḡaniꞌa niro, 'Mene, mama Aberahamo, rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa bare ḡabodadu zeḡe vaḡe onamine, zeꞌe ḡihuriꞌuma.'  
\v 31 Rehano Aberahamoꞌa niro, 'Ze Mose zu peroveta azaḡa ḡoere mene egozinine, rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡabode iḡuniroteꞌe vazeḡa ḡoere zuni mene hune egohaꞌuma.'”   
\c 17  
\s1 Haḡaize Sauꞌa rae Modeꞌeteꞌe zu Fieꞌeteꞌe moneo Ihoziro  
\r (Mataio 18:6-7, 21:22; Mareko 9:42)  
\p
\v 1 Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Vaze ibi sauꞌano tutuzeꞌeteꞌeꞌe ḡauḡaꞌe mada niduꞌa fureruꞌohe, rehano vaze haḡai sauꞌano tutuzeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe aduga boro hidiꞌuma.  
\v 2 Aniꞌa vaze komeꞌakomeꞌa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga haḡai sauꞌano tutune veꞌonine, hadi horeḡa ane ꞌunuo autadu davarao mae feunogaꞌe ufeta manoḡa.  
\v 3 Eꞌanoꞌo zaeꞌa bare tohutohoꞌi! Ekalesia nabugoꞌa haḡai sauꞌa haḡaoꞌidene, ronoꞌi. Ebu aniꞌa haḡaiḡa sauꞌanonoꞌo ḡihuroꞌidene, haḡaiḡa sauꞌa rae modoꞌi.  
\v 4 Aniꞌa mada tiba zamaḡano ḡae fuꞌo aheu fare ḡae mazao haḡai sauꞌa haḡaoꞌidene, zu ḡae fuꞌo aheu fare ḡae vaḡe bare aradu raenaꞌa, 'E ḡae mazao haḡai sauꞌa haḡaeha. E mene bare haḡaiꞌuma,' rae roꞌidene, ane haḡai sauꞌa aḡutu modoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 5 Apostolo azaḡaniꞌa Zuhiꞌa Boro niro, “Eme ḡa mazao fieꞌeteꞌe ufeta borofoꞌi!”  
\v 6 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa naenaeziro, “Zaꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌetaꞌaꞌe fufu maḡa komeꞌa tiba heuḡa radu Irimo ireḡa ninaꞌa, 'Ḡaeꞌa bare taigota iḡunadu davarao ḡuhuroꞌi,' rae reine, ireḡaniꞌa zae ḡoere egoziniꞌuma.   
\p
\v 7 Zae boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahoga teite reine, tuḡure vazeḡa eꞌeꞌa mebao raha huꞌiꞌuma ga mamoe taufiꞌuma. Ebu aniꞌa gauonoꞌo bare arine, ane zuhiꞌaꞌa ninaꞌa, 'Aroꞌi, ehoradu oganoꞌi,' rae reꞌumahe?  
\v 8 Mene. Ane zuhiꞌaꞌa ꞌahige reꞌuma, 'Eḡe veize ḡorava ogomuḡa ḡorohadu ruhiboꞌi, ebu e ibite oganoga veize danahoꞌi. Eꞌe ḡaruganobuꞌu ḡa oganoꞌi.'  
\v 9 Ebu tuḡure vazeḡaꞌe zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa rateꞌe gauḡa haḡairoteꞌe uꞌano zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa ani mazao manoḡa tauḡi rae niꞌumahe? Mene.  
\v 10 Eꞌanoꞌo zae zuni Badiꞌaꞌa ziꞌeteꞌe gauḡa haḡae hauḡoꞌidene, ꞌahige roꞌi, 'Eme tuḡure azaḡa komeꞌa. Eme emeḡeꞌa haḡae huniteꞌe gauḡa haḡae tauḡeha.'”   
\s1 Refera Azaḡa Gaubanana Faiziro  
\p
\v 11 Iesuꞌa Ierusalema onamiroteꞌe ibiḡano Samaria zu Galilea habaꞌa nemaḡano vitine onamiro.  
\v 12 Ebu aniꞌa ne ꞌahoga diuḡirotene, refera azaḡa gaubanana hidiro. Ze faḡano edanadu Iesu horoniro,  
\v 13 ebu ḡihau huaro, “Vaze boro Iesu, eme vetuḡafoꞌi!”  
\v 14 Iesuꞌa horozadu ziro, “Dibuꞌo azaḡa vaḡe onamadu ahirize ihozoꞌi.” Ebu ze ibio onameꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano, referazeꞌa deheru manoriro.   
\p
\v 15 Zeḡe boꞌaḡano vaze tibaꞌe referaḡaniꞌa manoroga horonirotene, agoḡa boro hina Badiꞌa niguneꞌenaꞌa, Iesu vaḡe bare ariro.  
\v 16 Ebu ani Iesu oda babaḡano ḡuḡuradu manoḡa tauḡi rae niro. Vaze ꞌadiꞌe Samaria vazeḡa.  
\v 17 Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadiniro, “E vaze gaubanana faizeha, rehano vaze fuꞌo ḡazaḡa fareꞌe noumao?  
\v 18 Iuda mene vazeḡa, ḡaꞌa daꞌo aradu Badiꞌa niguneꞌehe?”  
\v 19 Ebu Iesuꞌa niro, “Iḡunadu onamoꞌi. Ḡaeꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, ḡaeꞌa manoreha.”   
\s1 Badiꞌaꞌa Zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe Madaḡa  
\r (Mataio 24:23-28, 37-41)  
\p
\v 20 Mada ꞌahogano Farisea azaḡaniꞌa Iesu ḡadiniro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡaꞌe naniꞌa ariꞌuma?” Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡaꞌe ubumaze hina ḡianoga mene idaḡa.  
\v 21 'Ḡianoꞌi, ꞌahama raꞌohe!' ga 'ꞌOmoa raꞌohe!' rae mene reꞌuma, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zae boꞌaḡano\f + \fr 17:21 \fqa zae zamaḡano \f* zuhiꞌaziꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 22 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌa zazore mone Vaze Ubuga rahao ḡianihi reiteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ariꞌuma, rehano zaꞌe ani mene horoniꞌuma.  
\v 23 Vazeꞌa raenaꞌa, 'Ḡianoꞌi, Iesuꞌe ꞌomo eꞌe,' ga 'Iesuꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe,' rae zoꞌidene, ago buau onamoꞌi zu ago hegotoꞌi.  
\v 24 Vaze Ubuganiꞌa bare arine, vaze niduꞌa huneꞌa horoniꞌuma. Aꞌe viriꞌa vazahadu adure naenaenoꞌo aganadu vaze niduꞌa horoneꞌeteꞌe heuḡa.  
\v 25 Rehano ibite aniꞌe aduga ḡehaḡa hidiꞌuma zu izidi eganiꞌa ani hezahohaꞌuma.   
\p
\v 26 Vaze Ubuganiꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡanoꞌe Noa madaḡa teigiꞌuma.  
\v 27 Eꞌe madaḡano vaze niduꞌa iḡaiḡa haḡainuteꞌe teige ogaunu, gaginu zu hahurinu, onamo Noaꞌa ḡasi boro diuḡiro. Ebu hena zobo boroꞌa aradu zeḡe niduꞌa ruize hauḡiro.  
\v 28 ꞌUguḡaniꞌa Lota madaḡano zuni fureraro. Vaze niduꞌa iḡaiḡa haḡainuteꞌe teige ogaunu, gaginu, hoitinu, seroninu, hihinu ebu neze ogoraunu.  
\v 29 Rehano Lotaꞌa Sodoma mode iḡunirotene, ire roga zu sulifuꞌa\f + \fr 17:29 \ft Sulifuꞌe ire roga ufeta gigiꞌaḡano haḡaifine tiꞌohe, ebu ufeta ḡezauꞌohe. \f* adureonoꞌo irugu teige rururu ovoadu zeḡe niduꞌa hune ruize hauḡiro.   
\p
\v 30 Vaze Ubuganiꞌa bare arine, eꞌe madaḡa teigiꞌuma.  
\v 31 Eꞌe madaḡano iniu ne enogano\f + \fr 17:31 \fqa ne binu hitagano \f* radiuꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe ḡauḡa mouga veize ne zamaḡa mene diuḡiꞌuma. Mebao hiheꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa zuni ne bare mene onamiꞌuma.  
\v 32 Lota inuga zamaroꞌi!  
\v 33 Iniuꞌa ane ḡabone obone giganine, ani ḡabone tuḡutuḡu mene hidiꞌuma. Rehano iniuꞌa ane ḡabone eḡe veize ahetine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma.  
\v 34 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, e bare ariteꞌe oheꞌano vaze aheuꞌe evane tibano bazeꞌeteꞌea ꞌahogaꞌe zamahanadu onamiꞌuma, u ꞌahogaꞌe muhine iḡuniꞌuma.  
\v 35 Roḡae aheuꞌe ꞌuvahu mirune radiuꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano ꞌahogaꞌe zamahanadu iḡuniꞌuma, u ꞌahogaꞌe muhine iḡuniꞌuma.”\f + \fr 17:35 \fv 36 \fv*\fqa Ohoze aheuꞌa mebao gaueꞌeteꞌea ꞌahogaꞌe zamahanadu iḡuniꞌuma, u ꞌahogaꞌe muhine iḡuniꞌuma. \f*  
\v 37 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ḡadiniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eꞌeguḡaniꞌa noumao fureraꞌuma?” Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Naginiꞌa rudaroteꞌe habaꞌano gaozaꞌa nuꞌoraꞌuma.”   
\c 18  
\s1 Ḡozoba zu Kota Vazeḡa Hari Idaidaḡa  
\p
\v 1 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa iḡaiḡa kuranoga zu kuru mene modoga veize hari ꞌahoga idane ziro,  
\v 2 “Haba ꞌahogano kota vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu. Aniꞌe Badiꞌa mene rihoninu zu vaze mene gubazinu.  
\v 3 Eꞌe habaꞌano ḡozoba ꞌahoganiꞌa zuni radiunu. Ani barebare kota vazeḡa vaḡe onamadu uminiro, 'Agire vazeḡaniꞌa eḡe mazao sauꞌa haḡaeꞌohe. Ḡaeꞌa ane haḡai sauꞌa naeḡa hanoꞌi!'  
\v 4 Kota vazeḡaꞌe faḡa hune ḡozoba eꞌe dananoga mene uratiro. Rehano vesuꞌu ani aneꞌa bare ꞌahige rae reiro, 'E Badiꞌa mene rihoneꞌohe zu vaze mene gubazeꞌohe.  
\v 5 Rehano ḡozoba ꞌadi e ufeta ḡunuḡunuheꞌe ꞌahine, e ani umido egadu dananiꞌuma. Mene ꞌougine, ani barebare aradu e fuḡofuḡohiꞌuma!'” \fig Ḡozobaꞌa barebare uminiro|src="43_Luke18:3_ImportunateWidow" size="col" ref="18:3-5" \fig*   
\p
\v 6 Ebu Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa bare reiro, “Zaꞌe Kota vazeḡaniꞌa nagini raꞌeteꞌe egoꞌi.  
\v 7 Badiꞌaꞌe aneꞌa ohotiroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ohere zu madai uminine, zeḡe umido ziniꞌuma, ebu danazogaꞌe mene sasiꞌuma.  
\v 8 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Badiꞌaꞌa nagini duduḡa raꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa ḡarihe ziniꞌuma. Rehano Vaze Ubuganiꞌa bare ariteꞌe madaḡano, Badiꞌa mazao fieꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa nu horoziꞌuma ga mene?”   
\s1 Farisea Vazeḡa zu Takesi Vazeḡa Hari Idaidaḡa  
\p
\v 9 Iesuꞌa ze zeḡeꞌa bare duduḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe zu vaze ovoe ḡiazeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa mazao hari ꞌahoga idane ziro,  
\v 10 “Mada ꞌahogano vaze aheuꞌa kuranoga radu kuru neḡa itiro. Vaze ꞌahogaꞌe Farisea vazeḡa zu ꞌahogaꞌe takesi vazeḡa.  
\v 11 Farisea vazeḡaꞌe edanadu aneꞌa bare ꞌahige kuraro, 'Badiꞌa, manoḡa tauḡi, mazaḡa eꞌe ḡonore azaḡa, haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa, ubuma ḡezo azaḡa zu ꞌuguḡa azaḡa nunu mene heuḡa, ebu takesi vazeḡa ꞌomo zu mene heuḡa.  
\v 12 Fura tiba zamaḡano e ḡae aheu ogomu moneo zaḡozaḡeꞌohe, zu eḡeꞌa hidiroteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌaonoꞌo sinu gaubananao rovonadu sinu tiba ḡauḡa ḡaneꞌohe.'  
\v 13 U takesi vazeḡaꞌe faḡano edanadu adure ḡoha zuni mene ite ehamuꞌenaꞌa ebu ꞌuꞌuga faꞌofaꞌoneꞌenaꞌa ꞌahige kuraro, 'Badiꞌa, eꞌe haḡai sauꞌa vazeḡa. Vetuḡahoꞌi!'   
\p
\v 14 Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, Badiꞌa ubumao duduḡa rae radu neḡa bariroteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe mene Farisea vazeḡa, rehano takesi vazeḡa. Iniu aneꞌa bare niḡa mae itine, Badiꞌaꞌa niḡa mae ovoiꞌuma, u iniu aneꞌa bare niḡa mae ovoine, Badiꞌaꞌa niḡa mae itiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Iesu zu Tahiꞌa Komeꞌakomeꞌa  
\r (Mataio 19:13-15; Mareko 10:13-16)  
\p
\v 15 Mada ꞌahogano vaze nuꞌa eneze guraḡa zuni tutuzadu Iesu vaḡe ariro, mazaḡa Iesuꞌa ꞌevoꞌa zeḡe rana touga uratiro. Rehano ani tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa horozadu tutuze ariroteꞌe azaḡa roziro.  
\v 16 ꞌOugirotene, Iesuꞌa tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌa huziro ebu vaze eꞌea ziro, “Tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌa eḡe mazao tuḡuzoꞌi. Ze ago gararoꞌi. Mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe tahiꞌa komeꞌakomeꞌa teigeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa.  
\v 17 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, iniuꞌa tahiꞌa komeꞌa teige Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe mene mae ḡihinine, ani Badiꞌaꞌa mene zuhiꞌaniꞌuma.”   
\s1 Maꞌora Vazeḡa  
\r (Mataio 19:16-30; Mareko 10:17-31)  
\p
\v 18 Iuda azaḡa ibitoziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Iesu ḡadiniro, “Ihore vazeḡa manoḡa, e nougine, ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma?”  
\v 19 Iesuꞌa niro, “Ḡa nougadu eꞌe manoḡa rae raꞌohe? Vazeni ꞌahoga zuni mene hune manoḡa, rehano Badiꞌa ane daꞌo manoḡa.  
\v 20 Ḡa Mose goro ḡoeꞌa edeḡa: 'Ubuma ago ḡezanoꞌi, vaze ago gorunoꞌi, ago ḡonotanoꞌi, vaze moneo ago ḡuriroꞌi ebu viꞌu mogo gubazoꞌi.'\x + \xo 18:20 \xt Vaḡiniro 20:12-16; Goro 5:16-20\x*”  
\v 21 Aniꞌa naenaeniro, “E komeꞌanonoꞌo ḡoere ꞌahi niduꞌa hegote ariro.”  
\v 22 Iesuꞌa ani ḡoere egadu niro, “Ḡa ḡau ꞌahoga ꞌize mene haḡaeha. Ḡauḡo niduꞌa seronadu zahara azaḡa zenoꞌi. ꞌOugine ḡa adureo ḡau naeḡa boroboro hidiꞌuma. Ebu aradu eḡe hegotoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 23 Aniꞌa Iesu ḡoere igirotene, zamaḡaniꞌa adudaro, mazaḡa aniꞌe ufeta maꞌora vazeḡa.  
\v 24 Ebu Iesuꞌa ani horonadu reiro, “Maꞌora azaḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe azaḡa rougaꞌe riḡa bagaḡa.  
\v 25 Kameroꞌe niduru hoꞌoga diuḡogaꞌe riḡa. Rehano maꞌora vazeḡaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaniꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa rougaꞌe ufeta riḡa.”   
\p
\v 26 Eꞌe igiroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ḡadiniro, “ꞌOugine, iniuꞌa ḡabone hidiꞌuma?”  
\v 27 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Vaze aneꞌa bare ḡabone hidogaꞌe mene idaḡa, rehano Badiꞌaꞌe idaḡa.”  
\v 28 Ebu Peteroꞌa niro, “Eme emeḡe ḡau niduꞌa modadu ḡa hegotiro.”  
\v 29 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, iniu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe veize neḡa, inuga, negoḡa, viꞌa moga ga tahiꞌaḡa modine,  
\v 30 aniꞌe izidi madaḡano ane naeḡa ḡae ḡehaḡa hidiꞌuma, ebu zama moneo ḡabone tuḡutuḡu hidiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Rune moneo Ḡae Uḡiduḡano Ihoziro  
\r (Mataio 20:17-19; Mareko 10:32-34)  
\p
\v 31 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare ani uhiḡano nuꞌozadu ziro, “Eme Ierusalema iteꞌohe. Eꞌea feurine, peroveta azaḡaniꞌa Vaze Ubuga moneo mirihiroteꞌe niduꞌa hudaꞌuma.  
\v 32 Vaze Ubugaꞌe Iuda mene azaḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌinadu zeꞌa ḡirihohaꞌuma, ani mae mazagaroniꞌuma, ani rana soꞌabidiꞌuma,  
\v 33 masiniꞌuma zu maꞌuma. Rehano mada uḡiduḡano aniꞌa bare ḡabode iḡuniꞌuma.”  
\v 34 Rehano Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe ane ḡoere huga mene ederiro, mazaḡa ḡoere huga aꞌe ꞌuꞌuruga ꞌahine, aniꞌa nagini zirotaꞌaꞌe mene ederiro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ubuma Kuruḡa Vazeḡa Fainiro  
\r (Mataio 20:29-34; Mareko 10:46-52)  
\p
\v 35 Iesuꞌa Ieriko hanitirotene, ubuma kuruḡa vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ibi genaḡano ehoradu vaze mazao hadi umidinu.  
\v 36 Ani vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa harae vitauꞌeteꞌe egadu naginiꞌa fureruꞌeteꞌe ḡadimaro.  
\v 37 Ebu zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Nazareta vazeḡa Iesuꞌa vitauꞌohe.”  
\v 38 Ze ꞌouge nirotene, ani ḡihau huaro, “Davida mariga Iesu, eḡe vetuḡahoꞌi!”  
\v 39 ꞌOugirotene, ibitiroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa roniro, “Ḡa sifu radoꞌi!” Rehano ani ufeta ḡihau huaro, “Davida mariga, eḡe vetuḡahoꞌ!”  
\v 40 Ebu Iesuꞌa tue edanadu ziro, “Ani tutune aroꞌi.”  
\v 41 Aniꞌa Iesu vaḡe arirotene, Iesuꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ḡa eḡeꞌa ḡae veize nagini haḡaoga urateꞌohe?” Aniꞌa naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, e ehamatihi.”  
\v 42 Iesuꞌa niro, “Ehamanoꞌi. Ḡaeꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌeꞌa manoꞌeha.”  
\v 43 ꞌOugirotene, ani zogone manoradu faine ehamaro, zu Badiꞌa niguneꞌenaꞌa Iesu hegotiro. Vaze niduꞌa eꞌe horonirotene, zeḡe zuni Badiꞌa niguniro.   
\c 19  
\s1 Iesu zu Zakaio  
\p
\v 1 Iesuꞌa Ieriko diuḡadu vitau onaminu.  
\v 2 Eꞌea vaze ꞌahoga niḡa Zakaioꞌa radiunu. Aniꞌe takesi vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa zu maꞌora vazeḡa.  
\v 3 Ani Iesuꞌe iniu rae ḡianihi reiro, rehano aniꞌe vaze futuꞌa ꞌahine, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa boꞌaḡano Iesu horonogaꞌe mene idararo.  
\v 4 Eꞌanoꞌo ani Iesu ḡianoga radu dure ibitiro, ebu Hiru ireḡa\f + \fr 19:4 \fqa Sikamo ireḡa \f* ꞌahoga sibiriro, mazaḡa Iesuꞌa eꞌe ibiḡano vitaꞌuma rae reiro.  
\v 5 Ebu Iesuꞌa eꞌe habaꞌano feurirotene, ite ehamanadu Zakaio niro, “Zakaio, ḡarihe bua ovaoꞌi. E izidi ḡae neo radiꞌuma.”  
\v 6 ꞌOugadu Zakaioꞌe ḡarihe sibire buanadu matuꞌeꞌenaꞌa, ane neo Iesu mae ḡihiniro. \fig Iesuꞌa Zakaio huniro|src="WA03891b.tif" size="col" ref="19:4" \fig*   
\p
\v 7 Vaze niduꞌa eꞌe horonadu gumude ḡoeriro, “Iesuꞌa haḡai sauꞌa vazeḡa neo diuḡadu radiuꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 8 Ebu Zakaioꞌa edanadu Zuhiꞌa Boro niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, ḡianoꞌi. E izidi eḡe ḡau niduꞌaonoꞌo ḡahaꞌa zahara azaḡa ziniꞌuma. Ebu eḡeꞌa vaze soꞌozadu ḡau ꞌahoga meiniro reine, ḡae ḡazaḡa bare baronoziniꞌuma.”  
\v 9 ꞌOugadu Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Izidi ḡa zu ḡae teite ne tibano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ḡabone hideha. Izidi Zakaio zuni Aberahamo mariga.  
\v 10 Vaze Ubugaꞌe dauḡiroteꞌe azaḡa vaḡadu ḡabozoga veize ariro.”   
\s1 Tuḡure Azaḡa Gaubanana Hari Idaidaḡa  
\r (Mataio 25:14-30)  
\p
\v 11 Iesuꞌa Ierusalema hanitirotene vaze niduꞌa ꞌahige rae zamariro, “Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa zogone fureraꞌuma.” ꞌOugadu ze Iesu ḡoere ꞌize abiteꞌeteꞌea, Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga idane ziro,  
\v 12 “Niḡa boro vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa radiunu. Aniꞌa kini iḡuri mouga veize haba faḡa onamadu bare arihi rae reiro.  
\v 13 Aniꞌa iḡuniroteꞌe madaḡano tuḡureḡa azaḡa gaubanana huzadu zeḡe tibatiba hadi silivaḡa tibatiba\f + \fr 19:13 \fqa mina tibatiba. \ft Mina tibaꞌe mada 100 gauḡa naeḡa. \f* ziniro. Ebu aniꞌa ziro, 'Hadi ꞌahi hina gauadu hadi borofoꞌi, onamo eḡeꞌa bare ariꞌuma.'  
\v 14 U ane haba azaḡaniꞌa ani heꞌeheꞌenadu ane ḡaruna hari odohe onameꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa tuḡunadu haba zuhiꞌaḡa mazao uminiro, 'Eme aniꞌe emeḡe kini rouga mene urateꞌohe.'   
\p
\v 15 Rehano haba zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa ani kinio ohonadu bare ariro. Ebu hadi silivaḡa ziniroteꞌe tuḡure azaḡa huzadu zeꞌa nougenouge hadi borofirotaꞌaꞌe ederihi rae reiro.  
\v 16 Ebu tuḡure vazeḡa ibiꞌaniꞌa ane vaḡe aradu niro, 'Zuhiꞌa, ḡaeꞌa iniroteꞌe hadi silivaḡa tiba hina hadi silivaḡa gaubanana ragate haḡairo.'  
\v 17 Ane zuhiꞌaꞌa niro, 'Manoḡa taugi, ḡaꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa manoḡa! Ḡaeꞌa zamaḡo niduꞌa hina gau komeꞌa faine odohe gauiro ꞌahine, ne niduꞌa gaubanana ḡianeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡano ohoꞌiꞌuma.'  
\v 18 Ebu tuḡure vazeḡa aheuḡaniꞌa aradu niro, 'Zuhiꞌa, ḡaeꞌa iniroteꞌe hadi silivaḡa tiba hina hadi silivaḡa fuꞌo ragate haḡairo.'  
\v 19 Zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa naenaeniro, 'Manoḡa tauḡi! Ḡa zuni ne niduꞌa fuꞌo ḡianeꞌeteꞌe vazeḡano ohoꞌiꞌuma.'   
\p
\v 20 Rehano tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa aradu niro, 'Zuhiꞌa, ḡae hadiꞌe ꞌahi eꞌe. Eḡeꞌa mene daunoga veize dabua hina ꞌumadu ꞌuꞌuru tiro.  
\v 21 Ḡaꞌe vaze riḡa. Vazeꞌa tiroteꞌe ḡauḡa ḡaeꞌa maꞌohe, zu vazeꞌa ḡoraroteꞌe ḡauḡa ḡaeꞌa hiriveꞌohe. Eꞌanoꞌo e ḡa rihoꞌadu ꞌouge haḡairo.'  
\v 22 Zuhiꞌaḡaniꞌa niro, 'Ḡaꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa sauꞌa! Ḡaeꞌa rateꞌe ḡoeꞌa uꞌano, e aduga ḡaniꞌuma! Ḡae zamarone, eꞌe vaze riḡa radu e vazeꞌa tiroteꞌe ḡauḡa maꞌohe zu ḡoraroteꞌe ḡauḡa hiriveꞌohe rae ederirohe?  
\v 23 ꞌOugirotene, ḡa nougadu hadi tiꞌeteꞌe neḡano eḡe hadi mene tiro? ꞌOugifone, e bare aradu hadi eꞌe bare ragate meifo.'   
\p
\v 24 Ebu ani vaetadu uhiḡano edaroteꞌe azaḡa ziro, 'Ani mazaonoꞌo hadi silivaḡa tiba eꞌe moꞌi, ebu hadi silivaḡa gaubanana meiroteꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa hanoꞌi.'  
\v 25 Rehano zeḡeꞌa niro, 'Zuhiꞌa, ani hadi silivaḡa gaubanana amahi meiro.'  
\v 26 Ani naenaeziro, 'Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe. Iniuꞌa nagini hidiroteꞌe faine odohe gauine, ani bare borofe hidiꞌuma. Rehano iniuꞌa nagini hidiroteꞌe mene faine odohe gauine, ani mazao nagini komeꞌa zuni meiniꞌuma.  
\v 27 Ebu eḡeꞌa kini rouga mene uratiroteꞌe agire azaḡa tutuze aradu eḡe zamao mau ruzoꞌi.'”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ierusalema Diuḡiro  
\r (Mataio 21:1-11; Mareko 11:1-11; Ioane 12:12-19)  
\p
\v 28 Iesuꞌa ḡoere hauḡadu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa vitize Ierusalema uꞌa itiro.  
\v 29 Ebu aniꞌa Olivi Maḡano Betefage zu Betania neḡano feurirotene, ane tahiꞌa aheu tuḡuzeꞌenaꞌa ziro,  
\v 30 “Zama mone neḡa onamoꞌi. Eꞌe neḡa diuḡine, vazeni ꞌahoga mene ehoriroteꞌe donikiḡa ubuga batune touga horoniꞌuma. Ebu fuhiꞌadu ꞌahi zamahu aroꞌi.  
\v 31 Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa, 'Nougadu fuiꞌeꞌohe?' rae ḡadizoꞌidene, 'Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa urateꞌohe,' rae noꞌi.”   
\p
\v 32 Ebu Iesuꞌa tuḡuziroteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ibite ne eꞌe onamirotene, Iesuꞌa ziroteꞌe teige doniki ubuga ꞌahoga horoniro.  
\v 33 Ze doniki ubuga eꞌe fuhiꞌiroteꞌe zamaḡano doniki taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ḡadiziro, “Za nougadu doniki ubuga fuhiꞌeꞌohe?”  
\v 34 Zeꞌa naenaeziro, “Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa urateꞌohe.” Ze ꞌouge reirotene doniki taufeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ziniro.  
\v 35 Ebu ze doniki ubuga tutune Iesu vaḡe aradu dabuaze doniki ubuga ḡarunio zahariro, ebu Iesuꞌa eꞌe rana tire ehoriro.  
\v 36 Ebu Iesuꞌa onameꞌeteꞌea, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa dabuaze ane ibio hiraro.   
\p
\v 37 Ebu Iesuꞌa Olivi Maḡanonoꞌo ovoeꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa hanitirotene, ane hegoteꞌeteꞌe vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa niduꞌa onameꞌenaꞌa, matuꞌuzeta huaro zu Badiꞌa niguniro, mazaḡa ze Iesuꞌa haḡainuteꞌe haḡai gigiꞌaḡa niduꞌa horoniro.  
\v 38 Zeꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro,  
\q1 “Zuhiꞌa Boro niḡano areꞌeteꞌe kiniḡaꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune!  
\q2 Adureo uniho manoḡa,  
\q2 hitana huneo Badiꞌa nigunihi!”   
\p
\v 39 Rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa boꞌaḡano Farisea azaḡa nuꞌa Iesu niro, “Ihore vazeḡa, ḡa hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ꞌouge huauꞌeteꞌe gararoꞌi!”  
\v 40 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, ze sifu radiune, hadi niduꞌa ḡihau huaꞌuma.”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ierusalema uꞌano Niaro  
\p
\v 41 Iesuꞌa Ierusalema hanitadu eꞌe horonirotene niaro.  
\v 42 Ebu aniꞌa reiro, “Ierusalema azaḡa, izidi zaꞌe uniho manoḡa maꞌeteꞌe ibiḡa ederifone, manoḡa reifo. Rehano izidi za eꞌe ederoga mene idaḡa.  
\v 43 Mada ꞌahoganiꞌa zae mazao fureraꞌuma. Eꞌe madaḡano zae agire azaḡaniꞌa raha ḡabiꞌa haḡadu merau ganaḡeḡeziꞌuma, ebu zamao haoziꞌuma.  
\v 44 Zeḡeꞌa zae haba zu haba azaḡa niduꞌa rahao zimi feuziꞌuma. Ebu zae ne ogoraroteꞌe hadiḡa niduꞌa fahe ḡuzuhadu hadini ꞌahoga hadi ꞌahoga ranao mene radiꞌuma, mazaḡa zaꞌe Badiꞌaꞌa zae vaḡe ariroteꞌe madaḡa mene ederiro.”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Kuru Neḡa Deheniro  
\r (Mataio 21:12-17; Mareko 11:15-19; Ioane 2:13-22)  
\p
\v 45 Ebu Iesuꞌa kuru neḡa habaꞌano diuḡadu serosero azaḡa hegoze buziro.  
\v 46 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Badiꞌa neꞌe kuru neḡa reꞌuma.' Rehano zaeꞌa kuru neḡaꞌe ḡonore azaḡa neḡano ḡihuniro.”   
\p
\v 47 Ebu Iesuꞌa mada niduꞌa kuru neḡano ihoziro. Rehano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu vaze ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ani matihi reiro.  
\v 48 Rehano ze ani matiteꞌe ibiḡa ꞌahoga mene horoniro, mazaḡa vaze niduꞌa Iesu ḡoere faifaine abitinu.   
\c 20  
\s1 Iesu Gigiꞌaḡa moneo Ḡadiniro  
\r (Mataio 21:23-27; Mareko 11:27-33)  
\p
\v 1 Mada ꞌahogano Iesuꞌa kuru neḡano ihozinu zu hari manoḡa haraminu. Eꞌe madaḡano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa, Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu vaze boroboroꞌa ani vaḡe onamiro.  
\v 2 Ebu ze Iesu ḡadiniro, “Ḡa noꞌe gigiꞌaḡa hina ꞌahiguḡa haḡaeꞌohe? Iniuꞌa ꞌahi gigiꞌaḡa ḡaniro? Efoꞌi.”  
\v 3 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡe zuni ḡadimu ꞌahoga zinihi.  
\v 4 Ioaneꞌa babatiso zinirotaꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo ga vaze mazaonoꞌo? Ehoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 5 Ze zeḡe daꞌo ḡoꞌaneꞌenaꞌa, ꞌahige rae reiro, “Badiꞌa mazaonoꞌo reine, 'Za nougadu Ioane ḡoere mene mae ḡihiniro?' rae ifiꞌuma.  
\v 6 U vaze mazaonoꞌo reine, vaze niduꞌa hadi hina uḡufiꞌuma, mazaḡa zeḡe niduꞌa Ioaneꞌe hube hune peroveta vazeḡa rae mae ḡihineꞌohe.”  
\v 7 Eꞌanoꞌo ze ꞌahige naenaeniro, “Eme aḡuꞌa, Ioaneꞌa babatiso zinirotaꞌaꞌe iniu mazaonoꞌo ariro.”  
\v 8 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡe zuni noꞌe gigiꞌaḡa hina haḡai ꞌahiguḡa haḡaeꞌeteꞌe mene ihoziꞌuma.”   
\s1 Hihi Azaḡa Sauꞌa Hari Idaidaḡa  
\r (Mataio 21:33-46; Mareko 12:1-12)  
\p
\v 9 Iesuꞌa vaze mazao hari ꞌahi idane ziro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa vaini mebaḡa ḡoranadu hihi azaḡa nu ꞌevoreo tiro. Ebu aniꞌa haba ꞌahoga onamadu mada faḡa ragavinu.  
\v 10 Vaini maḡa hiriveꞌeteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa feurirotene, vaini mebaḡa vazeḡaniꞌa vaini maḡa nu mouga radu ane tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahoga hihi azaḡa vaḡe tuḡune onamiro. Rehano zeꞌa ani bounadu ꞌevoꞌa isoḡa tuḡune baroniro.  
\v 11 Hena ani tuḡure vazeḡa ꞌahoga zeḡe vaḡe bare tuḡuniro, rehano zeꞌa ani zuni bouniro, ani mae mazagarone runiro zu ꞌevoꞌa isoḡa tuḡune baroniro.  
\v 12 Ebu ani tuḡure vazeḡa uḡiduḡa zeḡe vaḡe bare tuḡuniro, rehano ze ani ru hanadu uhine baroniro.   
\p
\v 13 ꞌOugadu vaini mebaḡa vazeḡaniꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, 'E nougiꞌuma? Eḡe zamarone ubude tuḡuniꞌuma. Ze ani gubaniꞌuma gaogi.'  
\v 14 Rehano hihi azaḡaniꞌa ubuga horonirotene, zeḡeꞌa ḡoꞌaneꞌenaꞌa, neneḡaniro, 'Aniꞌe moga mazaonoꞌo vaini mebaḡa ꞌadi meiteꞌe vazeḡa. Eme ani matihi, ꞌougine vaini mebaḡa ꞌadiꞌe emeḡeꞌa meꞌuma.'  
\v 15 Eꞌanoꞌo zeꞌa vaini mebaḡanonoꞌo ubuga uhine bunadu mau runiro. ꞌOugadu vaini mebaḡa vazeḡaꞌe zeḡe mazao nougiꞌuma?  
\v 16 Ani aradu hihi azaḡa mau ruziꞌuma ebu vaini mebaḡaꞌe vaze nu ziniꞌuma.”  
\p Vazevazeꞌa hari eꞌe egadu reiro, “Eꞌeguḡaniꞌa mene fureraune manoḡa!”  
\v 17 Ebu Iesuꞌa ze ḡiaḡiazadu ziro, “Tena Buka Zaḡoḡano mirihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa ꞌadi huga zamaroꞌi,  
\q1 'Vazeꞌa hadi hina ne ogorarotene, zeꞌa mae modiroteꞌe hadiḡaꞌe ne duꞌe rinedeꞌeteꞌe hadiḡa reiro.'\x + \xo 20:17 \xt Salamo 118:22 \x*   
\m
\v 18 Iniuꞌa hadi eꞌe rana higaune, ani varadu tahitahiꞌuma, zu hadi eꞌeꞌa vaze ꞌahoga rana higaune, aniꞌe seꞌetiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 19 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡaꞌe Iesuꞌa zeḡe moneo hari idaidaḡa reiroteꞌe ederirotene, Iesu zogone obone tihi reiro. Rehano ze vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa zeḡe mazao maḡuniꞌuma radu rihoziro. \fig Ne duꞌe rinedeꞌeteꞌe hadiḡa|src="43_Luke20:17_Cornerstone_1" size="col" ref="20:17" \fig*   
\s1 Takesiꞌe Iniu Haꞌuma?  
\r (Mataio 22:15-22; Mareko 12:13-17)  
\p
\v 20 Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa zu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡaniꞌa Iesu obone tihi radu ḡiaḡianiro. Zeꞌe vaze duduḡa rae soꞌosoꞌozeꞌeteꞌe rihirihi azaḡa nu Iesu vaḡe tuḡuziro, mazaḡa Iesuꞌa ḡoere nu rae veꞌorine, aniꞌe Roma gavana vazeḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌinihi rae reiro.  
\v 21 Ebu rihirihi azaḡaniꞌa Iesu vaḡe onamadu ḡadiniro, “Ihore vazeḡa, eme edeḡa, ḡaꞌe huga daꞌo ḡoereꞌohe zu ihozeꞌohe, vaze niduꞌa mazao mene inaheꞌohe, ebu Badiꞌa mone ibiḡa hugano ihozeꞌohe.  
\v 22 Emeꞌe Roma kiniḡa mazao takesi haune, duduḡa ga mene?”   
\p
\v 23 Iesuꞌa ze ani soꞌonihi raꞌetaꞌaꞌe ederadu ziro,  
\v 24 “Roma hadiḡa\f + \fr 20:24 \fqa denari \f* tiba ihohoꞌi. Iniu viga zu iniu niḡa eꞌe rana mirihiro?” Zeꞌa naenaeniro, “Aꞌe Roma kiniḡa viga zu niḡa.”  
\v 25 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Tena Roma kiniḡa ḡauꞌe Roma kiniḡa hanoꞌi, u Badiꞌa ḡauꞌe Badiꞌa hanoꞌi.”  
\v 26 ꞌOugadu ze vaze zamao Iesu ḡoereꞌe veꞌoḡa rae rouga mene idararo, ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadimuze naenaeniroteꞌe uꞌano ze zaguzaganadu sifu radiro.   
\s1 Runeonoꞌo Bare Ḡabodeꞌeteꞌe moneo Ḡoeriro  
\r (Mataio 22:23-33; Mareko 12:18-27)  
\p
\v 27 Sadukea azaḡa nuꞌa Iesu vaḡe ariro. Zeꞌe vazeꞌa runeonoꞌo mene bare ḡabode iḡuniꞌuma rae raꞌeteꞌe azaḡa.  
\v 28 Ze Iesu ḡadiniro, “Ihore vazeḡa, Moseꞌa goro ḡoeꞌa ꞌahoga ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Ohoze ꞌahoganiꞌa rudanadu ane inugaꞌe ubuga ꞌoꞌoꞌa reine, ohoze negoḡaniꞌa ḡozobaḡa teite hahuriꞌuma, ebu ubuga furenine ubuganiꞌa rune negoḡa ehaꞌa meꞌuma.'\x + \xo 20:28 \xt Goro 25:5-6 \x*  
\v 29 Hari ꞌahi zamaroꞌi. Nego niduꞌa fuꞌo aheu fare radiunu. Ibiꞌaniꞌa hahuriro ebu ubuga oꞌoꞌa rudaro.  
\v 30 ꞌOugadu negoḡa aheuḡaniꞌa ḡozobaḡa teite hahuriro.  
\v 31 Ebu negoḡa uḡiduḡa zuni ani teite hahuriro. Ebu negoḡa niduꞌa fuꞌo aheu fare ḡozobaḡa teite hahuriro, rehano zeḡe niduꞌa ubudeze oꞌoꞌa rudaro.  
\v 32 Ḡonagano ḡozoba eꞌe zuni rudaro.  
\v 33 ꞌOugadu runeonoꞌo bare ḡabode iḡuniteꞌe madaḡano roḡae aꞌe iniu inuga reꞌuma? Mazaḡa ohoze niduꞌa fuꞌo aheu fareꞌa ani teite hahuriro.”   
\p
\v 34 Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Raha ꞌadao radiuꞌeteꞌe ohozeḡa zu roḡaeḡaꞌe hahureꞌohe.  
\v 35 Rehano runeonoꞌo bare ḡabode iḡunadu Badiꞌa habao radoga idaḡa raꞌeteꞌe ohozeḡa zu roḡaeḡaꞌe mene hahuriꞌuma.  
\v 36 Ebu ze mene bare rudaꞌuma, mazaḡa zeꞌe tuḡure viga heuḡa. Zeꞌe runeonoꞌo ḡabodiroteꞌe azaḡa uꞌano, Badiꞌa ubuga raꞌohe.  
\v 37 Rune azaḡaniꞌa bare ḡabodeꞌeteꞌe moneo, Mose zuni ire renoga hariḡa ihoziro. Eꞌea ani Badiꞌa ꞌahige huniro, 'Aberahamo Badiꞌa, Isako Badiꞌa zu Iakobo Badiꞌa.'\x + \xo 20:37 \xt Vaḡiniro 3:6 \x*  
\v 38 Badiꞌaꞌe mene rune azaḡa Badiꞌa, rehano ḡabone azaḡa Badiꞌa. Zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe Badiꞌa veize ḡabodeꞌohe.”   
\p
\v 39 Ebu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa nuꞌa naenaeniro, “Ihore vazeḡa, ḡae naenaeꞌe manoḡa tauḡi!”  
\v 40 Eꞌe enogano ze Iesu mene bare inare ḡadiniro.   
\s1 Kerisoꞌe Iniu Mariga?  
\r (Mataio 22:41-46; Mareko 12:35-37)  
\p
\v 41 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Nougadu vazeꞌa Kerisoꞌe Davida mariga raꞌohe?  
\v 42 Davidaꞌa Keriso moneo Salamo bukaḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro,  
\q1 'Badiꞌaꞌa eḡe Zuhiꞌa Boro niro,  
\q2 “Eḡe edaꞌe moneo ehoroꞌi,   
\q1
\v 43 onamo eḡeꞌa agireḡo niduꞌa madu odaḡo ꞌuꞌuḡano raharahaziꞌuma.”'\x + \xo 20:42-43 \xt Salamo 110:1\x*   
\m
\v 44 Davidaꞌa Keriso mazao, 'Zuhiꞌa Boro,' rae huniro. Tena Kerisoꞌe nougenouge Davida mariga reꞌuma?”   
\s1 Mose Goro Ḡoeꞌa Ihozeꞌeteꞌe Azaḡa Ḡiazoꞌi  
\r (Mataio 23:1-36; Mareko 12:38-40; Luka 11:37-54)  
\p
\v 45 Vaze niduꞌa Iesu ḡoere abitiroteꞌea, Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro,  
\v 46 “Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡa ḡiazoꞌi. Ze dabua manoḡa faḡa vidau ragavoga, vaze ḡehaḡa habaꞌano vazeꞌa ze gubazeꞌenaꞌa, zeḡe mazao unihoga, nuꞌonuꞌo neḡano vaze boroboroꞌa ehoreꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano ehoroga, zu muio nize boro azaḡaniꞌa ehoreꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano ehoroga urateꞌohe.  
\v 47 Ebu zeꞌe ḡozoba soꞌozadu toheze niduꞌa meizeꞌohe, zu vaze ihozifine faḡafe ḡurire kurauꞌohe. ꞌUguḡa azaḡaꞌe aduga boro bagaḡa hidiꞌuma.”   
\c 21  
\s1 Ḡozoba Ḡahunone Hadiḡa  
\r (Mareko 12:41-44)  
\p
\v 1 Iesuꞌa kuru neḡano maꞌora azaḡaniꞌa ḡahunone mauḡa zamaḡano zeḡe ḡahunone ufiꞌeteꞌe horoziro.  
\v 2 Ebu zahara ḡozobaḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa kopa hadiḡa komeꞌa aheu ufiroteꞌe zuni horoniro.  
\v 3 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, zahara ḡozobaḡa ꞌadaꞌa vaze niduꞌa ufeta vitize hadi boro ofeha.  
\v 4 Zeḡe niduꞌaꞌe hadize ḡehaḡa rehano, tahiḡa daꞌo ofeha. U ḡozoba ꞌadiꞌe zahara roḡaeḡa, rehano ane hadiḡa niduꞌa ebu ane ogomu hadiḡa niduꞌa ofeha.” \fig Ḡozoba ḡahunoneḡa|src="WA03903b.tif" size="col" ref="21:1-4" \fig*   
\s1 Kuru Neḡa Fahe Ḡuzuhiteꞌe moneo Ḡoeriro  
\r (Mataio 24:1-2; Mareko 13:1-2)  
\p
\v 5 Iesu tahiꞌa nuꞌa kuru neḡa horonadu aꞌe hadi manoḡa zu Badiꞌa haroteꞌe ḡahunoneḡa hina rohorohoniroteꞌe moneo niguniro. Rehano Iesuꞌa ziro,  
\v 6 “Izidi zaeꞌa horoneꞌeteꞌe ḡauḡa niduꞌaꞌe fahe ḡuzuhiteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ariꞌuma. Eꞌe madaḡano hadini ꞌahoga hadi ꞌahoga rana mene radiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Haḡai Nu Badeḡa zu Aduga  
\r (Mataio 24:3-14; Mareko 13:3-13)  
\p
\v 7 ꞌOugadu ze Iesu ḡadiniro, “Ihore vazeḡa, eꞌeguḡaniꞌa naniꞌa fureraꞌuma? Ebu eꞌeguḡaniꞌa nariga fureranateꞌe madaḡanoꞌe nagi haḡai nu badeḡaniꞌa ibite fureraꞌuma?”  
\v 8 Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa zae mene soꞌosoꞌozifine tohutohoꞌi. Vaze ḡehaḡaniꞌa eḡe niḡano aradu ꞌahige reꞌuma, 'Eꞌe Keriso,' ebu 'Madaḡa ꞌai haniteha!' Rehano ze ago hegotoꞌi.  
\v 9 Uti zu roteto hariḡa egoꞌidene, ago rihanoꞌi. Eꞌeguḡaniꞌa hube hune ibite fureraꞌuma, rehano mada ḡonagaꞌe zogone mene ariꞌuma.”  
\v 10 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Haba ꞌahoganiꞌa haba ꞌahoga teite utitiꞌuma, zu gavamani ꞌahoganiꞌa gavamani ꞌahoga teite utitiꞌuma.  
\v 11 Haba nunuo habaꞌa borofe hagariꞌuma, zagaꞌa hiaꞌuma zu ugi boroꞌa fureraꞌuma. Ebu adureonoꞌo riho ḡauḡa zu haḡai nu badeḡa boroboroꞌa fureraꞌuma.   
\p
\v 12 Rehano eꞌeguḡaniꞌa ꞌizema fureranogano, vazevazeꞌa za oboze teadu sausauziꞌuma, ebu nu'onu'o neḡano zu ḡuꞌa neḡano ohoze tiꞌuma. Eḡe uꞌano, kini zu gavana azaḡa mazao zae tutuze onamiꞌuma.  
\v 13 Aꞌe zaeꞌa zeḡe mazao eḡe hari manoḡa rae fureniteꞌe madaḡa reꞌuma.  
\v 14 Eꞌanoꞌo zamaze rinedadu nougenouge zae bare biriteꞌe moneo zamaze ago ibite adudanoꞌi.  
\v 15 Mazaḡa eḡeꞌa ḡoere zu zamarone huhuzaḡa zenadu agireze ꞌahoganiꞌa zuni zae mene agatoziꞌuma ebu zae ḡoere mene hezahohaꞌuma.  
\v 16 Zae vize moze, negoze, nabudize zu zae vazeꞌa zuni za revoziniꞌuma, ebu zae boꞌaḡano nuꞌe runeo tuḡuziꞌuma.  
\v 17 Eḡe uꞌano vaze niduꞌa za heꞌeheꞌeziꞌuma.  
\v 18 Rehano iguze tiba zuni mene dauniꞌuma.  
\v 19 Zaeꞌa edau gigaraune, ḡabone hidiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Ierusalema Habaꞌa Ruiniꞌuma  
\r (Mataio 24:15-21; Mareko 13:14-19)  
\p
\v 20 “Ierusalemaꞌe uti azaḡaniꞌa ganaḡeḡenoga horonoꞌidene, aꞌe Ierusalema ruiniteꞌe madaḡa ꞌai haniteha rae ederiꞌuma.  
\v 21 Eꞌe madaḡano Iudea habaꞌano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe maḡa ferau itoꞌi. Ierusalema zamaḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe ferau vaḡinoꞌi, ebu guniꞌa neḡano radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Ierusalema ago diuḡoꞌi.  
\v 22 Mazaḡa eꞌe madaḡaꞌe Buka Zaḡoḡano mirihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa hudanadu Ierusalema azaḡa aduga boro ziniteꞌe madaḡa reꞌuma.  
\v 23 Eꞌe madaḡano ahiꞌeta roḡaeḡa zu nune hina ene guraḡa ḡubuzeꞌeteꞌe roḡaeḡaꞌe feranoga mene idaḡa radu aduga boro hidiꞌuma! Raha ꞌahao aduga boro bagaḡaniꞌa fureraꞌuma, ebu Badiꞌa zama ḡugiꞌa vaze mazao fureraꞌuma.  
\v 24 Zeꞌe benisi hina zimi ruziꞌuma, ebu ḡuꞌa azaḡa teige oboze teadu ꞌavoꞌa habaꞌa nunu tutuze onamiꞌuma. Iuda mene azaḡaniꞌa Ierusalema ruinadu zuhiꞌaniꞌuma, onamo zeḡe madaꞌa hauḡiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ariteꞌe Madaḡa  
\r (Mataio 24:29-31; Mareko 13:24-27)  
\p
\v 25 “Ebu mada, bato zu buzuva ragano haḡai nu badeḡa horoniꞌuma. Raha ꞌada haba nunu azaḡaniꞌa davara zu saꞌu boroboro guguḡa uꞌano, rihau rudaꞌuma ebu zamazeꞌa ꞌadaꞌadiꞌuma.  
\v 26 Vazeꞌa nagini rahao ꞌada fureratitaꞌaꞌe edereꞌe ꞌahine, rihau rudanadu higau bauriꞌuma, mazaḡa adure gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa hagahagariꞌuma.  
\v 27 Eꞌe madaḡano ze Vaze Ubuganiꞌa gigiꞌaḡa boro zu agaḡa boro hune madu ḡoze hina areꞌeteꞌe horoniꞌuma.  
\v 28 ꞌAhiguḡaniꞌa ḡadahe fureranoꞌidene, iḡunadu dude ehamanoꞌi, mazaḡa Badiꞌaꞌa zae ḡaboziteꞌe madaḡa ꞌai haniteha.”   
\s1 Figi Ireḡa Hari Idaidaḡa  
\r (Mataio 24:32-35; Mareko 13:28-31)  
\p
\v 29 Ebu Iesuꞌa hari ꞌahoga idane ziro, “Figi ireḡa zu ire nunu ḡianoꞌi.  
\v 30 Za zaeꞌa bare ire rouḡaniꞌa udufaꞌoga horoneꞌetene, irugu madaḡaniꞌa haniteha rae edereꞌohe.  
\v 31 Eꞌe teige, ꞌahiguḡaniꞌa fureranoga horonoꞌidene, Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa haniteha rae ederoꞌi.  
\v 32 Eḡeꞌa hube hune ziꞌohe, izidi egaꞌe mene hauḡiꞌuma, onamo ꞌahiguḡa niduꞌa fureraꞌuma.  
\v 33 Adure zu rahaꞌe hauḡiꞌuma, rehano eḡe ḡoereꞌe mene hune hauḡiꞌuma.”   
\s1 Ruhibe Radoꞌi  
\p
\v 34 “Zaꞌe ufeta reꞌoreꞌeteꞌe zu gageꞌeteꞌe ebu ḡaboneze zamare borofeꞌeteꞌe uꞌano, zamaze mene adudafine tohutohoꞌi. Ebu zaꞌe eḡeꞌa bare areꞌeteꞌe madaḡano mene zaguzagafine zae bare ḡiazoꞌi, mazaḡa eꞌe madaḡaꞌe ꞌahiri miniḡaniꞌa mani tabara ꞌahiriniꞌeteꞌe teigiꞌuma.  
\v 35 Eꞌe madaḡaniꞌa raha ꞌada vaze niduꞌa mazao fureraꞌuma.  
\v 36 Eꞌanoꞌo aduganiꞌa fureratiteꞌe madaḡano feranoga zu Vaze Ubuga zamao edanoga veize, mada niduꞌa kurauꞌenaꞌa tohutohe radoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 37 Mada niduꞌa Iesuꞌe kuru neḡano ihozinu, u ohere niduꞌaꞌe vaḡinadu Olivi Maḡa rae huneꞌeteꞌe maḡano radiunu.  
\v 38 Ebu oherebau uzeuze vaze niduꞌa Iesu ḡoere abitoga veize kuru neḡa onamiro.   
\c 22  
\s1 Iudaꞌa Iesu Revohatihi Reiro  
\r (Mataio 26:1-5, 14-16; Mareko 14:1-2, 10-11; Ioane 11:45-53)  
\p
\v 1 Isiti Oꞌoꞌa ꞌUvauḡa Odoga Muiḡa, niḡa ꞌahogaꞌe Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa madaḡaniꞌa hanitiro.  
\v 2 Dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Iesu matiteꞌe ibiḡa nu vaḡiro, mazaḡa ze vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa maḡuniꞌuma radu rihoziro.   
\p
\v 3 Isakariota vazeḡa, niḡa Iudaꞌe Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano tahiꞌa ꞌahoga. Sataniꞌa ane zama diuḡiro.  
\v 4 Aniꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu kuru neḡa uti vazeḡa boroboro vaḡe onamadu zeḡe ꞌevoreo Iesu riꞌiniteꞌe ibiḡa ḡoꞌane vaḡiro.  
\v 5 Ze matuꞌe rudanadu Iuda hadi haꞌuma rae ḡoitoriro.  
\v 6 Iudaꞌa zuni, “Idaḡa,” radu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa oꞌoꞌa madaḡano Iesu riꞌinoga veize mada manoḡa ꞌahoga vaḡiro.   
\s1 Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa Ruhibe Tiro  
\r (Mataio 26:17-25; Mareko 14:12-21; Ioane 13:21-30)  
\p
\v 7 Isiti Oꞌoꞌa ꞌUvahuḡa Odoga Muiḡa zamaḡano mada ibiꞌaꞌe Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa. Eꞌe madaḡano dibuꞌo mamoeḡa ubuga maro.  
\v 8 Eꞌe madaḡa meirotene, Iesuꞌa Petero zu Ioane tuḡuzeꞌenaꞌa, ziro, “Onamadu emeḡe veize Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ogomuḡa ruhibe toꞌi.”  
\v 9 Ebu zeꞌa ḡadiniro, “Ḡa urao eme nouma ruhibe tiꞌuma?”  
\v 10 Aniꞌa naenaeziro, “Ne boro diuḡine, ohoze ꞌahoganiꞌa vu ḡoḡoreḡa odohe onameꞌeteꞌe horoniꞌuma. Ebu ani hegotadu aneꞌa diuḡeꞌeteꞌe neḡa diuḡoꞌi.  
\v 11 Diuḡadu eꞌe ne vazeḡa noꞌi, 'Ihore vazeḡaniꞌa ꞌahige raꞌohe: E eḡe tahiꞌatahiꞌa teite Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ogomuḡa atihi. Iꞌudo azaḡa veize ruhibiroteꞌe habaꞌaꞌe noumao?'  
\v 12 ꞌOugine, aniꞌa ne hitagano bazuni neḡa boro ꞌahoga ihoziꞌuma, zu zaꞌe ehoro habaꞌa ruhibe teateꞌe horoniꞌuma. Eꞌea ogomufe ruhibe toꞌi.”  
\v 13 Ze iḡunadu onamiro, ebu Iesuꞌa ziroteꞌe idunane niduꞌa horoniro. ꞌOugadu Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ruhibe tiro.   
\s1 Ḡonaga Ogomuḡa Aro  
\r (Mataio 26:26-30; Mareko 14:22-26; 1Korinto 11:23-25)  
\p
\v 14 Madaḡaniꞌa feurirotene, Iesu apostolo azaḡa teite ogomu fataḡa uhiḡano ehoriro.  
\v 15 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “E ꞌizema aduga hidogano, zae teite Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡa ogomuḡa ꞌadi anoga hube hune uratiro.  
\v 16 Mazaḡa eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, eꞌe Mui ogomuḡa ꞌahiꞌe mene bare aꞌuma, onamo Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡano Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡaniꞌa hugano fureraꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 17 Ebu aniꞌa vaini vuḡa bioḡa madu Badiꞌa mazao kuraro ebu ziro, “Bio ꞌahi madu zaꞌe tahitahe gagoꞌi.  
\v 18 Mazaḡa eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, eꞌe vaini vuḡa mene bare gagiꞌuma, onamo Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡaniꞌa ariꞌuma.”  
\v 19 Ebu ani ꞌuvahu odoga meiro zu Badiꞌa mazao kuranadu vahege ziniro, ebu ziro, “ꞌUvahu odoga ꞌahiꞌe zae veize moditeꞌe ahirihe. Zaeꞌa eḡe zamarifine iḡaiḡa ꞌahi haḡaoꞌi.”   
\p
\v 20 Ebu ḡorava ogomuḡa enogano ani vaini vuḡa bioḡa madu ziro, “Vaini vuḡa bioḡa ꞌahiꞌe eḡeꞌa zae veize beꞌuneꞌeteꞌe ruhe hina ohoneꞌeteꞌe ḡoitoreḡa iziga.  
\v 21 Rehano eḡe revoniteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe eḡe teite ogau tiburuꞌohe.  
\v 22 Vaze Ubugaꞌe Badiꞌa urao rudaꞌuma. Rehano ani revohatiteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe aduga boro hidiꞌuma.”  
\v 23 ꞌOugadu ze zeḡeꞌa bare ḡadimutitiro, “Emeḡe boꞌaḡano iniuꞌa ꞌougiꞌuma?”   
\s1 Iniuꞌe Niḡa Boro?  
\p
\v 24 Ebu Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌa boꞌaḡano iniuꞌe ḡihiꞌa hune radu ze zeḡeꞌa bare taꞌirotitiro.  
\v 25 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Badiꞌa aḡuꞌa azaḡa habaꞌano kini niduꞌaꞌe zeḡe haba azaḡa riḡa zuhiꞌaziꞌohe. Ebu inaraze hina zeḡe haba azaḡa rana edauꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe zeḡeꞌa bare 'Duꞌu Vazeḡa' rae huzeꞌohe.  
\v 26 Rehano za ze ago teigoꞌi. Zae boꞌaḡano vaze ḡihiꞌaḡa huneꞌe tahiꞌa komeꞌa teigiꞌuma, ebu iniu zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe vazeḡaꞌe tuḡure vazeḡa teigiꞌuma.  
\v 27 Iniuꞌe ufeta ḡihiꞌaḡa? Ehore ogauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ga tuḡure vazeḡa? Aꞌe ehore ogauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa. Rehano eꞌe zae boꞌaḡano tuḡure vazeḡa heuḡa.   
\p
\v 28 Zaꞌe eḡeꞌa aduga hidiroteꞌe zamaḡano eḡe teite radiroteꞌe azaḡa.  
\v 29 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡe Mamaꞌa ḡau niduꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡa iniroteꞌe teige, eḡeꞌa zae zuni eꞌe gigiꞌaḡa ziniꞌohe.  
\v 30 Ebu zaꞌe eḡeꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano eḡe teite ogaꞌuma zu gagiꞌuma, ebu kini ehoro habaꞌano ehoradu Isaraela azaḡa, urabo niduꞌa gaubanana aheu fare kotaziꞌuma.”   
\s1 Peteroꞌa Iesu Oꞌoniꞌuma rae Ihoziro  
\r (Mataio 26:31-35; Mareko 14:27-31; Ioane 13:36-38)  
\p
\v 31 Ebu Iesuꞌa Simona niro, “Simona, Simona, ꞌadi egoꞌi. Sataniꞌa vuidi zuizuineꞌeteꞌe\f + \fr 22:31 \ft Vuidi hiriveꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano vuidi zuizuinine, hugaꞌe zamaḡano radiuꞌohe ebu ogaḡaꞌe rururuꞌohe. \f* teige, zae zama tuhunoga veize Badiꞌa uminiro.  
\v 32 Rehano ḡaeꞌa eḡe mazao fieꞌeteꞌeꞌa mene dauḡifine, e ḡae veize kuraro. Eꞌanoꞌo ḡaeꞌa ḡihuradu eḡe vaḡe bariteꞌe madaḡano negoḡo duḡuru inarazoꞌi.”  
\v 33 Peteroꞌa naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eꞌe ḡae teite ḡuꞌa neḡano diuḡiꞌuma, ebu ḡae teite rudaꞌuma zuni idaḡa!”  
\v 34 Iesuꞌa niro, “Petero, eḡeꞌa ḡaꞌohe, izidi ohere kokorokuꞌa ꞌizema uganogano, ḡaeꞌa ḡae uḡidu oꞌoheꞌenaꞌa, e aḡuꞌa rae reꞌuma.”   
\s1 Hadi Fuseḡa, Nihara zu Benisi  
\p
\v 35 Ebu Iesuꞌa ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa ziro, “Zaeꞌa eḡe gau haḡaoga veize tuḡuziroteꞌe madaḡano zaꞌe hadi fuseḡa, nihara ebu tamaka mene odohe onamiro. Eꞌe madaḡano ḡau ꞌahoga ferezirohe?” Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Mene.”  
\v 36 Aniꞌa ziro, “Izidi zaꞌe hadi fusezeta zu niharazeta roꞌidene, eꞌe moꞌi. Ebu zaꞌe benisize oꞌoꞌa roꞌidene, dabuaze seronadu eꞌe hoitoꞌi.\f + \fr 22:36 \ft Eꞌe hugaꞌe, 'Aduga hideꞌeteꞌe uꞌano ruhiboꞌi.' \f*  
\v 37 Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Vazevazeꞌa aniꞌe ḡonore azaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga rae zamariꞌuma.'\x + \xo 22:37 \xt Isaia 53:12 \x* Eḡeꞌa ziꞌohe, eꞌe ḡoeꞌaniꞌa eḡe mazao hudaꞌuma. Hube hune eḡe moneo mirihiroteꞌeꞌa izidi hudauꞌohe.”  
\v 38 Zeḡeꞌa naenaeniro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, emeḡe mazaoꞌe benisi aheu.” Iesuꞌa ziro, “Ahiḡa.”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Olivi Maḡano Kuraro  
\r (Mataio 26:36-46; Mareko 14:32-42)  
\p
\v 39 Ebu Iesuꞌe iḡaiḡa haḡainuteꞌe teige, Olivi Maḡa onamiro zu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌa ane hegotiro.  
\v 40 Aniꞌa eꞌe habaꞌano feuradu ziro, “Sataniꞌa tuhuzadu zaeꞌa mene uitifine kuranoꞌi.”  
\v 41 Ebu Iesuꞌa ze modadu tahiḡa mobade onamiro ebu obena hina tuḡadu kuraro,  
\v 42 “Mama, ḡa uratoꞌidene, eḡe mazaonoꞌo bio aduga ꞌadi mae vaḡinoꞌi. Rehano eḡe mene urao, ḡae urao daꞌo haḡaoꞌi.”  
\v 43 Eꞌe madaḡano tuḡure viga ꞌahoganiꞌa adureonoꞌo ane vaḡe ovadu inaraharo.  
\v 44 Ani zamaḡa ufeta adudanadu zamaḡa niduꞌa hina ufeta inare kuraro. Eꞌanoꞌo irairaḡaniꞌa ru teige rahao sore buaro.   
\p
\v 45 Ebu Iesuꞌa kuru hauḡadu ane tahiꞌatahiꞌa vaḡe bare onamirotene ze bazeꞌeteꞌe horoziro, mazaḡa zamaze ufeta aradu ahirizeꞌa taoraro.  
\v 46 Eꞌanoꞌo aniꞌa ziro, “Za nougadu baze radiuꞌohe? Iḡunoꞌi, ebu Sataniꞌa tuhuzadu zaeꞌa mene uitifine kuranoꞌi.”   
\s1 Iesu Obone Tiro  
\r (Mataio 26:47-56; Mareko 14:43-50; Ioane 18:3-11)  
\p
\v 47 Iesuꞌa ꞌize ḡoereꞌeteꞌea, vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa ani vaḡe ariro. Ebu Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana aheu fare boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga, Iudaꞌa ibitadu Iesu furaꞌinoga veize ani uhiḡa ariro.  
\v 48 Rehano Iesuꞌa niro, “Iuda, ḡaꞌe Vaze Ubuga furaꞌinadu revohatihi raꞌehe?”  
\v 49 Iesu tahiꞌatahiꞌaꞌe naginiꞌa fureruꞌeteꞌe horonadu Iesu niro, “Zuhiꞌa Boro, eme benisi hina utitoziniꞌumahe?”  
\v 50 Ebu zeḡe boꞌaḡano ꞌahoganiꞌa benisi ahase bunadu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa tuḡure vazeḡa udirotene, edaꞌe teḡaḡa variꞌe butiro.  
\v 51 Rehano Iesuꞌa niro, “Ago ꞌougoꞌi!” Ebu Iesuꞌa vaze eꞌe teḡa obonadu fainiro.   
\p
\v 52 Ebu Iesuꞌa ani obone touga veize ariroteꞌe dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa, kuru neḡa vazeḡa boroboro zu vaze boroboro ziro, “Zaꞌe ḡonore vazeḡa obone tiꞌeteꞌe teige, benisi ebu somori boro madu eḡe obohe touga veize arahe?  
\v 53 Mada niduꞌa eꞌe zae teite kuru neḡa habaꞌano radiunu. Eꞌe madaḡano zaꞌe mene obohe tiro. Rehano izidiꞌe zae madaḡa zu uzaboꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe madaḡa.”   
\s1 Peteroꞌa Iesu Oꞌoniro  
\r (Mataio 26:57-58, 69-75; Mareko 14:53-54, 66-72; Ioane 18:12-18, 25-27)  
\p
\v 54 Zeꞌa Iesu obone teadu dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡa ne tutune onamiro. U Peteroꞌe faḡanonoꞌo zeḡe ḡaruna hegotiro.  
\v 55 Vaze nuꞌa eꞌe ne habaꞌa nemaḡano ire roga hofadu ehore ḡeḡemaḡiro. Petero zuni zeḡe teite ehoriro.  
\v 56 ꞌOugirotene, tuḡure roḡaeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa Peteroꞌe ire roga genaḡano ehoreꞌeteꞌe horoniro. Ani Petero ḡiane runeꞌenaꞌa reiro, “Vaze ꞌadi zuni Iesu teite radiudo.”  
\v 57 Rehano Peteroꞌa oꞌonadu niro, “Roḡae, e ani aḡua.”  
\v 58 Mada tahiḡa enogano vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa horonadu niro, “Ḡa zuni Iesu hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano ꞌahoga.” Rehano Peteroꞌa niro, “Ohoze, eꞌe mene!”  
\v 59 Mada tahiḡa ḡarugano, vaze ꞌahoganiꞌa barebare ḡoeriro, “Vaze ꞌadi hube hune Iesu teite radiudo, mazaḡa ani zuni Galilea vazeḡa.”  
\v 60 Rehano Peteroꞌa naenaeniro, “Ohoze, e ḡaꞌa nagini raꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa!”  
\p Peteroꞌa ꞌize ḡoereꞌeteꞌea, kokorokuꞌa ugaro.  
\v 61 Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa vaetadu Petero ḡianiro. ꞌOugadu Peteroꞌe Zuhiꞌa Boroꞌa ꞌahige rae niroteꞌe zamariro, “Izidi ohere kokorokuꞌa ꞌizema uganogano, ḡaꞌa ḡae uḡidu eḡe oꞌohiꞌuma.”  
\v 62 Ebu aniꞌa ne enona buanadu niau rudaro. \fig Peteroꞌa Iesu oꞌoniro|src="WA03920b.tif" size="col" ref="22:54-62" \fig*   
\s1 Uti Azaḡaniꞌa Iesu rae Sausauniro zu Masiniro  
\r (Mataio 26:67-68; Mareko 14:65)  
\p
\v 63 Iesu ḡiane radiuꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa ani ḡirihoharo zu bouniro.  
\v 64 Ze ani ubuma ꞌuadu ḡadiniro, “Peroveta vazeḡa, iniuꞌa ḡa bouꞌeha? Efoꞌi.”  
\v 65 Ebu ze ḡoere nunu hina ani rae sausauniro.   
\s1 Iesu Kotao Ohoniro  
\r (Mataio 26:59-66; Mareko 14:55-64; Ioane 18:19-24)  
\p
\v 66 Irarirotene, dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa nuꞌoranadu vaze boroboroꞌa ibitohauꞌeteꞌe kotaḡano ḡoꞌaniro. Ebu Iesuꞌe zeḡe kotao tutune mae ohoniro.  
\v 67 Ebu zeꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌe Keriso roꞌidene, efoꞌi.” Iesuꞌa naenaeziro, “Eḡeꞌa, 'Oꞌe,' rae zine zuni, zaꞌe eḡe ḡoere mene mae ḡihiniꞌuma.  
\v 68 Ebu eḡeꞌa, 'E Kerisohe?' rae ḡadizine zuni, zaꞌe mene naenaehiꞌuma.  
\v 69 Rehano izidionoꞌo onamo zama mone Vaze Ubuganiꞌa Gigiꞌaḡa Boro Badiꞌaḡa edaꞌe moneo ehoriꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 70 Zeḡe niduꞌa ḡadiniro, “Tena ḡaꞌe Badiꞌa Ubugahe?” Aniꞌa ziro, “Za zaeꞌa bare eꞌe Keriso rae raꞌohe.”  
\v 71 Ebu ze zeḡeꞌa bare neneḡaniro, “Eme aniꞌe veꞌoḡa rae raꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa bare vaḡiꞌumahe? Emeḡeꞌa ane hebeonoꞌo ḡoere veꞌoḡa rateꞌe egeha!”   
\c 23  
\s1 Pilato zamao Iesu mae Ohoniro  
\r (Mataio 27:1-2, 11-14; Mareko 15:1-5; Ioane 18:28-38)  
\p
\v 1 Ebu kota azaḡa niduꞌa iḡunadu Iesu Pilato vaḡe tutune onamiro.  
\v 2 Zeḡeꞌa Pilato mazao Iesuꞌe veꞌoḡa rae fureniro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe emeḡe ne azaḡa soꞌozadu ibi veꞌoḡano tutuzeꞌohe. Roma kiniḡa mazao takesi hauꞌeteꞌe garareꞌohe, zu ani aneꞌa bare raenaꞌa, 'Eꞌe Keriso, kini,' rae raꞌohe.”  
\v 3 Eꞌanoꞌo Pilatoꞌa Iesu ḡadiniro, “Ḡaꞌe Iuda azaḡa kinihe?” Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Oꞌe, ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare eꞌe kini rae raꞌohe.”  
\v 4 ꞌOugadu Pilatoꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa ziro, “E ani mazaonoꞌo veꞌoḡa ꞌahoga mene horoneꞌohe.”  
\v 5 Rehano ze teꞌoteꞌau ḡoeriro, “Aniꞌe Galilea habaꞌanonoꞌo Iudea habaꞌa niduꞌa onamo Ierusalema ꞌahi zuni vaze ḡehaḡa ihozeꞌenaꞌa, ibi veꞌoḡano tutuzeꞌohe.”   
\s1 Iesu Heroda zamao mae Ohoniro  
\p
\v 6 Pilatoꞌa ḡoereze egadu ḡadiziro, “Iesuꞌe Galilea vazeḡahe?”  
\v 7 Ani Iesuꞌe kini Herodaꞌa ḡianeꞌeteꞌe Galilea habaꞌa vazeḡa rae ederadu ani Heroda vaḡe tuḡuniro. Eꞌe madaḡano Herodaꞌe Ierusalema zamaḡano radiunu.   
\p
\v 8 Herodaꞌa Iesu horonirotene, matuꞌe rudaro, mazaḡa ani amahionoꞌo Iesu ḡianihi reiro, zu Iesu hariḡa igiro ꞌahine, Iesuꞌa haḡai gigiꞌa haḡaoga horonihi reiro.  
\v 9 Eꞌanoꞌo Herodaꞌe ḡadimu ḡehaḡa Iesu ḡadiniro, rehano Iesuꞌa mene naenaeniro.  
\v 10 Eꞌea edau radiuꞌeteꞌe dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa ihozeꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Iesu ꞌuteꞌenaꞌa, ufeta rae sausauniro.  
\v 11 Heroda zu ane uti azaḡaꞌe Iesu rae sausauniro zu ḡirihoharo. Ebu dabua manoḡa vidohanadu Pilato vaḡe bare tuḡune onamiro.  
\v 12 Ibite Heroda ebu Pilatoꞌe agirotitido, rehano eꞌe madaḡanoꞌe vazetitiro.   
\s1 Iesu Runeo Tuḡuniꞌuma rae Reiro  
\r (Mataio 27:15-26; Mareko 15:6-15; Ioane 18:39-19:16)  
\p
\v 13 Pilatoꞌa dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa, vaze boroboro ebu haba azaḡa huze nuꞌoziro.  
\v 14 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe vaze ꞌadaꞌa haba azaḡa ibi veꞌoḡano ibitoziro radu tutune areha. Rehano eḡeꞌa zae zamao ani ḡadinatene, zaeꞌa ane moneo rateꞌe veꞌoḡa ꞌahogani mene horoneha.  
\v 15 Heroda zuni ani mazaonoꞌo veꞌoḡani ꞌahoga mene horonadu emeḡe vaḡe bare tuḡune areha. Hube hune, ani mazaoꞌe runeo tuḡuniteꞌe veꞌoḡani ꞌahogaꞌe oꞌoꞌa.  
\v 16 Eꞌanoꞌo eḡeꞌa ani masinadu tuḡune buniꞌuma.”\f + \fr 23:16 \fv 17 \fv*\fqa Izidi Iḡine Modiroteꞌe Muiḡano aniꞌa vaze ꞌahoga ḡuꞌa neḡanonoꞌo mae buniꞌuma reiro. \f*   
\p
\v 18 Rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa niduꞌa huau iḡuniro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe manoꞌi, u Barabasiꞌe tuḡune bunoꞌi!”  
\v 19 Barabasiꞌe Ierusalema zamaḡano Roma gavamani utitoziniro zu vaze zimiro ꞌahine, ḡuꞌa neḡano ohoniro.  
\v 20 U Pilatoꞌe Iesu tuḡune bunihi radu bare ziro.  
\v 21 Rehano ze ḡihau huaro, “Ani satauronoꞌi! Satauronoꞌi!”  
\v 22 Ebu Pilatoꞌa ḡae uḡiduḡano ziro, “Ani nagi veꞌoḡa haḡairo? E ani rune moneo tuḡuniteꞌe veꞌoḡani ꞌahoga mene horoneha. Eꞌanoꞌo e ani masinadu tuḡune buniꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 23 Rehano vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa Iesu satauronoga veize ḡihau teꞌoteꞌau huaro. ꞌOugadu zeḡe agoꞌe ane ago ufeta vitiniro.  
\v 24 Eꞌanoꞌo Pilatoꞌe zeḡe ura haḡaiꞌuma rae reiro.  
\v 25 Ebu ani zeḡeꞌa uminiroteꞌe teige, Roma gavamani utitoziniroteꞌe zu vaze goruziroteꞌe vazeḡa, Barabasi ḡuꞌa neḡanonoꞌo mae buniro. U zeḡe urao Iesuꞌe satauronoga veize uti azaḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌiniro.   
\s1 Iesu Satauroniro  
\r (Mataio 27:32-44; Mareko 15:21-32; Ioane 19:17-27)  
\p
\v 26 Uti azaḡaniꞌa Iesu tutune onamiroteꞌea, Kurene vazeḡa ꞌahoga niḡa Simona hidiro. Ze aniꞌa guniꞌa neḡanonoꞌo areꞌeteꞌe ibiḡano obonadu Iesu satauro mae heratoharo, ebu Iesu ḡaruna hegotoga veize tuḡutuḡuniro.  
\v 27 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa zuni Iesu hegote onamiro. Zeḡe boꞌaḡano roḡaeroḡaeꞌa Iesu vetuḡaneadu niau kuaro.  
\v 28 Iesuꞌa tehadu ziro, “Ierusalema aboḡaaboḡa, eḡe uꞌano ago nianoꞌi, rehano za zu ubudeze veize nianoꞌi.  
\v 29 Mazaḡa aduga boro hiditeꞌe madaḡaniꞌa arine, vaze niduꞌa ꞌahige reꞌuma, 'Gabani roḡaeḡa, ene mene hune fureniroteꞌe roḡaeḡa, zu nune hina ene mene hune ḡubuziroteꞌe roḡaeḡaꞌe manoḡa tauḡi!'  
\v 30 Eꞌe madaḡano ze maḡa niꞌuma, 'Emeḡe rana iḡau buanoꞌi!' ebu maḡa komeꞌa niꞌuma, 'Fahanadu emeḡe ḡahifoꞌi!'  
\v 31 Eꞌe ire ḡaboga heuḡa, rehano zaeꞌa satauroheꞌohe. ꞌOugine za, ire roḡa azaḡa, aduga ufeta boro hidiꞌuma.”   
\p
\v 32 Ḡonore azaḡa aheu zuni Iesu teite zemoga radu tutuze onamiro.  
\v 33 Ebu zeꞌe Vadini Isiga rae huneꞌeteꞌe habaꞌano feuriro. Eꞌea Iesu zu ḡonore azaḡa aheu satauroziro. Vaze ꞌahogaꞌe Iesu edaꞌe moneo zu ꞌahogaꞌe kauri moneo ikokoziro.  
\v 34 Ebu Iesuꞌa satauronoꞌo reiro, “Mama, zeḡe haḡai sauꞌa aḡutu modoꞌi, mazaḡa zeꞌe nagini haḡaeꞌetaꞌaꞌe aḡuꞌa.” Ze kaḡusi arahoḡa arahadu Iesu dabua ḡahugotitiro.   
\p
\v 35 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡaniꞌa edanadu muririnu. U vaze ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaꞌe Iesu ḡirihohauꞌenaꞌa ḡoeriro, “Ani vaze nunu ḡaboziro. Aniꞌe Keriso, Badiꞌaꞌa ohotiroteꞌe vazeḡa reine, ani aneꞌa bare ḡaboniꞌuma!”  
\v 36 Uti azaḡaniꞌa zuni ani vaḡe aradu rae sausauniro ebu vaini vuḡa ḡiḡiꞌa gagoharo.  
\v 37 Ebu zeḡeꞌa niro, “Ḡaꞌe Iuda azaḡa kini roꞌidene, ḡa ḡaeꞌa bare ḡaboꞌoꞌi!”  
\v 38 Iesu satauro hitaganoꞌe ane haḡai sauꞌaꞌe nagini rae ihozifine ꞌahige rae mirihiro, “ꞌADIꞌE IUDA AZAḠA KINI.”   
\p
\v 39 Iesu teite satauroniroteꞌe ḡonore vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa zuni ani rae sausauniro, “Ḡaꞌe mene Kerisohe? Ḡa ḡae bare zu emeḡe ḡabofoꞌi!”  
\v 40 Rehano ḡonore vazeḡa ꞌahoganiꞌa ḡonore vazeḡa ꞌomo roniro, “Ḡa Badiꞌa mene rihoneꞌehe? Ḡae zuni ane teite idaḡa runeo tuḡuzeha.  
\v 41 Emetaneꞌe emeḡe haḡai sauꞌa uꞌano eꞌe naeḡa aduga hideꞌohe, rehano vaze ꞌadiꞌe haḡai sauꞌa ꞌahogani mene haḡairo.”  
\v 42 Ebu aneꞌa Iesu niro, “Iesu, ḡaeꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe habaꞌa diuḡoꞌidene, eḡe zuni zamaroꞌi.”  
\v 43 Iesuꞌa naenaeniro, “Eḡeꞌa hube hune ḡaꞌohe, izidi ḡaꞌe eḡe teite Badiꞌa habao radiꞌuma.” \fig Iesu zu ḡonore vazeḡa aheu satauroziro|src="CN01836B.TIF" size="col" ref="23:33-43" \fig*   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Rudaro  
\r (Mataio 27:45-56; Mareko 15:33-41; Ioane 19:28-30)  
\p
\v 44 Madai kirikiri meirotene, haba niduꞌa uzaboꞌa ꞌuiro, onamo ḡorava mone mada uḡidu.  
\v 45 Mada mene hiaro, ebu kuru neḡano Haba Zaḡoḡa Hune ꞌueꞌeteꞌe dabuaḡaniꞌa nemao zigau ꞌaꞌadaro.  
\v 46 Ebu Iesuꞌa agoḡa boro hina ḡihau huaro, “Mama, eḡe vineꞌe ḡae ꞌevoreo tiꞌohe.” Ani ꞌouge huaroteꞌe enogano iriga riꞌiro.   
\p
\v 47 Roma uti vazeḡa boroꞌe naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe horonirotene, ani Badiꞌa niguniro ebu ꞌahige rae reiro, “Vaze ꞌadiꞌe hube hune vaze duduḡa reiro!”  
\v 48 Vaze ḡuḡuvaḡa zuni Iesuꞌa satauro rana rudaroteꞌe muririro, ebu naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe horonirotene zamaze ufeta areꞌenaꞌa,\f + \fr 23:48 \fqa ꞌuꞌunize faꞌofaꞌoneꞌenaꞌa \f* neze bare ḡouriro.  
\v 49 Iesu edeḡa azaḡa niduꞌa zu Galilea habaꞌanonoꞌo hegote ariroteꞌe roḡaeḡaroḡaeḡaꞌe faḡano edanadu eꞌe niduꞌa muririro.   
\s1 Iesu Guriro  
\r (Mataio 27:57-61; Mareko 15:42-47; Ioane 19:38-42)  
\p
\v 50 Vaze ꞌahoga, niḡa Iosefaꞌa radiunu. Aniꞌe vaze manoḡa zu duduḡa, ebu Iuda azaḡa nuꞌonuꞌo boro ibitohauꞌeteꞌe vazeḡa ꞌahoga.  
\v 51 Aniꞌe Iudea habaꞌano Arimate neḡa vazeḡa, zu Badiꞌaꞌa zuhiꞌaziꞌeteꞌe guhine radiunu. Ebu aniꞌe nuꞌonuꞌo azaḡa boroboroꞌa Iesu matihi reirotene, ḡoereze zu haḡaize mene mae ḡihiniro.  
\v 52 Aniꞌa Pilato vaḡe onamadu Iesu ahiꞌa mouga veize uminiro, ebu Pilatoꞌa ani ꞌevoꞌa riꞌiniro.  
\v 53 ꞌOugadu Iosefaꞌa satauronoꞌo Iesu ahiri mae bunadu dabua manoḡa hina ꞌumiro. Ebu vatava huꞌiroteꞌe iduḡa zamaḡano Iesu ahiri tiro. Idu aꞌe rune vaze ꞌahoga ꞌize mene tiroteꞌe iduḡa iziga.  
\v 54 Aꞌe Bana Madaḡa veize ruhibeꞌeteꞌe ḡoravaḡa, ebu Bana Madaḡa hanitiro.   
\p
\v 55 Galilea habaꞌanonoꞌo Iesu hegote ariroteꞌe roḡaeḡaroḡaeḡaꞌe Iosefa hegote onamadu iduḡa horoniro, ebu Iesu ahiri nouma tiroteꞌe horoniro.  
\v 56 Ebu ze neze baradu Iesu ahiri asohanoga veize murava hohoḡa zu dehoro hohoḡa manoḡa ruhibiro. Ebu Mose goro ḡoeꞌa idunaḡano Bana Madaḡano ze ahirize ohone baniro.   
\c 24  
\s1 Iesuꞌa Bare Ḡabodiro  
\r (Mataio 28:1-10; Mareko 16:1-8; Ioane 20:1-10)  
\p
\v 1 Fura oherebau uzeuze, roḡaeroḡaeꞌe zeꞌa ruhibiroteꞌe muravaḡa hohoḡa madu idu onamiro.  
\v 2 Ze feurirotene, idu ꞌuiroteꞌe hadiḡa boro kiune vaḡinoga horoniro.  
\v 3 Ebu ze diuḡirotene, Zuhiꞌa Boro Iesu ahiri mene horoniro.  
\v 4 ꞌOugadu zamare ꞌadaꞌadiroteꞌea, ohoze aheuꞌa tabara zeḡe babaḡano edaro. Zeꞌe dabua vazavazahoḡa vidaro.  
\v 5 Ebu roḡaeroḡaeꞌa rihau rudanadu ubumaze rahao ḡuḡuriro. Rehano ohoze aheuꞌa ziro, “Za nougadu ḡabone vazeḡa rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaḡeꞌohe?  
\v 6 Ani ꞌahao ꞌoꞌoꞌa, rehano bare ḡabode iḡuneha. Aniꞌa Galilea habaꞌano zae teite radiunutene, nagini ziroteꞌe zamaroꞌi.  
\v 7 Aniꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, 'Vaze Ubugaꞌe haḡai sauꞌa azaḡa ꞌevoreo riꞌini huniꞌuma ebu satauroniꞌuma, rehano mada uḡiduḡano bare ḡabode iḡuniꞌuma.'”  
\v 8 ꞌOuge reirotene, roḡaeroḡaeꞌa Iesuꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa zamariro.   
\p
\v 9 Ze iduonoꞌo baradu zeḡe mazao naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe niduꞌa Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana tiba fare zu vaze niduꞌa ziro.  
\v 10 Idu onamiroteꞌe roḡaeḡaroḡaeḡaꞌe Magadala roḡaeḡa Maria, Ioana, Iakobo viꞌa Maria ebu roḡae nunu. Zeꞌe naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe apostolo azaḡa ziro.  
\v 11 Rehano apostolo azaḡaꞌe zeḡe ḡoereꞌe ḡiriho hariḡa radu mene mae ḡihiniro.  
\v 12 U Peteroꞌe iḡunadu idu dure onamiro. Ebu aniꞌa ḡuḡuradu idu zamaḡa ḡianirotene, Iesu ahiri ꞌumiroteꞌe dabuaḡa daꞌo deꞌea radoga horoniro. Ebu ani naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe zamare ꞌadaꞌadeꞌenaꞌa, neḡa bare onamiro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Emausa Neḡa Ibiḡano Fureraro  
\r (Mareko 16:12-13)  
\p
\v 13 Eꞌe madaḡano Iesu hegoteꞌeteꞌe azaḡa boꞌaḡano vaze aheuꞌa Emausa neḡa onamiro. Eꞌe neḡa faḡaꞌe Ierusalemaonoꞌo gaubanana tiba fare kilomita.  
\v 14 Zeꞌe naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe niduꞌa moneo ḡoretitinu.  
\v 15 Zeḡeꞌa ḡoꞌane onameꞌeteꞌe zamaḡano, Iesuꞌa zeḡe uhiḡa aradu zeḡe teite onamiro.  
\v 16 Ze ani horoniro rehano, aꞌe Iesu rae mene ederiro, mazaḡa ubumaze ꞌuadu ze ani mene ederiro.   
\p
\v 17 Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “Zaꞌe onameꞌenaꞌa, nagini ḡoꞌaneꞌohe?” Ebu zamazeꞌa areꞌenaꞌa, ze tue edaro.  
\v 18 Zeḡe boꞌaḡano vaze ꞌahoga, niḡa Kuleopaꞌa niro, “Mada nu zamaḡano Ierusalemao naginiꞌa fureranataꞌaꞌe vaze niduꞌa edeḡa. Ḡaꞌe eꞌea radiunu rehano, ḡae daꞌo aḡuꞌahe?”   
\p
\v 19 Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “Naginiꞌa fureraneha?” Ze naenaeniro, “Aꞌe Nazareta vazeḡa Iesu hariḡa. Aniꞌe Badiꞌa zu vaze niduꞌa zamao haḡai gigiꞌaḡa haḡainuteꞌe zu ḡoere gigiꞌaḡa haraminuteꞌe peroveta vazeḡa.  
\v 20 Rehano dibuꞌo vazeḡa ḡihiꞌaḡaḡihiꞌaḡa zu vaze ibitoziꞌeteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa Iesu runeo tuḡuniꞌuma radu satauroniro.  
\v 21 Eme aniꞌe Isaraela azaḡa agireze mazaonoꞌo bohaze buziteꞌe vazeḡa rae mae ḡihiniro. Mene eꞌe daꞌo, izidi Iesu rudaroteꞌe madaḡa enogano mada uḡidu maha,  
\v 22 ebu emeḡe boꞌaḡano roḡae nuꞌa emeḡe mae zaguzagufeha. Ze izidi oherebau uzeuze idu onameha,  
\v 23 rehano Iesu ahiꞌa mene horoneha. Ebu ze bare aradu ꞌahige rae raha, 'Tuḡure viga nuꞌa fureranadu Iesuꞌe bare ḡabodeha rae raha.'  
\v 24 Eꞌanoꞌo emeḡe boꞌaḡano vaze nuꞌa idu onamatene, roḡaeroḡaeꞌa rateꞌe teige horoneha, ebu zeḡe zuni Iesu ahiꞌaꞌe mene horoneha.”   
\p
\v 25 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe kauriḡa. Za peroveta azaḡaniꞌa reiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa ufeta negane mae ḡihineꞌohe.  
\v 26 Peroveta azaḡaniꞌa reiroteꞌe teige, Kerisoꞌe ꞌouge aduga meꞌuma ebu hena ane haba ḡihiꞌa hune diuḡiꞌuma.”  
\v 27 Ebu Iesuꞌa Moseonoꞌo onamo peroveta azaḡa niduꞌa ani moneo Buka Zaḡoḡa niduꞌa zamaḡano nagini mirihiroteꞌe faine ihoziro.   
\p
\v 28 Ze Emausa neḡa hanitirotene, Iesuꞌe ꞌize ibio onameꞌeteꞌe teigiro.  
\v 29 ꞌOugadu ze Iesu ḡihau uminiro, “Ḡoravaraneha zu madaꞌe hauḡeha. Emeḡe ne onamadu bazihi.” Eꞌanoꞌo Iesuꞌa zeḡe neo bazi onamiro.   
\p
\v 30 Aniꞌa zeḡe teite ogomu atihi radu ehorirotene, ꞌuvahu odoga madu Badiꞌa mazao kuraro ebu vahege ziniro.  
\v 31 ꞌOugirotene, ubumazeꞌa bohatanadu aniꞌe Iesu rae ederiro. Rehano zeḡe mazaonoꞌo aniꞌa dauḡiro.  
\v 32 Ebu ze ḡoretitiro, “Aneꞌa ibio eme teite ḡoerateꞌe zu Buka Zaḡoḡa huga ihofateꞌe zamaḡano zamafeꞌa matuꞌe rudaneha!”   
\p
\v 33 Ebu ze zogone iḡunadu Ierusalema bare itiro, ebu eꞌea Iesu tahiꞌa gaubanana tiba fare zu zeḡe teite radiunuteꞌe azaḡaniꞌa nuꞌoru tiburaroteꞌe horoziro.  
\v 34 Zeꞌa ꞌahige rae reiro, “Hube hune Iesuꞌa bare ḡabodeha ebu Simona\f + \fr 24:34 \ft Petero \f* mazao fureraneha!”  
\v 35 ꞌOugadu vaze aheu eꞌeꞌa zuni Emausa ibiḡano zeḡe mazao naginiꞌa fureraroteꞌe ihoziro, zu Iesuꞌa ꞌuvahu odoga vahegirotene aniꞌe Iesu rae ederiroteꞌe hariḡa meꞌodoziniro.   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Ane Tahiꞌatahiꞌa mazao Fureraro  
\r (Mataio 28:16-20; Mareko 16:14-18; Ioane 20:19-23; Apostolo 1:6-8)  
\p
\v 36 Ze harize meꞌodeꞌeteꞌea, Iesu aneꞌa bare zeḡe boꞌaḡano edaro ebu ziro, “Zama roḡeḡaꞌe zae teite radoꞌi.”  
\v 37 Rehano zeꞌe zaguzagaro zu rihau rudaro, mazaḡa ze ane vine horoneꞌohe rae zamariro.  
\v 38 Iesuꞌa ziro, “Zaꞌe nougadu rihauꞌohe? Nougadu zamare doudeꞌohe?  
\v 39 Eḡe ꞌevore zu oda ḡianoꞌi. ꞌAhiꞌe eḡe! Obohoꞌi zu ḡiahoꞌi. Vineꞌe modare zu isine oꞌoꞌa, rehano za horoheꞌeteꞌe teige, eꞌe modareheta zu isineheta.”  
\v 40 Aniꞌa ꞌouge radu ꞌevoꞌa zu odaḡa ihoziro.  
\v 41 Rehano ze matuꞌe rudaroteꞌe zu zaguzagaroteꞌe uꞌano, ꞌize Iesu ḡoere mene mae ḡihiniro. Ebu Iesuꞌa ḡadiziro, “Zae mazao ogomu nu eꞌehe?”  
\v 42 ꞌOugadu ze ḡozone kiroḡa tiba haro.  
\v 43 Ebu aniꞌa madu zeḡe zamao aro.   
\p
\v 44 Ebu Iesuꞌa ziro, “Eḡeꞌa zae teite radiunuteꞌe madaḡano ꞌahige rae ziro, 'Mose goro ḡoeꞌa, peroveta azaḡa buka zu Salamo bukaḡa zamaḡano eḡe moneo mirihiroteꞌe ḡoeꞌa niduꞌa hube hune hudaꞌuma.'”  
\v 45 Ebu Iesuꞌa ze Buka Zaḡoḡa huga ederoga veize zamaze bohaniro.  
\v 46 Ebu aniꞌa ziro, “Buka Zaḡoḡano ꞌahige rae mirihiro, 'Kerisoꞌe aduga hidiꞌuma, ebu mada uḡiduḡano rune azaḡa boꞌaḡano bare ḡabodiꞌuma.  
\v 47 Ebu Keriso niḡano vaze haḡaiḡa sauꞌa rae modeꞌeteꞌe hariḡa manoḡaꞌe Ierusalemaonoꞌo onamo habaꞌahabaꞌa niduꞌa zamaḡano haramiꞌuma.'  
\v 48 Zaꞌe eꞌeguḡa niduꞌa hudaroteꞌe horoneha, eꞌanoꞌo zaeꞌa vaze niduꞌa mazao eḡe hari manoḡa haramiꞌuma.  
\v 49 Ḡiꞌanoꞌi, eḡe Mamaꞌa ḡoitoriroteꞌe Vine Zaḡoḡa eḡeꞌa zae mazao tuḡuniꞌuma. Eꞌanoꞌo Ierusalema zamaḡano guhiu radoꞌi, onamo adureonoꞌo areꞌeteꞌe gigiꞌaḡaniꞌa zae iri'avoziꞌuma.”   
\s1 Iesuꞌa Adure Itiro  
\r (Mareko 16:19-20; Apostolo 1:9-11)  
\p
\v 50 Ebu Iesuꞌa ze tutuzadu Betania neḡa uhiḡa onamiro. Ebu ꞌevoꞌa ḡihinadu zeḡe veize kuraro.  
\v 51 Aniꞌa zeḡe veize kurauꞌenaꞌa ze muhiziro, ebu ani adure ḡoha mae ḡihine itiro.  
\v 52 Ebu ze Iesu mazao kuraro zu matuꞌuzeta Ierusalema bare onamiro.  
\v 53 Ebu ze Badiꞌa niguneꞌenaꞌa, iḡaiḡa kuru neḡano radiunu. \fig Iesuꞌa adure itiro|src="DN00497b.tif" size="col" ref="24:51" \fig*   